rect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic Oakley lenses with its sunglasses and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you demand: each Oakley frame comes with original brand markings certified by Oakley itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-holbrook-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(10, 'Swarovski SK1024', 'Swarovski', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 276.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Swarovski-SK1024-Silver-401M-Eyeglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Swarovski-SK1024-Gold-404M-Eyeglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Swarovski SK1024 Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Swarovski frames. Swarovski eyewear for women instantly brightens any look with the shimmer of cut crystal accents. Our collection of Swarovski frames offers bold sophistication and glimmer, favoring classic silhouettes artfully enhanced with Swarovski crystal designs and sculptural accents. Women who enjoy a hint of glamour and glimmer in their day-to-day looks will appreciate the shimmering options in Swarovski eyewear.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/swarovski-sk1024-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(11, 'Burberry BE4291', 'Burberry', 'Sunglasses', 314.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/burberry-sun-BE4291-3007-H.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/burberry-be4291-sunglasses-346487-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/burberry-be4291-sunglasses-3001g-angle.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Burberry BE4291 Sunglasses now. Ditch the status quo and stand out from the crowd with a pair of Burberry BE4291 sunglasses for men. These semi-rimless frames offer an unusual rectangular silhouette that’s eye-catching but not overbearing. The lightweight plastic rims are hypoallergenic, and they feature subtle curves at each corner to give the glasses a gently upswept appearance. For effortless style every day of the week, reach for these innovative Burberry sunglasses for men. Throughout Burberry\'s 150 year history, it has become one of the most famous and recognizable names in fashion, not to mention eyewear. Burberry is dedicated to providing the highest quality products and materials so that its eyeglass frames maintain the legacy of fashion, elegance, and style for which Burberry is known. Classic styling and traditional designs are meshed with modern accents and youthful influences to make Burberry a company that never sacrifices style to maintain its high standards.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/burberry-be4291-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(12, 'Burberry BE2357', 'Burberry', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 296.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Burberry-Esme-Black-3757-Eyeglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/burberry-eye-BE2357-3981.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/burberry-eye-BE2357-3980.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Burberry BE2357 Eyeglasses now. These women’s Burberry BE2357 eyeglasses offer an elegant solution to your need for glasses. The cat-eye frames are crafted in hypoallergenic plastic that\'s lightweight and durable. The slim wire core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears. Take comfort and confidence wherever you go wearing these refined glasses from Burberry. Throughout Burberry\'s 150 year history, it has become one of the most famous and recognizable names in fashion, not to mention eyewear. Burberry is dedicated to providing the highest quality products and materials so that its eyeglass frames maintain the legacy of fashion, elegance, and style for which Burberry is known. Classic styling and traditional designs are meshed with modern accents and youthful influences to make Burberry a company that never sacrifices style to maintain its high standards.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/burberry-be2357-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(13, 'Dolce & Gabbana DG3415', 'Dolce & Gabbana', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 335.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Dolce-Gabbana-DG3415-Matte-Black-2525-Eyeglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Dolce-Gabbana-DG3415-Havana-502-Eyeglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Dolce & Gabbana DG3415 Eyeglasses now. Luxury is all in the details, and Dolce & Gabbana eyewear for men and women has plenty to show off. Sleek eyeglasses and sunglasses frames accented with metallic embellishments, crystal ornamentation, and more, are as much jewelry as they are eyewear. D&G puts an haute couture spin on classic frames styles that stand out from the crowd.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/dolce-gabbana-dg3415-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(14, 'Ray-Ban RB2289 - MEGA BALORAMA BLACKED OUT COLLECTION', 'Ray-Ban', 'Sunglasses', 282.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB2289-Black-6826J5-Dark-Grey-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB2289 - MEGA BALORAMA BLACKED OUT COLLECTION Sunglasses now. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb2289-mega-balorama-blacked-out-collection-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(15, 'EasyClip EC421 With Magnetic Clip-On Lens', 'EasyClip', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 209.98, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/easyclip-eyeglasses-ec421-blue-crystal-blue-wclip.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/easyclip-eyeglasses--ec421-brown-crystal-marbled-wclip.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/easyclip-eyeglasses-ec421-red-crystal-white-wclip.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore EasyClip EC421 With Magnetic Clip-On Lens Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on EasyClip frames. The EasyClip EC421 With Magnetic Clip-On Lens eyeglasses for women are stylish and functional. These rectangular clip-on frames feature a subtle upswept browline for an elegant appearance. The plastic rims are lightweight, comfortable, and durable, with sturdy components to keep them in place through wear after wear. No matter where life takes you, indoors or out, you can just clip on your EasyClip® and in a second, change your optical frames into sunglasses! EasyClip® frames come with a customizable magnetic clip-on, designed to be discreet, practical, and stylish. The temples of these frames can rotate 360°, making them durable, comfortable, and perfect for kids! Technology designed for real life.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/easyclip-ec-421-with-clip-on-lens-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(16, 'Nike 7090', 'Nike', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 236.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/nike-7090-eyeglasses-001-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/nike-eyeglasses-7090-matte-navy.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/nike-eyeglasses-7090-matte-dark-grey.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/nike-7090-eyeglasses-018-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/nike-eye-7090-068.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/nike-eye-7090-010.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Nike 7090 Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Nike frames. The Nike 7090 eyeglasses for men are designed with an eye toward comfort and style. The rectangular frames are lightweight, durable, and flexible, resulting in glasses that are comfortable to wear throughout your day. The wire cores of the slim plastic temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and the brow end offers a designer appeal. For quality eyewear designed with you in mind, reach for these stylish rectangular glasses by Nike. The Nike eyewear collection offers the same dependability as the brand’s celebrated sports apparel and equipment. These frames come with innovative performance features to outfit your lifestyle. Find athletic eyewear for men, women, and children—including sunglasses customized with lenses in your prescription—eyewear that’s designed to keep up on any adventure. Excellence in design is part of Nike’s commitment to its customers. Men, women, and children count on this global name for their eyewear, for sports and for everyday performance.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/nike-7090-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(17, 'Ray-Ban RB5397 - Elliot Optics', 'Ray-Ban', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 210.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Elliot-Optics-2000-Black-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Elliot-Optics-Havana-2012-Eyeglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Elliot-Optics-Blue-On-Transparent-Blue-8324-Eyeglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Elliot-Optics-8174-Yellow-Blue-Havana-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Elliot-Optics-Brown-Grey-Havana-8173-Eyeglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Elliot-Optics-8175-Brown-Violet-Havana-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Elliot-Optics-Striped-Brown-Green-8255-Eyeglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB5397-Havana-On-Transparent-Green-8249-Eyeglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB5397-Striped-Grey-e-Blue-8254-Eyeglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB5397-Striped-Brown-e-Red-8251-Eyeglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB5397 - Elliot Optics Eyeglasses now. For a look that’s both professional and distinctive, opt for the Ray-Ban RB5397 - Elliot Optics eyeglasses. These unisex frames feature rounded edges and plastic rims, materials that make them lightweight yet sturdy, ideal for long days in front of the computer or sunnier occasions outdoors. The skull temples curve inward to keep the glasses from slipping during activity, while designer appeal to these timeless frames is enhanced by classic style. For clean design, choose these elegant Ray-Ban eyeglasses. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb5397-elliot-optics-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(18, 'Ray-Ban Meta RW4006 - Wayfarer', 'Ray-Ban Meta', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 299.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RW4006-Black-601-SB-Electronics-1.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RW4006-Black-601SM1-Green-Electronics-1.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Ray-Ban Meta RW4006 - Wayfarer Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Ray-Ban Meta frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-meta-rw4006-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(19, 'XXL Scottie', 'XXL', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 207.50, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/xxl-SCOTTIE-gunmetal.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/xxl-SCOTTIE-brown.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/XXL-eye-Scottie-Navy.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore XXL Scottie Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on XXL frames. XXL Eyewear specializes in creating frames for the man with a larger head, in lightweight, hypoallergenic titanium, performance plastic, and sturdy, corrosion-resistant Monel alloy. Explore men’s eyewear styles by XXL to find wider eye, bridge, and temple sizes for a comfortable slip- and pinch-free fit. XXL frames offer the same refined appearance as other designer brands, but these are proportioned specifically for you. No more searching through frames to find a style that happens to be the right size—each XXL frame is designed for fashion and fit, so you get the style you want, and not whatever is left.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/xxl-scottie-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(20, 'Ray-Ban RB6513', 'Ray-Ban', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 249.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB6513-Black-On-Silver-3163-Eyeglasses-1.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB6513-Optics-Black-On-Gold-2890-Eyeglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB6513-Gunmetal-3135-Eyeglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB6513-Black-3161-Eyeglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB6513 Eyeglasses now. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb6513-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(21, 'Gucci GG1138O', 'Gucci', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 385.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Gucci-GG1138O-001-Eyeglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Gucci GG1138O Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Gucci frames. These refined GG1138O eyeglasses from Gucci are ideal for the wearer who appreciates a classic look with an upscale flair. The rectangular rims are crafted in hypoallergenic, lightweight plastic that’s durable and sturdy enough for your everyday wear. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and boast signature branding near the brow end for designer appeal. Enjoy clean styling in these timeless rectangular GG1138O glasses from Gucci. Founded in Florence, Italy, in 1921, Gucci is one of the world\'s leading luxury brands. Following the House\'s centenary, Gucci forges ahead into the next hundred years, continuing to redefine luxury while celebrating the creativity, Italian craftsmanship, and innovation at the core of its values. Gucci is part of the global luxury group Kering, which manages the development of a series of renowned Houses in fashion, leather goods, jewelry, and eyewear. Discover more about Gucci at www.gucci.com . The latest range of sunglasses and optical frames embodies Gucci\'s signature designs. Drawing inspiration from the archive of the House, the eyewear collection combines emblematic codes with new details in an unexpected selection of shapes and styles.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/gucci-gg1138o-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(22, 'Modo 4238', 'Modo', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 335.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Modo-eye-4238-navy.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Modo-eye-4238-brown-gun.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Modo-eye-4238-olive.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Modo 4238 Eyeglasses now. Modo 4238 eyeglasses for men boast a titanium metal frame that’s lightweight, durable, and corrosion-resistant. The rectangular rims are hypoallergenic and feature an elegant split wingtip design. These glasses come with thin metal cores to ensure they\'re comfortable behind the ears, even after extended wear. With their classic styling and high quality construction, these Modo eyeglasses make an excellent addition to your everyday wardrobe. The philosophy of Modo is that simplicity is the highest form of sophistication. Created in SoHo, the trendsetting Modo eyewear collection is \"eyewear for the individual.\" Modo eyewear offers a new type of luxury with uncompromising craftsmanship, design sensitivity and urban influences.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/modo-4238-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(23, 'Ray-Ban RB8903', 'Ray-Ban', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 276.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB8903-Optics-5263-Black-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB8903-Optics-5200-Havana-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB8903-Optics-5262-Blue-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB8903-Optics-5244-Grey-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB8903-Optics-5681-Black-a.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB8903 Eyeglasses now. These Ray-Ban RB8903 eyeglasses reflect a timeless aesthetic that’s always in style. The rectangular rims are crafted in hypoallergenic, lightweight plastic that\'s durable enough to stand up to everyday wear. The slim temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for added stability behind the ears. Enjoy clean design wherever you go wearing these timeless rectangular Ray-Ban RB8903 eyeglasses. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb8903-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(24, 'Oakley Barrelhouse 0.5', 'Oakley', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 255.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Barrelhousea-05-Pewter-317402-Eyeglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Barrelhousea-05-Matte-Black-317401-Eyeglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Barrelhousea-05-Matte-Midnight-317404-Eyeglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley Barrelhouse 0.5 Eyeglasses now. Oakley Barrelhouse 0.5 eyeglasses offer a bold rectangular design that’s sure to turn heads. The metal frames make these glasses lightweight and comfortable, while also allowing them to retain their shape over time. Rimless construction minimizes the visible area of the lenses, resulting in an elegantly framed eye profile. If you appreciate high-quality eyewear with sport-inspired style, choose these Oakley men\'s glasses. The Oakley brand is universally recognized and is synonymous with innovative, quality craftsmanship. Oakley is a leading name in sports eyewear because it offers athletes stylish eyewear that is made with cutting-edge design and technology so that it not only looks good but can also withstand harsh environments and truly extreme conditions. Oakley builds its optical frames with care and precision, and Oakley’s eyeglasses also feature top-quality materials, like O Matter® and Unobtainium®. Oakley glasses are made with a three-point fit system, which maximizes optical performance by holding the lenses in precise optical alignment. Oakley offers both lifestyle and performance eyeglasses that transition seamlessly from the office to the outdoors. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic Oakley eyeglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you love: each Oakley frame comes with original brand markings certified by Oakley itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-barrelhouse-0.5-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(25, 'Costa Fantail Pro', 'Costa', 'Sunglasses', 309.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Fantail-PRO-Matte-Black-907901-Blue-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Fantail-PRO-Matte-Black-907902-Green-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Fantail-PRO-Matte-Black-907903-Copper-Silver-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Fantail-PRO-Matte-Black-907904-Gray-Silver-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Fantail-PRO-Matte-Black-907905-Sunrise-Silver-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Fantail-PRO-Matte-Gray-907909-Blue-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Fantail-PRO-Matte-Gray-907910-Green-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Fantail-PRO-Matte-Black-907914-Gold-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Fantail-PRO-Matte-Tortoise-907915-Green-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Fantail-PRO-Matte-Wetlands-907907-Green-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Fantail-PRO-Tiger-Shark-907913-Blue-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Costa Fantail Pro Sunglasses now. Step out in distinctive style wearing the men’s Costa Fantail Pro sunglasses. These rectangular frames are made from a lightweight, durable plastic that\'s strong enough to keep up on your busiest days. The thick rims feature a subtle fishtail design with cutouts at the inner corners for added eye exposure. For comfort as well as style, opt for these cool Costa sunglasses. Costa eyewear is made for those with an active lifestyle, bringing a healthy dose of fashion to the beach or trailhead. Polarized sunglasses, eyeglasses, and C-Mates bifocal readers by Costa will help you navigate in any direction your adventure leads. Created by fisherman for fisherman in the late 1980s, Costa continues to create quality sunglasses and eyeglasses with innovative technologies. These performance glasses were \"born on the water,\" and they’re made to last—each pair is a worthy investment. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Costa dealer, selling only 100% authentic Costa 580 polarized lenses with its sunglasses, prescription sunglasses, and readers frames. Costa brings you the best of both worlds—innovative lens technology paired with authentic Costa frames for any outdoor adventure. Additional Information: Costa Lens Colors and Materials (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/costa-fantail-pro-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(26, 'Gucci GG0737O', 'Gucci', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 500.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Gucci-GG0737O-crystal-018-Eyeglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Gucci GG0737O Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Gucci frames. The GG0737O eyeglasses from Gucci are a modern interpretation of the classic rectangular silhouette. The subtle curves at the upper rims complement a variety of facial types, and provide an elegant contrast to straight lines lower on the brow. Crafted in hypoallergenic plastic, these glasses are lightweight but sturdy enough to last through years of wear. Enjoy effortlessness every day when you reach for these timeless men\'s Gucci eyeglasses. Founded in Florence, Italy, in 1921, Gucci is one of the world\'s leading luxury brands. Following the House\'s centenary, Gucci forges ahead into the next hundred years, continuing to redefine luxury while celebrating the creativity, Italian craftsmanship, and innovation at the core of its values. Gucci is part of the global luxury group Kering, which manages the development of a series of renowned Houses in fashion, leather goods, jewelry, and eyewear. Discover more about Gucci at www.gucci.com . The latest range of sunglasses and optical frames embodies Gucci\'s signature designs. Drawing inspiration from the archive of the House, the eyewear collection combines emblematic codes with new details in an unexpected selection of shapes and styles.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/gucci-gg0737o-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(27, 'CHARMANT Titanium Perfection CT 8333EN', 'CHARMANT Titanium Perfection', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 312.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/CHARMANTTitaniumPerfection-eye-CT8333EN-Gray.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/CHARMANTTitaniumPerfection-eye-CT8333EN-Light-Brown.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/CHARMANTTitaniumPerfection-eye-CT8333EN-White.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore CHARMANT Titanium Perfection CT 8333EN Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on CHARMANT Titanium Perfection frames. Discover refinement that lasts in CHARMANT Titanium Perfection eyewear for men and women. These frames showcase traditional styles with elegant detailing, elevating them above everyday looks while maintaining goes-with-all ease. This eyewear speaks to men and women who insist on frames that deliver exceptional fit, sturdy design, and timeless looks.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/charmant-titanium-perfection-ct-8333en-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(28, 'Flexon EP8006', 'Flexon', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 279.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Flexon-Eye-FlexonEp8006-MatteGrey-20.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Flexon-Eye-FlexonEp8006-MatteTortoise-246.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Flexon EP8006 Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Flexon frames. Flexon rounds out its eyeglasses collection with the EP8006. These unisex round frames are made in metal, which is both lightweight and durable. The metal rims feature a subtle inward curve that adds interest to an otherwise basic silhouette. With comfortable wire cores and flexible rubber tips, these glasses stay put while you work or play. Flexon eyewear combines innovative \'memory metal\' engineering and contemporary design elements to yield eyeglasses that suit your lifestyle—and your fashion sense. This groundbreaking eyewear line for men and women features frames made from a lightweight, flexible titanium-nickel alloy—so even if you drop or bend your frames, they\'ll return to their original shape.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/flexon-ep8006-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(29, 'Chesterfield CH70XL', 'Chesterfield', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 205.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/chesterfield-ch70xl-eyeglasses-0003-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Chesterfield-eyeglasses-CH70XL-0PJP00.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Chesterfield-eye-CH70XL-Gray-Crystal-CBL.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Chesterfield CH70XL Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Chesterfield frames. The CH70XL eyeglasses from Chesterfield boast a handsome, classic design. These rectangular frames are made in metal and plastic, materials that make these glasses lightweight but sturdy. The metal rims feature an elegant polished finish, while the plastic temples are coated for comfort behind the ears. For refined taste in eyewear, choose these CH70XL glasses by Chesterfield.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/chesterfield-ch70xl-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(30, 'Emporio Armani EA1059', 'Emporio Armani', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 183.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Emporio-Armani-EA1059-3001-Matte-Black-Eyeglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Emporio-Armani-EA1059-3179-Matte-Brown-Gunmetal-Eyeglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Emporio Armani EA1059 Eyeglasses now. Emporio Armani offers a refined aesthetic in these men’s EA1059 eyeglasses. The rounded edges and slight wingtips add sophistication to a classic style. These glasses are crafted in metal, which is both lightweight and durable, ensuring comfortable, long-lasting wear. The metal frames feature an elegant polished finish with subtle textures on the inside rims for comfort against the skin. With their sleek design and timeless silhouette, these Emporio Armani glasses suit men who appreciate contemporary fashion but prefer not to be overtly trendy. The Emporio Armani eyewear collection leans on minimalist contemporary silhouettes and thick-rimmed frames in vibrant colors to create stunning modern eyewear for men and women. Youthful styles abound, with quirky accents and novel details that reflect your bold sense of fashion. The Armani tradition for smart luxury design shows in the artful lines and thoughtful details of this eyewear collection. Express your personal taste in sharp glasses from Emporio Armani.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/emporio-armani-ea1059-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(31, 'Skechers SE2154', 'Skechers', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 185.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/skechers-eyeglasses-SE2154-092.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Skechers SE2154 Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Skechers frames. Skechers SE2154 eyeglasses for women are chic and sporty. These rectangular frames are made from lightweight plastic that’s strong and durable, you won\'t worry about these glasses breaking! The skulls feature a subtle browline design, with slightly curved temples that curve inward gently for stability behind the ears. With their charmingly vintage feel, these Skechers glasses make an attractive addition to your everyday look.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/skechers-se2154-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(32, 'Liz Claiborne L 654', 'Liz Claiborne', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 210.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/liz-claiborne-eyeglasses-L-654-0UFM00.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/liz-claiborne-eyeglasses-L-654-0RY800.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Liz Claiborne L 654 Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Liz Claiborne frames. The Liz Claiborne L 654 eyeglasses reflect the designer’s commitment to on-trend style at an accessible cost. These rectangular semi-rimless frames are metal, with a lightweight construction that\'s comfortable to wear. The slightly upswept browline and squared endpoints add elegance. For effortlessness in professional settings or casual outings, choose these eye-catching L 654 glasses by Liz Claiborne.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/liz-claiborne-l-654-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(33, 'Oakley Wire Tap 2.0 RX', 'Oakley', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 387.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Wire-Tap-20-515203-Satin-Light-Steel-Eyeglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/oakley-eyeglasses-wire-tap-2-rx-OX5152-01.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley Wire Tap 2.0 RX Eyeglasses now. The Oakley Wire Tap 2.0 RX eyeglasses offer a distinctive, sporty style that’s at once professional and hip. These rectangular semi-rimless frames are made in lightweight metal that retains its shape for lasting beauty. The wirecore temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, with a keyhole opening at each temple allowing you to customize your fit by adjusting how much of the lens is exposed, increasing or decreasing light exposure depending on your preference. Enjoy cutting-edge design with performance advantages when you opt for these cool Wire Tap RX glasses from Oakley. The Oakley brand is universally recognized and is synonymous with innovative, quality craftsmanship. Oakley is a leading name in sports eyewear because it offers athletes stylish eyewear that is made with cutting-edge design and technology so that it not only looks good but can also withstand harsh environments and truly extreme conditions. Oakley builds its optical frames with care and precision, and Oakley’s eyeglasses also feature top-quality materials, like O Matter® and Unobtainium®. Oakley glasses are made with a three-point fit system, which maximizes optical performance by holding the lenses in precise optical alignment. Oakley offers both lifestyle and performance eyeglasses that transition seamlessly from the office to the outdoors. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic Oakley eyeglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you love: each Oakley frame comes with original brand markings certified by Oakley itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-wire-tap-2.0-rx-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(34, 'Fatheadz Wallstreet', 'Fatheadz', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 110.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/fatheadz-eye-WALLSTREET-black.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Fatheadz Wallstreet Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Fatheadz frames. Fatheadz Wallstreet XL eyeglasses for men make a stylish, functional addition to your look. The rectangular frames are made from hypoallergenic plastic that’s lightweight and durable, so you don\'t have to worry about these glasses losing their shape or breaking! The robust saddle bridges curve inward gently to keep the glasses from slipping during active pursuits. You’ll find the modern styling and the classic edge you prefer within the Fatheadz eyewear collection, including sporty wraparound frames, classic wayfarers, and sleek metal frames, in contemporary full-rim and semi-rimless styles. Fatheadz eyewear is designed to provide grip and comfort specifically for the man with a large or wide head—these frames feature longer temple arms and wider bridge and lens widths so they don’t slip, slide, or pinch.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/fatheadz-wallstreet-xl-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL);
