ates bifocal readers by Costa will help you navigate in any direction your adventure leads. Created by fisherman for fisherman in the late 1980s, Costa continues to create quality sunglasses and eyeglasses with innovative technologies. These performance glasses were \"born on the water,\" and they’re made to last—each pair is a worthy investment. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Costa dealer, selling only 100% authentic Costa 580 polarized lenses with its sunglasses, prescription sunglasses, and readers frames. Costa sunglasses readers bring you the best of both worlds, with Costa lens technology combined with gradual magnification in powers from +1.75 to +2.50 (no visible line).', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/costa-c-mates-bifocal-readers-tuna-alley-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(55, 'Ray-Ban RB3025JM - Aviator Full Color', 'Ray-Ban', 'Sunglasses', 231.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Aviator-Full-Color-Legend-Black-On-Gold-919671-Grey-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB3025JM-Grey-919632-Light-Grey-Gradient-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB3025JM - Aviator Full Color Sunglasses now. Reach for a pair of Ray-Ban RB3025JM aviator Full Color sunglasses and enjoy the attention they’ll draw. These bold shades boast an unmistakable profile, one that’s earned the aviator a place in popular culture as a timeless symbol of style and accomplishment. The metal rims are durable, while flexible hinges ensure comfort behind the ears. A coated temple tip offers added protection against slipping or sliding when you\'re on the move, a feature especially appreciated when swimming or at the beach. For effortlessness and sophistication every day, choose these handsome aviator sunglasses from Ray-Ban. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb3025jm-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(56, 'Versace VE4361', 'Versace', 'Sunglasses', 384.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/versace-ve4361-sunglasses-gb187-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/versace-sun-VE4361-531987.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/versace-ve4361-sunglasses-536077-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/versace-sun-VE4361-521773.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/versace-sun-VE4361-401-87.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/versace-sun-VE4361-533087.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/versace-sun-VE4361-311-6G.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Versace-VE4361-Transparent-Fuxia-5334-5-Fuchsia-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Versace-VE4361-Black-542287-Dark-Grey-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Versace VE4361 Sunglasses now. Versace puts a contemporary spin on the classic rectangular shades in these VE4361 sunglasses for men. The frames are crafted in hypoallergenic plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to heavy use. The thick rims feature a subtle butterfly shape and come with coated tips for comfort behind the ears. A small Versace medallion adorns each temple, marking your status as a connoisseur of fashion and style. Extravagant designs and bold embellishments feature prominently on the frames in the Versace eyewear collection. Versace\'s haute couture expertise shines in this collection of designer sunglasses and prescription eyewear for men and women. Rx-ready frames in sun and optical styles offer an opportunity to showcase your personal style in eyewear tailored with your prescription. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Versace retailer, selling only 100% authentic Versace eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you love: each Versace frame comes with original brand markings certified by Versace itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/versace-ve4361-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(57, 'Revo Winston S', 'Revo', 'Sunglasses', 239.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/WinstonS-RE1245-01-BL-34.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/WinstonS-RE1245-12-GN-34.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Revo Winston S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Revo frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/revo-winston-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(58, 'Gucci GG0692O', 'Gucci', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 465.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/gucci-eyeglasses-GG0692O-001.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Gucci GG0692O Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Gucci frames. The GG0692O eyeglasses from Gucci are a perfect example of classic style with a modern twist. The rectangular rims are made in metal that’s both lightweight and sturdy, while plastic temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears. Enjoy impeccable design when you opt for these timeless rectangular eyeglasses by Gucci. Founded in Florence, Italy, in 1921, Gucci is one of the world\'s leading luxury brands. Following the House\'s centenary, Gucci forges ahead into the next hundred years, continuing to redefine luxury while celebrating the creativity, Italian craftsmanship, and innovation at the core of its values. Gucci is part of the global luxury group Kering, which manages the development of a series of renowned Houses in fashion, leather goods, jewelry, and eyewear. Discover more about Gucci at www.gucci.com . The latest range of sunglasses and optical frames embodies Gucci\'s signature designs. Drawing inspiration from the archive of the House, the eyewear collection combines emblematic codes with new details in an unexpected selection of shapes and styles.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/gucci-gg0692o-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(59, 'Maui Jim Kaupo Gap-437', 'Maui Jim', 'Sunglasses', 259.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/maui-jim-sunglasses-h437-10-kaupo-gap.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/maui-jim-sunglasses-437-02-kaupo-gap.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/maui-jim-sunglasses-kaupo-gap-b437-03m.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Maui Jim Kaupo Gap-437 Sunglasses now. Live life on the edge in Kaupo Gap-437 unisex sunglasses by Maui Jim. The rectangular frames of these sunglasses are made in lightweight, durable plastic that’s strong enough to keep up on your most action-packed adventures. The wirecore temples curve inward gently for added stability behind the ears, and boast a subtle styling near the brow end. Step out in style wearing these cool rectangular sunglasses from Maui Jim. Maui Jim has led the eyewear industry by design and innovation since 1980, offering eyes everywhere superior protection from the harmful rays of the sun in its popular line of sunglasses. From iconic shades with patented technologies, to readers perfect for sunny-day pastimes, to the impressively stylish and comfortable daily-wear frames in the Optical line, Maui Jim creates men’s and women’s performance eyewear for any scenario. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Maui Jim dealer, selling only 100% authentic Maui Jim sunglasses frames and lenses. Polarized with an anti-reflective coating, Maui Jim lenses reveal the vibrant colors of the world while protecting your eyes from the effects of the sun\'s harsh glare and harmful rays. Satisfaction guaranteed. Additional Information: Maui Lens Colors Information (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/maui-jim-kaupo-gap-437-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(60, 'Dolce & Gabbana DG4474', 'Dolce & Gabbana', 'Sunglasses', 415.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Dolce-Gabbana-DG4474-Black-501-87-Dark-Grey-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Dolce-Gabbana-DG4474-Havana-502-73-Dark-Brown-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Dolce & Gabbana DG4474 Sunglasses now. Luxury is all in the details, and Dolce & Gabbana eyewear for men and women has plenty to show off. Sleek eyeglasses and sunglasses frames accented with metallic embellishments, crystal ornamentation, and more, are as much jewelry as they are eyewear. D&G puts an haute couture spin on classic frames styles that stand out from the crowd.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/dolce-gabbana-dg4474-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(61, 'Caterpillar CTO-3016', 'Caterpillar', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 139.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Caterpillar-eye-CTO-3016-005.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Caterpillar-eye-CTO-3016-001.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Caterpillar-eye-CTO-3016-004.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Caterpillar CTO-3016 Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Caterpillar frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/caterpillar-cto-3016-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(62, 'Electric Knoxville XL S', 'Electric', 'Sunglasses', 225.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/electric-sun-KNOXVILLE-XL-S-matte-black-EE16001090.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Electric Knoxville XL S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Electric frames. These Electric Knoxville XL S sunglasses for men exude an urban aesthetic. The wayfarer-style frames are constructed from hypoallergenic, lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to extended wear. The skull temples curve inward gently to keep the glasses from slipping during your active lifestyle. A subtle keyhole detail at the top of the rims adds a touch of elegance to these cool shades. For stylish sun protection wherever you go, opt for these Electric Knoxville XL S sunglasses by Electric.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/electric-knoxville-xl-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(63, 'Christian Siriano Sanne', 'Christian Siriano', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 120.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/CSiriano-eye-sanne-black-nude.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/CSiriano-eye-sanne-purple-tortoise.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Christian Siriano Sanne Eyeglasses now. Christian Siriano crafts an edgy, chic style in the Sanne eyeglasses for women. These rectangular rims are crafted from strong and lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to keep up on your busiest days. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and boast signature branding near the brow end for designer appeal. For exceptional designer eyewear with distinctive styling elements, choose these Sanne glasses by Christian Siriano.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/christian-siriano-sanne-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(64, 'Costa Spearo XL', 'Costa', 'Sunglasses', 309.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Spearo-XL-Matte-Black-901302-Green-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Spearo-XL-Matte-Black-901301-Blue-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Spearo-XL-Matte-Reef-901307-Green-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Spearo-XL-Matte-Black-901306-Gray-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/costa-sunglasses-spearo-xl-06S9013-05.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Spearo-XL-Matte-Reef-901308-Blue-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Spearo-XL-Matte-Black-901317-Gold-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Spearo-XL-Matte-Black-901304-Gray-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Spearo-XL-Matte-Black-901305-Blue-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Spearo-XL-Midnight-Blue-901315-Gray-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Costa Spearo XL Sunglasses now. Reach for the Costa Spearo XL sunglasses and enjoy fishing or water-sports in style. The rectangular rims on these shades are accented by cutouts at the upper brow, adding visual interest to an otherwise straightforward silhouette. Crafted with a lightweight but sturdy plastic construction, these glasses offer superior impact resistance while they stay put through rugged adventures. A woven label at the temple announces your affinity for active pursuits and eye-catching accessories alike. Costa eyewear is made for those with an active lifestyle, bringing a healthy dose of fashion to the beach or trailhead. Polarized sunglasses, eyeglasses, and C-Mates bifocal readers by Costa will help you navigate in any direction your adventure leads. Created by fisherman for fisherman in the late 1980s, Costa continues to create quality sunglasses and eyeglasses with innovative technologies. These performance glasses were \"born on the water,\" and they’re made to last—each pair is a worthy investment. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Costa dealer, selling only 100% authentic Costa 580 polarized lenses with its sunglasses, prescription sunglasses, and readers frames. Costa brings you the best of both worlds—innovative lens technology paired with authentic Costa frames for any outdoor adventure. Additional Information: Costa Lens Colors and Materials (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/costa-spearo-xl-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(65, 'Easytwist ET903 No Clip-On Lens', 'Easytwist', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 199.98, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/EasyTwist_Eyeglasses_ET903_20.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/EasyTwist_Eyeglasses_ET903_10.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Easytwist ET903 No Clip-On Lens Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Easytwist frames. The Easytwist ET903 No Clip-On Lens eyeglasses for men offer an innovative twist on a classic rectangular design. The metal frames are lightweight and comfortable, but sturdy enough to keep their shape through years of wear. A metal corewire allows you to adjust the fit for comfort and stability. If you\'re looking for style that lasts, opt for these no-clip lenses from Easytwist.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/easytwist-et-903-no-clip-on-lens-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(66, 'Armani Exchange AX3050', 'Armani Exchange', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 132.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Armani-Exchange-AX3050-8078-Matte-Black-Eyeglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Armani-Exchange-AX3050-8246-Matte-Havana-Eyeglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Armani Exchange AX3050 Eyeglasses now. Embrace timeless style and showcase your distinctive taste wearing these men\'s Armani Exchange AX3050 eyeglasses. The square rims are crafted in hypoallergenic plastic that\'s lightweight but sturdy, resulting in comfortable glasses that stay put throughout your day. The wirecore temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears. Enjoy refined styling when you step out in these elegant glasses from Armani Exchange. A|X—or Armani Exchange—eyeglasses for men and women feature an assortment of high-end frames in contemporary styles. The brand is the playful, youthful sibling of the famed Italian brand Giorgio Armani. In stark contrast to the clean-cut, sophisticated tailoring of the luxury Armani label, A|X cites \"street-chic culture, fashionable dance music, freedom, and personal styles\" as its inspirations. Those trendy influences show in this versatile eyewear line that provides luxury in every detail. From a longtime leader in the high-end fashion industry, Armani Exchange makes no compromises on style.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/armani-exchange-ax3050-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(67, 'Converse CV5086MAG-SET', 'Converse', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 152.55, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Converse-eye-CV5086MAG-SET-crystal-origin-story-022.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Converse-eye-CV5086MAG-SET-crystal-clear-970.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Converse-eye-CV5086MAG-SET-black-001.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Converse-eye-CV5086MAG-SET-crystal-obsidian-411.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Converse CV5086MAG-SET Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Converse frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/converse-cv5086mag-set-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(68, 'Ray-Ban Junior RJ9060S', 'Ray-Ban Junior', 'Sunglasses', 97.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Junior-Erika-Kids-704911-Havana-Grey-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Junior-Erika-Kids-700673-Havana-Brown-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ray-ban-jr-sun-RJ9060S-710813.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Junior-Erika-Kids-70096Q-Fuchsia-Fluo-Brown-Orange-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Junior-Erika-Kids-70084V-Violet-Fluo-Grey-Violet-a.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban Junior RJ9060S Sunglasses now. The Ray-Ban Junior RJ9060S sunglasses offer cool, youthful style. These shades boast a distinctive look featuring rounded edges and sleek lines that draw attention to the wearer’s eyes. The lightweight plastic rims are comfortable, and durable enough to last through your longest days outdoors. If you\'re looking for chic designer sunglasses with an edge of rebellion, try on these from Ray-Ban Junior. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-junior-rj9060s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(69, 'Easytwist N Clip CT227 With Magnetic Clip-On Lens', 'Easytwist N Clip', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 217.98, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/EasyTwistNClip-eye-CT227-Grey-20.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/easytwistnclip-ct227-black.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Easytwist N Clip CT227 With Magnetic Clip-On Lens Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Easytwist N Clip frames. These Easytwist N Clip CT227 With Magnetic Clip-On Lens eyeglasses for men boast a clean, professional look. The metal rectangular frames are strong and durable. The clip-on design allows you to wear these glasses without the need for ear hooks or headbands, making them ideal for active wearers. A magnetic clasp holds the clip-on lens in place so your eyes remain focused while you work or play.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/easytwist-n-clip-ct-227-with-clip-on-lens-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(70, 'Modo STEVIA', 'Modo', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 210.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Modo-Eye-STEVIA-BlueGreyTortoise-TT49.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Modo-Eye-STEVIA-Moss-SS49.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Modo-Eye-STEVIA-BurgundyBlueGradient-LG49.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Modo-Eye-STEVIA-OrangePurpleTortoise-TT49.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Modo STEVIA Eyeglasses now. The philosophy of Modo is that simplicity is the highest form of sophistication. Created in SoHo, the trendsetting Modo eyewear collection is \"eyewear for the individual.\" Modo eyewear offers a new type of luxury with uncompromising craftsmanship, design sensitivity and urban influences.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/modo-stevia-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL);
