(71, 'Chesterfield CH84XL', 'Chesterfield', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 205.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/chesterfield-eyeglasses-CH-84XL-0003-00.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/chesterfield-eyeglasses-CH-84XL-0FRE-00.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Chesterfield CH84XL Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Chesterfield frames. The Chesterfield CH84XL eyeglasses for men are a modern interpretation of the classic rectangular silhouette. The semi-rimless design displays your facial features prominently, and metal rims offer plenty of flexibility to adjust the fit. These elegant glasses come in a variety of colors, so you can coordinate them with your wardrobe or wear them to complement your personal style.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/chesterfield-ch84xl-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
