(95, 'Kate Spade Annika/S', 'Kate Spade', 'Sunglasses', 210.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/katespade-annikas-sunglasses-086pvw-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/katespade-sun-annikas-jbhp-56-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/F-ANNIKS0X00Y7.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Kate Spade Annika/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Kate Spade frames. Kate Spade Annika/S sunglasses offer a fun, feminine take on the classic rectangular silhouette. The oversized rectangular rims are crafted in hypoallergenic Monel Coated Copper alloy for comfort and durability. A plate at the temple features a metallic copper color that reflects warm shades of light as you move your head. For chic style that’s both vintage-inspired and modern, reach for these Annika/S sunglasses from Kate Spade. The sunglasses and eyeglasses in our Kate Spade collection offer the brand\'s defining mix of colors, patterns, and bold femininity. The Kate Spade eyewear line is perfect for women who appreciate an elegant look with a dash of playfulness. From sunglasses to prescription eyeglasses and sunglasses frames, the Kate Spade collection includes a spectacular array of hues, whimsical patterns, and charming shapes.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/kate-spade-annika-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(96, 'Costa Gulf Shore', 'Costa', 'Sunglasses', 222.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Gulf-Shore-Shiny-Black-907404-Blue-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Gulf-Shore-Shiny-Black-907402-Gray-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Gulf-Shore-Tortoise-907403-Green-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Costa Gulf Shore Sunglasses now. Enjoy the great outdoors in comfort when you wear the Gulf Shore sunglasses from Costa. These rimless frames are made from plant-based plastic that’s lightweight and durable, perfect for long days in the sun. The rectangular shape suits a variety of facial profiles, while slightly curved upper rims offer added protection against glare. For cool sunglasses designed with the environment in mind, reach for these Gulf Shore shades by Costa. Costa eyewear is made for those with an active lifestyle, bringing a healthy dose of fashion to the beach or trailhead. Polarized sunglasses, eyeglasses, and C-Mates bifocal readers by Costa will help you navigate in any direction your adventure leads. Created by fisherman for fisherman in the late 1980s, Costa continues to create quality sunglasses and eyeglasses with innovative technologies. These performance glasses were \"born on the water,\" and they’re made to last—each pair is a worthy investment. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Costa dealer, selling only 100% authentic Costa 580 polarized lenses with its sunglasses, prescription sunglasses, and readers frames. Costa brings you the best of both worlds—innovative lens technology paired with authentic Costa frames for any outdoor adventure. Additional Information: Costa Lens Colors and Materials (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/costa-gulf-shore-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(97, 'Takumi TK1182 With Magnetic Clip-On Lens', 'Takumi', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 209.98, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Takumi-eye-TK1182-multicolor-mint-brown-light-brown-060.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Takumi-eye-TK1182-multicolor-teal-lilac-purple-050.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Takumi-eye-TK1182-multicolor-pink-yellow-brown-030.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Takumi TK1182 With Magnetic Clip-On Lens Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Takumi frames. Upgrade your look with a pair of Takumi TK1182 With Magnetic Clip-On Lens eyeglasses. These women’s glasses offer a refined, professional appearance that\'s equally at home in the office or out on the town. The metal rims provide durability while plastic temples offer comfort behind the ears and flexibility where you need it: at the tips for easier positioning. Explore the Takumi eyewear collection for sunglasses and eyeglasses to suit refined tastes. Takumi frames, built with TurboFlex® technology allowing temple arms to rotate 360°, are durable, comfortable, and perfectly suited for everyday wear. This maker’s innovative designs and careful attention to detail live up to the meaning of the Takumi name: “Master craftsman.”', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/takumi-tk1182-with-magnetic-clip-on-lens-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(98, 'Coach HC7012', 'Coach', 'Sunglasses', 183.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/coach-sun-HC7012-910211.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Coach HC7012 Sunglasses now. Add a touch of classic style to your everyday look with these women’s Coach HC7012 sunglasses. The aviator-style frames are made in lightweight, corrosion-resistant metal that retains its shape for lasting beauty. The wirecore temples curve inward gently for stability, and come coated with socks over the tips for comfort behind the ears. Enjoy classic aviator styling when you opt for these women\'s sunglasses. Women’s designer eyewear by Coach exudes a distinctive big-city vibe in chic frames that blend modern sophistication with vintage-inspired style. The result is a collection of daring luxury eyewear that complements a wide range of wardrobes. Browse oversized frames in bold colors, or sleek silhouettes in subtle neutral hues. Coach uses modern color palettes in two-tone frames, but also includes the classics, drawing inspiration from vintage eyewear styles in black or tortoiseshell to create elegant frames that appeal to contemporary tastes.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/coach-hc7012-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(99, 'Oakley BXTR', 'Oakley', 'Sunglasses', 196.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-BXTR-Matte-Desert-Tan-928004-Prizm-Ruby-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-BXTR-Matte-Fern-928010-Prizm-Bronze-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-BXTR-Matte-Black-928003-Prizm-Sapphire-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-BXTR-Matte-Black-928001-Black-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-BXTR-Matte-Black-928005-Prizm-Black-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-BXTR-Coalesce-Collection-Transparent-Fern-928011-Prizm-Bronze-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-BXTR-Matte-Black-928015-Prizm-Black-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-BXTR-Matte-White-928002-Road-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-BXTR-Matte-Black-928019-Prizm-Black-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-BXTR-Matte-Balsam-928009-Prizm-Grey-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-BXTR-Patrick-Mahomes-II-Matte-Tan-928008-Tungsten-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-BXTR-Pacific-Matte-Abyss-928018-Prizm-Black-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley BXTR Sunglasses now. Oakley Bxtr sunglasses offer a bold, sporty look. The unisex frames are made with Oakley’s lightweight O Matter plastic, which offers durability and flexibility for activewear. Three-pointed lens geometry provides protection from glare and wind at high speeds. A keyhole shape at the endpoints adds interest to these understated shades. The Oakley brand is universally recognized and is synonymous with innovative, quality craftsmanship. Oakley is a leading name in sports sunglasses because it offers athletes stylish shades that are made with cutting edge design and technology so that it not only looks good but can also withstand harsh environments and truly extreme conditions. Oakley has perfected sporty wrap sunglasses and shields and has modernized interpretations of other classic designs. The Oakley sunglass collection offers a wide variety of frames in an exciting collection of colors and performance-driven lens shading. FramesDirect.com is your online outlet for Oakley Sunglasses. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic Oakley lenses with its sunglasses and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you demand: each Oakley frame comes with original brand markings certified by Oakley itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-bxtr-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(100, 'Ray-Ban RB3516', 'Ray-Ban', 'Sunglasses', 207.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ray-ban-sun-RB3516-004-13-wm-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ray-ban-sun-RB3516-006-9A-wm-angle.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB3516 Sunglasses now. Unleash your inner fashionista when you wear the aviator-style Ray-Ban RB3516 sunglasses for men. These bold shades boast a thick, sturdy frame made in metal and plastic that\'s lightweight enough to keep you comfortable throughout your day. The metal components include the classic butterfly silhouette at the top of the rims and narrow wirecore temples with textured tips for added grip. Crafted in strong yet flexible plastic, the doublebridge endpoints feature a sleek keyhole design, a timeless look popular today on runways around the world. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb3516-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(101, 'Oakley Enduro', 'Oakley', 'Sunglasses', 190.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/oakley-sun-enduro-oo9223-05.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley Enduro Sunglasses now. The Oakley brand is universally recognized and is synonymous with innovative, quality craftsmanship. Oakley is a leading name in sports sunglasses because it offers athletes stylish shades that are made with cutting edge design and technology so that it not only looks good but can also withstand harsh environments and truly extreme conditions. Oakley has perfected sporty wrap sunglasses and shields and has modernized interpretations of other classic designs. The Oakley sunglass collection offers a wide variety of frames in an exciting collection of colors and performance-driven lens shading. FramesDirect.com is your online outlet for Oakley Sunglasses. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic Oakley lenses with its sunglasses and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you demand: each Oakley frame comes with original brand markings certified by Oakley itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-enduro-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(102, 'Liz Claiborne L 560S', 'Liz Claiborne', 'Sunglasses', 165.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Liz-Claiborne-sunglasses-560-S-0JGPJS.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/F-L560S0JUBJS.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/F-L560S0807AM.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Liz Claiborne L 560S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Liz Claiborne frames. Embrace timeless style and showcase your distinctive taste wearing these Liz Claiborne L 560S sunglasses. These rectangular frames are crafted in hypoallergenic plastic that’s lightweight and durable, with a sturdy saddle-style browline profile. The slim temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears. Make an impression wherever you go when you slip on these cool shades from Liz Claiborne.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/liz-claiborne-l.claiborn-560s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(103, 'Takumi TK1154 With Magnetic Clip-On Lens', 'Takumi', 'Prescription Eyeglasses', 209.98, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Takumi-eye-TK1154-brown-amber-010.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Takumi-eye-TK1154-blue-brown-marbled-050.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Takumi-eye-TK1154-red-pink-marbled-030.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Takumi TK1154 With Magnetic Clip-On Lens Eyeglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Takumi frames. Takumi TK1154 With Magnetic Clip-On Lens eyeglasses for women are stylish and convenient. These rectangular clip-on frames are made from lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to last through your long workday or busy social schedule. The slim temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, with designer appeal. For chic eyeglasses designed to fit seamlessly into your lifestyle, reach for these Takumi clip-ons. Explore the Takumi eyewear collection for sunglasses and eyeglasses to suit refined tastes. Takumi frames, built with TurboFlex® technology allowing temple arms to rotate 360°, are durable, comfortable, and perfectly suited for everyday wear. This maker’s innovative designs and careful attention to detail live up to the meaning of the Takumi name: “Master craftsman.”', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/takumi-tk1154-with-magnetic-clip-on-lens-eyeglasses', NULL, NULL),
(104, 'Marc Jacobs Marc 764-S', 'Marc Jacobs', 'Sunglasses', 184.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Marc-Jacobs-764-S-Tortoise-4402B2-Blue-Grad-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Marc-Jacobs-764-S-Black-1100L3-Grey-Grad-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Marc-Jacobs-764-S-Pink-Light-3540L3-Grey-Grad-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Marc Jacobs Marc 764-S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Marc Jacobs frames. The Marc Jacobs eyewear line has the perfect frames for men and women with eclectic tastes. Marc Jacobs eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses incorporate whimsical touches—think sculptural flowers at the temples, or frames shapes transformed from oval to cat-eye with an artful arc of metal around the lenses. Go bold or go subtle with Marc Jacobs eyewear, with chunky, oversized sunglasses in the mix alongside streamlined everyday glasses that transition effortlessly from work to weekend.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/marc-jacobs-marc-764-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL);
