(105, 'Ray-Ban Junior RJ9052S New Wayfarer', 'Ray-Ban Junior', 'Sunglasses', 86.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Junior-New-Wayfarer-Kids-152-73-Havana-Dark-Brown-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Junior-New-Wayfarer-Kids-100-71-Black-Dark-Green-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Junior-New-Wayfarer-Kids-178-80-Blue-On-Orange-Blue-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Junior-New-Wayfarer-Kids-100S55-Black-Blue-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Junior-New-Wayfarer-Kids-70624L-Blue-Grey-Dark-Grey-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Junior-New-Wayfarer-Kids-100-11-Black-Grey-Dark-Grey-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Junior-New-Wayfarer-Kids-70218G-Violet-Grey-Dark-Grey-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Junior-New-Wayfarer-Kids-70636G-Grey-Grey-Silver-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Junior-New-Wayfarer-Kids-100S6Q-Black-Brown-Orange-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Junior-New-Wayfarer-Kids-Summer-Capsule-7147B1-Purple-Blue-Violet-a.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban Junior RJ9052S New Wayfarer Sunglasses now. These Ray-Ban Junior RJ9052S New Wayfarer sunglasses for children are a stylish way to protect their eyes from the sun. The oversized frames are made in hypoallergenic, lightweight plastic that’s sturdy enough to stand up to wear and tear. The thin temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for added stability behind the ears. For sunny days out on the town or a day at the beach, opt for these cool junior wayfarers from Ray-Ban. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-junior-rj9052s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(106, 'Ray-Ban RB4162', 'Ray-Ban', 'Sunglasses', 195.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ray-ban-sun-RB4162-710-51.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ray-ban-sun-RB4162-601-32.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB4162 Sunglasses now. Live life on the cutting edge wearing Ray-Ban RB4162 sunglasses. These aviator-style shades feature a bold, sophisticated silhouette that’s poised to become the next big thing in men\'s fashion. The robust frames are made in lightweight and durable plastic that retains its shape for lasting beauty. For added convenience, these Ray-Ban sunglasses come with coated lenses for protection against glare and water, as well as an integrated socksetta strap for comfort behind the ears. Daring aviator style at its finest make these shades from Ray-Ban perfect for a man seeking an original yet timeless look Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb4162-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(107, 'Oakley Coinflip', 'Oakley', 'Sunglasses', 234.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Coinflip-Matte-Black-Camo-414404-Prizm-Ruby-Polarized-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley Coinflip Sunglasses now. Oakley Coinflip sunglasses for men offer the ideal blend of sport and style. The round frames are made in O Matter, a lightweight, durable plastic that’s flexible enough to move with you through your day. Three-pointed rivets at the endpoints add an edgy look to these shades. If you\'re looking for great sunglasses designed for action as well as glamour, choose the Oakley Coinflip. The Oakley brand is universally recognized and is synonymous with innovative, quality craftsmanship. Oakley is a leading name in sports sunglasses because it offers athletes stylish shades that are made with cutting edge design and technology so that it not only looks good but can also withstand harsh environments and truly extreme conditions. Oakley has perfected sporty wrap sunglasses and shields and has modernized interpretations of other classic designs. The Oakley sunglass collection offers a wide variety of frames in an exciting collection of colors and performance-driven lens shading. FramesDirect.com is your online outlet for Oakley Sunglasses. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic Oakley lenses with its sunglasses and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you demand: each Oakley frame comes with original brand markings certified by Oakley itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-coinflip-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(108, 'Ray-Ban RB2398', 'Ray-Ban', 'Sunglasses', 206.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB2398-Grey-Transparent-13553F-Blue-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB2398-Havana-Transparent-1292M2-Brown-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB2398-Havana-Transparent-Green-1376BH-Green-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB2398-Black-Transparent-1294GJ-Clear-Green-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB2398 Sunglasses now. These Ray-Ban RB2398 sunglasses offer a classic unisex design with timeless style. The thick, curved frames are made in lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to everyday wear. The robust doublebridge is supported by slim endpoints for an elegant look. For sunny days when you need reliable eye protection and exceptional quality, reach for these cool shades from Ray-Ban. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb2398-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(109, 'Armani Exchange AX2047S', 'Armani Exchange', 'Sunglasses', 91.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Armani-Exchange-AX2047S-Matte-Black-600087-Dark-Grey-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Armani-Exchange-AX2047S-Matte-Blue-609980-Dark-Blue-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Armani-Exchange-AX4112SU-Dark-Matte-Blue-818180-Dark-Blue-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Armani-Exchange-AX2047S-Matte-Gunmetal-6003Z3-Grey-Mirror-Silver-Polar-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Armani Exchange AX2047S Sunglasses now. A|X—or Armani Exchange—eyeglasses for men and women feature an assortment of high-end frames in contemporary styles. The brand is the playful, youthful sibling of the famed Italian brand Giorgio Armani. In stark contrast to the clean-cut, sophisticated tailoring of the luxury Armani label, A|X cites \"street-chic culture, fashionable dance music, freedom, and personal styles\" as its inspirations. Those trendy influences show in this versatile eyewear line that provides luxury in every detail. From a longtime leader in the high-end fashion industry, Armani Exchange makes no compromises on style.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/armani-exchange-ax2047s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
