(131, 'Nike RABID M', 'Nike', 'Sunglasses', 109.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/NikeSun-NIKERABIDMEV1110-MtDkGryCrtPrplGryWVioM15.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Nike RABID M Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Nike frames. The Nike eyewear collection offers the same dependability as the brand’s celebrated sports apparel and equipment. These frames come with innovative performance features to outfit your lifestyle. Find athletic eyewear for men, women, and children—including sunglasses customized with lenses in your prescription—eyewear that’s designed to keep up on any adventure. Excellence in design is part of Nike’s commitment to its customers. Men, women, and children count on this global name for their eyewear, for sports and for everyday performance.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/nike-rabid-m-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(132, 'Oakley Castel', 'Oakley', 'Sunglasses', 237.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Castel-Blue-Steel-914712-Prizm-Deep-Water-Polarized-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Castel-Olive-Ink-914704-Prizm-Tungsten-Polarized-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Castel-Matte-Grey-Smoke-914705-Prizm-Ruby-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Castel-Matte-Translucent-Blue-914706-Prizm-Deep-Water-Polarized-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Castel-Matte-Silver-Blue-Colorshift-914713-Prizm-Sapphire-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Castel-Matte-Black-Ink-914702-Black-Polarized-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley Castel Sunglasses now. Oakley offers a fresh take on the classic rectangular sunglasses in the Castel model. The thick rims are made of O Matter, a lightweight yet durable plastic material that retains its shape and comfort throughout extended wear. The wirecore stems allow these shades to adjust easily for a proper fit. A subtle keyhole at the upper rim draws attention to your eyes while protecting them from glare and wind at high speeds. Take an unconventional approach to old-school style wearing these edgy rectangular Oakley sunglasses crafted with plastic frames. The Oakley brand is universally recognized and is synonymous with innovative, quality craftsmanship. Oakley is a leading name in sports sunglasses because it offers athletes stylish shades that are made with cutting edge design and technology so that it not only looks good but can also withstand harsh environments and truly extreme conditions. Oakley has perfected sporty wrap sunglasses and shields and has modernized interpretations of other classic designs. The Oakley sunglass collection offers a wide variety of frames in an exciting collection of colors and performance-driven lens shading. FramesDirect.com is your online outlet for Oakley Sunglasses. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic Oakley lenses with its sunglasses and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you demand: each Oakley frame comes with original brand markings certified by Oakley itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-castel-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(133, 'Fatheadz Jaxon', 'Fatheadz', 'Sunglasses', 133.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/fatheadz-jaxon-sunglasses-blk-smk.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Fatheadz Jaxon Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Fatheadz frames. Unleash your inner fashionista with a pair of Fatheadz Jaxon sunglasses. These bold rectangular frames feature solid color rims with contrasting temples and tips for an eye-catching look. The durable plastic construction keeps these shades comfortable through long days, while flexible wire cores allow them to adjust easily for a customized fit. Whether you\'re protecting yourself from glare or the sun, Fatheadz sunglasses do it in style. You’ll find the modern styling and the classic edge you prefer within the Fatheadz eyewear collection, including sporty wraparound frames, classic wayfarers, and sleek metal frames, in contemporary full-rim and semi-rimless styles. Fatheadz eyewear is designed to provide grip and comfort specifically for the man with a large or wide head—these frames feature longer temple arms and wider bridge and lens widths so they don’t slip, slide, or pinch.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/fatheadz-jaxon-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(134, 'Polo PH4188', 'Polo', 'Sunglasses', 176.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Polo-Ralph-Lauren-PH4188-Dark-Havana-500373-Brown-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Polo PH4188 Sunglasses now. Unmatched attention to detail and exacting production standards result in designer frames that are beautiful and comfortable to wear, and that last through weekday and weekend living. Explore our line of Polo eyewear for men, women, and kids featuring stylish frames in rectangular, oval, and square shapes to suit your preferred style. Cat-eye frames in flirty hues make a charming accessory, while round tortoiseshell glasses lend a dapper touch.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/polo-ph4188-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(135, 'Ray-Ban RB3675', 'Ray-Ban', 'Sunglasses', 194.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB3675-001-51-Gold-Brown-a.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB3675 Sunglasses now. Reinvent vintage style with a pair of Ray-Ban RB3675 aviator sunglasses for men. The classic aviator silhouette is timeless, and these shades are crafted in materials that make them both lightweight and strong. The metal rims come coated with corrosion-resistant coating, while the metal corewire temples feature comfort-coated tips. For sunglasses that stand up to life’s demands, opt for the aviator from Ray-Ban. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb3675-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(136, 'Oakley Sliver Edge', 'Oakley', 'Sunglasses', 155.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Sliver-Edge-Matte-Black-941301-Prizm-Grey-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Sliver-Edge-Matte-Black-Ink-941302-Prizm-Ruby-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Sliver-Edge-Polished-Black-941304-Prizm-Black-Polarized-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Sliver-Edge-Steel-941306-Prizm-Sapphire-Polarized-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley Sliver Edge Sunglasses now. Update your look with Oakley Sliver Edge sunglasses. The sporty, high-wrap design offers maximum coverage, and Oakley\'s Three-Point Fit eliminates pressure points as it achieves precise visual alignment. The Silver Edge’s semi-rimless frames are comfortable and sturdy, thanks to lightweight and stress-resistant O Matter. Count on these updated Sliver sunglasses for a timeless, sleek look wperfect for medium and large faces. The Oakley brand is universally recognized and is synonymous with innovative, quality craftsmanship. Oakley is a leading name in sports sunglasses because it offers athletes stylish shades that are made with cutting edge design and technology so that it not only looks good but can also withstand harsh environments and truly extreme conditions. Oakley has perfected sporty wrap sunglasses and shields and has modernized interpretations of other classic designs. The Oakley sunglass collection offers a wide variety of frames in an exciting collection of colors and performance-driven lens shading. FramesDirect.com is your online outlet for Oakley Sunglasses. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic Oakley lenses with its sunglasses and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you demand: each Oakley frame comes with original brand markings certified by Oakley itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-sliver-edge-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(137, 'Black Flys Kissy Fly', 'Black Flys', 'Sunglasses', 70.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/black-flys-sunglasses-kissy-shiny-black-smoke-grad.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/black-flys-sunglasses-kissy-shiny-black-smoke.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/black-flys-sunglasses-kissy-shiny-black-smoke-pol.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/black-flys-sunglasses-kissy-red-black-smoke-grad.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/BLACK-FLYS-sun-KISSY-FLY-shiny-black-pink-smoke-polarized-lens.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/BLACK-FLYS-sun-KISSY-FLY-shiny-black-pink-smoke-gradient-lens.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-KISSY-FLY-shiny-black-pink-smoke-lens.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-KISSY-FLY-shiny-tortoise-brown-polarized-lens.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-KISSY-FLY-shiny-tortoise-brown-lens.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-KISSY-FLY-shiny-tortoise-brown-gradient-lens.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Black Flys Kissy Fly Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Black Flys frames. The Black Flys Kissy Fly sunglasses are a fun, youthful way to protect your eyes from the sun. These square frames are made in lightweight, durable plastic that’s strong enough to keep up on your sunny days. The thin temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears. Enjoy an urban vibe with old school cool when you opt for these Kissy Fly sunglasses from Black Flys.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/black-flys-kissy-fly-sunglasses', NULL, NULL);
