(138, 'Ray-Ban RB4194', 'Ray-Ban', 'Sunglasses', 160.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ray-ban-sun-RB4194-601.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ray-ban-sun-RB4194-710-83.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ray-ban-sun-RB4194-710-85.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ray-ban-sun-RB4194-601-9A.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB4194 Sunglasses now. Sport a classic look with modern flair when you wear the Ray-Ban RB4194 sunglasses. The square rims are bold and expressive, while the slim wayfarer frames exude sophistication. Crafted in lightweight plastic, these unisex shades are durable enough to stand up to regular wear. Their sturdy double bridges provide added stability behind the ears for increased comfort and performance. For an aesthetic that balances vintage styling with contemporary design elements, opt for these timeless square sunglasses from Ray-Ban. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb4194-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(139, 'Kate Spade Avaline 2/S', 'Kate Spade', 'Sunglasses', 180.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Kate-Spade-sunglasses-Avaline-2-S-006JNQ.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Kate Spade Avaline 2/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Kate Spade frames. Take your fashion to the next level with Kate Spade\'s Avaline 2/S sunglasses. Their aviator silhouette is reimagined with a double band and metal rims that exude dramatic glamour. The robust temples feature a subtle curve inward, and boast the familiar Spade insignia at the ends for added appeal. Constructed from corrosion-resistant metal, these aviator sunglasses are rugged enough to handle all types of sunny weather yet maintain their sophistication over time. The sunglasses and eyeglasses in our Kate Spade collection offer the brand\'s defining mix of colors, patterns, and bold femininity. The Kate Spade eyewear line is perfect for women who appreciate an elegant look with a dash of playfulness. From sunglasses to prescription eyeglasses and sunglasses frames, the Kate Spade collection includes a spectacular array of hues, whimsical patterns, and charming shapes.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/kate-spade-avaline-2-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(140, 'Black Flys F.G. TV', 'Black Flys', 'Sunglasses', 110.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/black-flys-fg-tv-sunglasses-lightbrn-gradient.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Black Flys F.G. TV Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Black Flys frames. With their sporty square shape, Black Flys F.G. TV sunglasses are ideal for women who enjoy an active lifestyle. The lightweight frames are constructed in durable, impact-resistant plastic that retains its shape for lasting beauty even after hours of wear. The legs curve inward to keep the shades from sliding down due to sweat, and feature signature branding near the brow end for added appeal. Show off your fashion sense wearing these fun sunglasses from Black Flys.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/black-flys-f.g.-tv-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(141, 'Hobie Mojo Float', 'Hobie', 'Sunglasses', 109.99, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/hobie-sun-mojo-float-satin-black-gry-cobalt-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/hobie-sun-mojo-float-satin-black-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/hobie-sun-mojo-float-shny-brwn-woodgrain-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/hobie-sun-mojo-float-satin-black-green-mirror-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/hobie-MOJOFLOAT-bo16226.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/hobie-MOJOFLOAT-bo16238.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/EyeKing-Sunglasses-Hobie-MOJO-FLOAT-MOJO-B016268.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Hobie Mojo Float Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Hobie frames. Enjoy long days in the sun wearing the Hobie Mojo Float sunglasses. The rectangular extended-size frames offer a slightly wrapped design for optimal eye protection at the periphery. The shark fin temples add retro-chic interest, and the signature logo at the hinge adds designer appeal. Crafted in TR-90, a durable thermoplastic, these streamlined sports sunglasses are sturdy yet flexible. Head out on the water in these shades and enjoy Hobie TPX floating technology for sunglasses that will not sink.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/hobie-mojo-float-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(142, 'Zeal Optics Tracker', 'Zeal Optics', 'Sunglasses', 159.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-sun-tracker-black-grey.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Zeal Optics Tracker Sunglasses now. Zeal Optics Tracker sunglasses offer a bold, rugged style that\'s ready for adventure. The frames are made from eco-friendly plastic that\'s lightweight and durable, perfect for glasses you\'ll wear every day. The rounded edges and subtly upswept browline add an element of whimsy to these cool shades. Subtle detailing on the lenses adds visual interest without overwhelming your facial features, allowing you to enjoy optimal vision indoors or out in the sun. Explore Zeal Optics and discover striking eyewear offered in classic and contemporary silhouettes, and designed for active wear. Sporty wraparounds and wraparound-inspired rectangles speak to wearers who want a sleek, modern look; those who prefer a more traditional profile will find squares and rounded-edged frames styles. This eyewear comes in an array of colors and patterns to suit a number of tastes; on-trend embellishments like metal accents on the frames, or distinctive cutaways on the temple arms, impart a hint of sophistication to Zeal Optics frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/zeal-optics-tracker-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(143, 'Maui Jim Twin Falls-417', 'Maui Jim', 'Sunglasses', 259.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/maui-jim-sun-twin-falls-417-02J.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Maui Jim Twin Falls-417 Sunglasses now. Discover a new world of color and clarity wearing Maui Jim Twin Falls-417 sunglasses. The rounded edges and low profile of these unisex shades provide an unobtrusive fit under a baseball or wide brim hat, while the high quality plastic provides durability and impact resistance. If you’re ready to take your sunglasses game to the next level, reach for these on point Twin Falls-417 shades by Maui Jim. Maui Jim has led the eyewear industry by design and innovation since 1980, offering eyes everywhere superior protection from the harmful rays of the sun in its popular line of sunglasses. From iconic shades with patented technologies, to readers perfect for sunny-day pastimes, to the impressively stylish and comfortable daily-wear frames in the Optical line, Maui Jim creates men’s and women’s performance eyewear for any scenario. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Maui Jim dealer, selling only 100% authentic Maui Jim sunglasses frames and lenses. Polarized with an anti-reflective coating, Maui Jim lenses reveal the vibrant colors of the world while protecting your eyes from the effects of the sun\'s harsh glare and harmful rays. Satisfaction guaranteed. Additional Information: Maui Lens Colors Information (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/maui-jim-twin-falls-417-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(144, 'Coach HC8374U', 'Coach', 'Sunglasses', 179.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Coach-HC8374U-512013-Sunglasses_030A.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Coach-HC8374U-574774-Sunglasses_030A.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Coach HC8374U Sunglasses now. Reach for a pair of chic and sophisticated sunglasses in the HC8374U from Coach. The designer crafts these frames with high-quality, hypoallergenic plastic that’s lightweight but sturdy enough to stand up to wear after wear. The rims are wide for enhanced protection against glare and wind at high speeds. Subtle details on the curved browline add elegance to these stylish shades. Enjoy impeccable style when you opt for the women\'s HC8374U sunglasses from Coach. Women’s designer eyewear by Coach exudes a distinctive big-city vibe in chic frames that blend modern sophistication with vintage-inspired style. The result is a collection of daring luxury eyewear that complements a wide range of wardrobes. Browse oversized frames in bold colors, or sleek silhouettes in subtle neutral hues. Coach uses modern color palettes in two-tone frames, but also includes the classics, drawing inspiration from vintage eyewear styles in black or tortoiseshell to create elegant frames that appeal to contemporary tastes.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/coach-hc8374u-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(145, 'Oakley M2', 'Oakley', 'Sunglasses', 160.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/oakley-m2-sunglasses-oo9212-01.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/oakley-m2-sunglasses-oo9212-03.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/oakley-m2-sunglasses-oo9212-04.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/oakley-m2-sunglasses-oo9212-07.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley M2 Sunglasses now. The Oakley brand is universally recognized and is synonymous with innovative, quality craftsmanship. Oakley is a leading name in sports sunglasses because it offers athletes stylish shades that are made with cutting edge design and technology so that it not only looks good but can also withstand harsh environments and truly extreme conditions. Oakley has perfected sporty wrap sunglasses and shields and has modernized interpretations of other classic designs. The Oakley sunglass collection offers a wide variety of frames in an exciting collection of colors and performance-driven lens shading. FramesDirect.com is your online outlet for Oakley Sunglasses. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic Oakley lenses with its sunglasses and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you demand: each Oakley frame comes with original brand markings certified by Oakley itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-m2-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(146, 'Ray-Ban RB3387', 'Ray-Ban', 'Sunglasses', 179.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ray-ban-sun-RB3387-003-68.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB3387 Sunglasses now. Reach for a pair of Ray-Ban RB3387 sunglasses and enjoy the benefits of classic styling combined with modern innovation. These aviator-style shades offer robust construction, with metal rims that are strong and long lasting. The lightweight frames come in a corrosion-resistant alloy that’s durable and retains its shape over time, resulting in lasting value you can appreciate every day you wear these cool sunglasses. A double rivet design adds flair at the brow end of the slimline temples, while the base adds a classy finish. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb3387-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
