(164, 'RALPH by Ralph Lauren RA5203', 'RALPH by Ralph Lauren', 'Sunglasses', 127.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ralph-ra5203-sunglasses-109013-54-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ralph-ra5203-sunglasses-109t5-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ralph-by-ralph-lauren-sun-RA5203-1463T5.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ralph-ra5203-sunglasses-146313-angle.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore RALPH by Ralph Lauren RA5203 Sunglasses now. Showcase your fashion-forward style wearing the women’s RALPH by Ralph Lauren RA5203 sunglasses. These cat-eye shades feature sleek, ergonomic frames crafted in lightweight plastic that\'s durable enough to stand up to your busy lifestyle. The wirecore temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and boast an embroidered metallic ‘R’ near the brow end for added appeal. Enjoy effortlessness every day when you reach for these cool sunglasses from Ralph Lauren. Ralph by Ralph Lauren lends compelling drama to the brand’s Ivy League-inspired roots. Discover oversized sunglasses frames, chunky styles, and sleek silhouettes, all with the effortless sophistication perfected by Ralph Lauren. The designer first shared his pioneering style in 1967 with the release of a line of men’s striped ties. They became an immediate hit and Lauren grew his business into a global fashion and lifestyle brand that includes his sunglasses and prescription sunglasses collection.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ralph-by-ralph-lauren-ra5203-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(165, 'RALPH by Ralph Lauren RA5207', 'RALPH by Ralph Lauren', 'Sunglasses', 114.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ralph-by-ralph-lauren-sun-RA5207-150613.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore RALPH by Ralph Lauren RA5207 Sunglasses now. RALPH by Ralph Lauren offers women a classic look in these RA5207 sunglasses. The rounded edges and butterfly silhouette are timeless, while the distinctive split browline adds an edge of drama. Crafted in lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to wear after wear, these shades boast a sturdy core for lasting beauty through years of use. For effortlessness and sophistication wherever you go, reach for these chic sunglasses from Ralph Lauren. Ralph by Ralph Lauren lends compelling drama to the brand’s Ivy League-inspired roots. Discover oversized sunglasses frames, chunky styles, and sleek silhouettes, all with the effortless sophistication perfected by Ralph Lauren. The designer first shared his pioneering style in 1967 with the release of a line of men’s striped ties. They became an immediate hit and Lauren grew his business into a global fashion and lifestyle brand that includes his sunglasses and prescription sunglasses collection.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ralph-by-ralph-lauren-ra5207-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(166, 'Oakley Cohort', 'Oakley', 'Sunglasses', 163.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Cohort-Sepia-930102-Dark-Brown-Gradient-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Cohort-Amethyst-930103-G40-Black-Gradient-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/oakley-cohort-18.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Cohort-Polished-Black-930104-Grey-Gradient-Polarized-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Cohort-Crystal-Black-930116-Prizm-Black-Polarized-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley Cohort Sunglasses now. Oakley Cohort sunglasses for women boast a sporty rectangular silhouette with an unmistakable flair for unconventional style. These shades offer impact protection against wind and glare, and their lightweight O-Matter plastic provides durability and flexibility. The skull temples curve inward to keep the glasses from slipping during high activity. A keyhole at the upper rims provide a point of connection to other Oakley accessories like hats, bags, or jackets, a subtle nod to the brand\'s renowned adventurous spirit. The Oakley brand is universally recognized and is synonymous with innovative, quality craftsmanship. Oakley is a leading name in sports sunglasses because it offers athletes stylish shades that are made with cutting edge design and technology so that it not only looks good but can also withstand harsh environments and truly extreme conditions. Oakley has perfected sporty wrap sunglasses and shields and has modernized interpretations of other classic designs. The Oakley sunglass collection offers a wide variety of frames in an exciting collection of colors and performance-driven lens shading. FramesDirect.com is your online outlet for Oakley Sunglasses. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic Oakley lenses with its sunglasses and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you demand: each Oakley frame comes with original brand markings certified by Oakley itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-cohort-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(167, 'Coach HC7064', 'Coach', 'Sunglasses', 203.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/coach-sun-HC7064-926513.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Coach HC7064 Sunglasses now. Reach for a pair of Coach HC7064 sunglasses and enjoy the aviator style at its finest. These shades boast metal rims that are strong, lightweight, and corrosion-resistant, all great qualities in eye protection. The skull temples curve inward gently to keep the glasses from slipping during activity. These aviator sunglasses offer an elevated look that’s still understated enough for everyday wear. Women’s designer eyewear by Coach exudes a distinctive big-city vibe in chic frames that blend modern sophistication with vintage-inspired style. The result is a collection of daring luxury eyewear that complements a wide range of wardrobes. Browse oversized frames in bold colors, or sleek silhouettes in subtle neutral hues. Coach uses modern color palettes in two-tone frames, but also includes the classics, drawing inspiration from vintage eyewear styles in black or tortoiseshell to create elegant frames that appeal to contemporary tastes.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/coach-hc7064-sunglasses', NULL, NULL);
