(168, 'Persol PO3108S', 'Persol', 'Sunglasses', 486.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/persol-sun-po3108s-960s3-49-angle.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Persol PO3108S Sunglasses now. Persol PO3108S sunglasses for men boast a timeless silhouette that’s fresh and fashionable. The oval frames are crafted in hypoallergenic plastic that\'s lightweight, durable, and resistant to corrosion, ideal qualities in shades you wear often. The slim temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for added stability behind the ears. These cool sunglasses for men offer an elegant and stylish appeal. Persol eyewear is among the most well respected and distinguished eyewear brands in the world. Each attractive and comfortable frame is expertly hand crafted in Lauriano, Italy. Persol eyewear is made of only the highest quality materials. Persol\'s Meflecto system gives each Persol frame a patented \"flexible stem\" that makes Persol glasses frames among the most comfortable on the market. Persol\'s ultra-stylish frames and unparalleled craftsmanship make Persol popular with musicians, actors, and cultural icons. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Persol retailer, selling only 100% authentic Persol eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you love: each Persol frame comes with original brand markings certified by Persol itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/persol-po3108s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(169, 'Coach HC7059', 'Coach', 'Sunglasses', 203.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/coach-hc7059-sunglasses-924890-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/coach-sun-HC7059-92496E.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Coach HC7059 Sunglasses now. Reach for a pair of Coach HC7059 sunglasses and enjoy the aviator look with designer flair. The metal rims are hypoallergenic, lightweight, and durable. A coated rubberized finish on the inner sides helps keep these shades in place even when they\'re worn over extended periods. Crafted by hand in luxurious leathers, the frames come with an engraved metallic band at their brow end that adds elegance to their sporty silhouette. Women’s designer eyewear by Coach exudes a distinctive big-city vibe in chic frames that blend modern sophistication with vintage-inspired style. The result is a collection of daring luxury eyewear that complements a wide range of wardrobes. Browse oversized frames in bold colors, or sleek silhouettes in subtle neutral hues. Coach uses modern color palettes in two-tone frames, but also includes the classics, drawing inspiration from vintage eyewear styles in black or tortoiseshell to create elegant frames that appeal to contemporary tastes.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/coach-hc7059-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(170, 'Saint Laurent SL 28', 'Saint Laurent', 'Sunglasses', 495.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Saint-Laurent-SL-28-Brown-Light-047-Brown-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Saint-Laurent-SL-28-Tortoise-Light-048-Brown-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Saint Laurent SL 28 Sunglasses now. The Saint Laurent eyewear collection places minimalist and convention-dodging glasses designs side by side. This acclaimed luxury fashion house infuses each piece with the glamour of Paris, and Saint Laurent sunglasses and eyeglasses for men and women are no exception.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/saint-laurent-sl-28-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(171, 'Oakley M2 XL', 'Oakley', 'Sunglasses', 184.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-M2-Framea-XL-Polished-Black-934308-Prizm-Road-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/oakley-sunglasses-m2-frame-xl-OO9343-19.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/oakley-sun-m2-frame-xl-OO9343-21.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-M2-Framea-XL-Polished-Black-934301-Grey-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-M2-Framea-XL-Polished-White-934305-Fire-Iridium-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley M2 XL Sunglasses now. Unleash your inner athlete with a pair of Oakley M2 XL sunglasses. These semi-rimless shades provide an unrestricted field of vision, so you can keep an eye on what\'s going on around you. The wrap design provides optimal protection against glare and wind at high speeds, while the lightweight O Matter plastic frame material keeps these shades comfortable through long days in the sun. For sporty sunglasses that live up to Oakley\'s reputation for innovation and quality, reach for these M2 XLs. The Oakley brand is universally recognized and is synonymous with innovative, quality craftsmanship. Oakley is a leading name in sports sunglasses because it offers athletes stylish shades that are made with cutting edge design and technology so that it not only looks good but can also withstand harsh environments and truly extreme conditions. Oakley has perfected sporty wrap sunglasses and shields and has modernized interpretations of other classic designs. The Oakley sunglass collection offers a wide variety of frames in an exciting collection of colors and performance-driven lens shading. FramesDirect.com is your online outlet for Oakley Sunglasses. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic Oakley lenses with its sunglasses and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you demand: each Oakley frame comes with original brand markings certified by Oakley itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-m2-xl-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(172, 'Gucci GG0024S', 'Gucci', 'Sunglasses', 370.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/gucci-sunglasses-GG0024S-002.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Gucci GG0024S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Gucci frames. Gucci adds a touch of old-school glamour to contemporary styling in these GG0024S sunglasses for women. The rounded edges and moderate lens width give these shades an elegant, classic look. Crafted in lightweight and durable plastic, the frames are comfortable to wear, yet sturdy enough to last through years of sunny days. Coated with anti-slip elements at the ends of the slim arms, these sunglasses stay put when you do, even on a boat or other vessel on water. Founded in Florence, Italy, in 1921, Gucci is one of the world\'s leading luxury brands. Following the House\'s centenary, Gucci forges ahead into the next hundred years, continuing to redefine luxury while celebrating the creativity, Italian craftsmanship, and innovation at the core of its values. Gucci is part of the global luxury group Kering, which manages the development of a series of renowned Houses in fashion, leather goods, jewelry, and eyewear. Discover more about Gucci at www.gucci.com . The latest range of sunglasses and optical frames embodies Gucci\'s signature designs. Drawing inspiration from the archive of the House, the eyewear collection combines emblematic codes with new details in an unexpected selection of shapes and styles.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/gucci-gg0024s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(173, 'Zeal Optics Isabelle', 'Zeal Optics', 'Sunglasses', 159.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-sunglasses-isabelle-lilac-11536.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Zeal Optics Isabelle Sunglasses now. Zeal Optics Isabelle sunglasses offer a fun, youthful look that’s all your own. These rounded frames are crafted in lightweight, durable plastic that\'s sturdy enough to stand up to your busy lifestyle. The slim arms curve inward gently for a secure fit behind the ears, while adding an element of style. Enjoy sunny days in these cool and comfortable Isabelle sunglasses from Zeal Optics. Explore Zeal Optics and discover striking eyewear offered in classic and contemporary silhouettes, and designed for active wear. Sporty wraparounds and wraparound-inspired rectangles speak to wearers who want a sleek, modern look; those who prefer a more traditional profile will find squares and rounded-edged frames styles. This eyewear comes in an array of colors and patterns to suit a number of tastes; on-trend embellishments like metal accents on the frames, or distinctive cutaways on the temple arms, impart a hint of sophistication to Zeal Optics frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/zeal-optics-isabelle-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(174, 'Oakley Goggles Line Miner Snow', 'Oakley Goggles', 'Sunglasses', 176.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/oakley-goggles-lineminer-snow-OO7070-01.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Line-Minera-L-Matte-Black-707002-Prizm-Torch-Iridium-Goggles.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Line-Minera-L-Matte-Black-707004-Prizm-Sapphire-Iridium-Goggles.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/oakley-goggles-line-miner-oo7070-57.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Line-Minera-L-Factory-Pilot-Factory-Pilot-Black-707065-Prizm-Sapphire-Iridium-Goggles.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley Goggles Line Miner Snow Sunglasses now. Oakley Goggles Line Miner Snow sunglasses offer unbeatable protection against glare and wind. These comfortable goggles wrap around the sides of your head to block wind at the eye sockets and reduce glare from overhead lights. Lightweight O-Matter plastic provides durability, flexibility, and impact resistance in these unisex sunglasses. The single-lens wraparound design offers a wider field of view than conventional frames with two lenses do. For superior optics in high-performance sport shades, opt for Oakley Goggles Line Miner Snow sunglasses. The Oakley brand is universally recognized and is synonymous with innovative, quality craftsmanship. Oakley is a leading name in sports sunglasses & goggles because it offers athletes stylish shades that are made with cutting edge design and technology so that it not only looks good but can also withstand harsh environments and truly extreme conditions. Oakley has perfected sporty wrap sunglasses, goggles, and shields and has modernized interpretations of other classic designs. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic Oakley Goggles and goggle lenses. Shop confidently for the quality sports eyewear you demand: each Oakley goggle comes with original brand markings and Oakley authentic lenses, both certified by Oakley itself. Additional Information: Oakley Lens Color Guide (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-goggles-line-miner-snow-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(175, 'Zeal Optics Capitol', 'Zeal Optics', 'Sunglasses', 159.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-sunglasses-capitol-11376.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-sunglasses-capitol-11317.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Zeal Optics Capitol Sunglasses now. Zeal Optics offers a bold, eco-friendly take on the classic square sunglasses in the Capitol. The frames are made from plastic that’s lightweight and durable, with a double browline for an unmistakable throwback feel. These shades come with coated lens treatments to prevent glare and smudges, so you can see clearly no matter where your adventure takes you. Explore Zeal Optics and discover striking eyewear offered in classic and contemporary silhouettes, and designed for active wear. Sporty wraparounds and wraparound-inspired rectangles speak to wearers who want a sleek, modern look; those who prefer a more traditional profile will find squares and rounded-edged frames styles. This eyewear comes in an array of colors and patterns to suit a number of tastes; on-trend embellishments like metal accents on the frames, or distinctive cutaways on the temple arms, impart a hint of sophistication to Zeal Optics frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/zeal-optics-capitol-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(176, 'Original Penguin The Merlin Sun', 'Original Penguin', 'Sunglasses', 228.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/original-peng-sunglasses-the-merlin-sun-denim-tort.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Original Penguin The Merlin Sun Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Original Penguin frames. The Merlin Sun shades from Original Penguin bring classic style to modern sunglasses. These sunnies are part of the series The Merlin Sun, featuring rectangular frames made from lightweight, durable plastic that’s designed to last. The skull temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and the sleek silhouette and distinctive details make them an ideal accessory on sunny days outdoors or when you\'re traveling abroad. Drawing from the eyewear fashion of the 1950s, our collection of Original Penguin showcases timeless silhouettes in full-rim and semi-rimless styles, paired with contemporary details. Clubmaster-inspired frames are the focus, in rounded-edge and square variations. Traditional round and aviator shapes are represented for a classically cool profile; modern ovals and rectangles present a more tailored look. This designer eyewear offers frames styles to suit a number of tastes, in shapes made to complement any face.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/original-penguin-the-merlin-sun-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(177, 'Gucci GG0010S', 'Gucci', 'Sunglasses', 465.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/gucci-gg0010s-sunglasses-001-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/gucci-sunglasses-GG0010S-003.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/gucci-sunglasses-GG0010S-004.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Gucci GG0010S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Gucci frames. Gear up for an active day with a pair of Gucci GG0010S sunglasses. These bold rectangular shades are crafted in hypoallergenic plastic that’s lightweight and durable, resulting in comfortable sunglasses you can wear all day long. The wirecore temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and feature a neat finish near the brow end for designer appeal. For chic style wherever you go, reach for these cool shades from Gucci. Founded in Florence, Italy, in 1921, Gucci is one of the world\'s leading luxury brands. Following the House\'s centenary, Gucci forges ahead into the next hundred years, continuing to redefine luxury while celebrating the creativity, Italian craftsmanship, and innovation at the core of its values. Gucci is part of the global luxury group Kering, which manages the development of a series of renowned Houses in fashion, leather goods, jewelry, and eyewear. Discover more about Gucci at www.gucci.com . The latest range of sunglasses and optical frames embodies Gucci\'s signature designs. Drawing inspiration from the archive of the House, the eyewear collection combines emblematic codes with new details in an unexpected selection of shapes and styles.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/gucci-gg0010s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(178, 'Vera Bradley Felicity', 'Vera Bradley', 'Sunglasses', 183.89, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/verawang-FELICITY-rosetoile.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Vera Bradley Felicity Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Vera Bradley frames. The women’s Vera Bradley Felicity aviator-style sunglasses boast a timeless look with a splash of vibrant color. The metal frames are strong and lightweight, with wirecore rims for flexibility. The skull temples curve inward gently to ensure stability behind the ears. A double rivet detail at each end adds elegance to these chic aviator sunglasses. For sunny days on the beach or in town, reach for these cool Vera Bradley Felicity shades.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/vera-bradley-felicity-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(179, 'Gucci GG0022S', 'Gucci', 'Sunglasses', 370.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/gucci-sunglasses-GG0022S-001.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/gucci-sunglasses-GG0022S-003.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Gucci GG0022S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Gucci frames. The GG0022S from Gucci are a pair of sunglasses designed with the fashion-savvy wearer in mind. The square rims are crafted in hypoallergenic plastic that’s lightweight, durable, and resistant to corrosion, heat, and sunlight. The slim temples feature coated tips for comfort behind the ears. Make a statement wearing these chic shades from Gucci. Founded in Florence, Italy, in 1921, Gucci is one of the world\'s leading luxury brands. Following the House\'s centenary, Gucci forges ahead into the next hundred years, continuing to redefine luxury while celebrating the creativity, Italian craftsmanship, and innovation at the core of its values. Gucci is part of the global luxury group Kering, which manages the development of a series of renowned Houses in fashion, leather goods, jewelry, and eyewear. Discover more about Gucci at www.gucci.com . The latest range of sunglasses and optical frames embodies Gucci\'s signature designs. Drawing inspiration from the archive of the House, the eyewear collection combines emblematic codes with new details in an unexpected selection of shapes and styles.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/gucci-gg0022s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
