(203, 'Michael Kors MK2024', 'Michael Kors', 'Sunglasses', 111.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/michael-kors-sun-MK2024-316011.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/michael-kors-sun-MK2024-310613.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/michael-kors-sun-MK2024-316213.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Michael Kors MK2024 Sunglasses now. Michael Kors serves up a bold look in these MK2024 sunglasses. The oversized frames are made from hypoallergenic, lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to your busy lifestyle. The slim temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for stability behind the ears. A metallic Michael Kors nameplate on the brow end adds designer appeal. For chic style with a touch of glamour, opt for these oversize sunglasses from Michael Kors. The sophisticated Michael Kors eyewear collection presents classic elegance to suit a variety of tastes. Frames by this celebrated designer exude a timeless appeal to complement modern wardrobes, but plenty of daring, trendsetting styles appear throughout the collection. From the modern, clean eyeglasses to the chic, wearable outerwear parading down the runways, Michael Kors continues to be a popular choice with those seeking accessible luxury.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/michael-kors-mk2024-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(204, 'Maui Jim Koko Head-737', 'Maui Jim', 'Sunglasses', 289.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/maui-jim-sunglasses-koko-head-h737-10m.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Maui Jim Koko Head-737 Sunglasses now. Add a touch of luxury to your outdoor look with Maui Jim Koko Head-737 sunglasses. These unisex shades feature rounded edges and gently swept-back angles that create an elegant, sophisticated silhouette. A lightweight plastic frame keeps these glasses comfortable even on long days outdoors, yet they’re sturdy enough to stand up to heavy use. The skull temples curve inward for stability behind the ears and designer appeal. For timeless style in high quality frames, reach for these Maui Jim sunglasses. Maui Jim has led the eyewear industry by design and innovation since 1980, offering eyes everywhere superior protection from the harmful rays of the sun in its popular line of sunglasses. From iconic shades with patented technologies, to readers perfect for sunny-day pastimes, to the impressively stylish and comfortable daily-wear frames in the Optical line, Maui Jim creates men’s and women’s performance eyewear for any scenario. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Maui Jim dealer, selling only 100% authentic Maui Jim sunglasses frames and lenses. Polarized with an anti-reflective coating, Maui Jim lenses reveal the vibrant colors of the world while protecting your eyes from the effects of the sun\'s harsh glare and harmful rays. Satisfaction guaranteed. Additional Information: Maui Lens Colors Information (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/maui-jim-koko-head-737-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
