(206, 'Ray-Ban RB4259', 'Ray-Ban', 'Sunglasses', 178.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ray-ban-sun-RB4259-601-71.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ray-ban-sun-RB4259-710-73.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ray-ban-sun-RB4259-731-E8.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB4259-Beige-616613-Brown-Dark-Brown-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB4259 Sunglasses now. These Ray-Ban RB4259 sunglasses offer a bold, distinctive look. The thick oval rims are made in hypoallergenic plastic that’s lightweight but sturdy enough to keep up on your sunny days. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears and boast an attractive design near the brow end. Enjoy head-turning style when you step out in these cool shades from Ray-Ban. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb4259-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(207, 'Michael Kors MK2023', 'Michael Kors', 'Sunglasses', 154.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/michael-kors-sun-MK2023-3106T5.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Michael Kors MK2023 Sunglasses now. Discover a new look wearing the Michael Kors MK2023 sunglasses. These round frames are made from strong and lustrous plastic that’s lightweight and durable, resulting in glasses you can wear all day long. The slim temples curve inward softly for stability behind the ears, with a keyhole at each temple showcasing your inner fashionista. Show off your style when you slip on these cool shades from Michael Kors. The sophisticated Michael Kors eyewear collection presents classic elegance to suit a variety of tastes. Frames by this celebrated designer exude a timeless appeal to complement modern wardrobes, but plenty of daring, trendsetting styles appear throughout the collection. From the modern, clean eyeglasses to the chic, wearable outerwear parading down the runways, Michael Kors continues to be a popular choice with those seeking accessible luxury.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/michael-kors-mk2023-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(208, 'Oakley SI Tombstone Spoil', 'Oakley', 'Sunglasses', 212.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/oakley-sunglasses-tombstone-spoil-OO9328-04.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/oakley-sunglasses-tombstone-spoil-OO9328-05.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley SI Tombstone Spoil Sunglasses now. The Oakley SI Tombstone Spoil sunglasses appeal to the marksman who values eye safety, comfort, and performance. The standard-issue frames boast rimless, shield-style lenses for a wide field of view and protection from dirt, dust, and debris at the periphery. The Switchlock Quick Lens Exchange allows you to easily change between tints and coatings based on light conditions. Crafted in patented O Matter, these frames meet or exceed the ANSI standards for high-velocity, high-mass impact resistance. With their sculpted temples, the SI Tombstone Spoil sunglasses will reliably stay in place during all your high-octane activities. The Oakley brand is universally recognized and is synonymous with innovative, quality craftsmanship. Oakley is a leading name in sports sunglasses because it offers athletes stylish shades that are made with cutting edge design and technology so that it not only looks good but can also withstand harsh environments and truly extreme conditions. Oakley has perfected sporty wrap sunglasses and shields and has modernized interpretations of other classic designs. The Oakley sunglass collection offers a wide variety of frames in an exciting collection of colors and performance-driven lens shading. FramesDirect.com is your online outlet for Oakley Sunglasses. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic Oakley lenses with its sunglasses and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you demand: each Oakley frame comes with original brand markings certified by Oakley itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-si-tombstone-spoil-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(209, 'Revo Traverse (RE 1036)', 'Revo', 'Sunglasses', 299.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/revo-sun-traverse-black-blu-water.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/revo-sunglasses-traverse-white-blue-water.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Revo Traverse (RE 1036) Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Revo frames. Revo Traverse (RE 1036) sunglasses have a classic oval silhouette with a sporty edge. The lightweight, corrosion-resistant plastic frames make them comfortable to wear and they won\'t melt if they come into contact with snow or water. The wire cores of the slimline temples allow you to adjust the fit for optimal visibility. Enjoy designer styling wherever you go wearing these cool Revo Traverse sunglasses.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/revo-traverse-re-1036-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(210, 'Ray-Ban RB4258', 'Ray-Ban', 'Sunglasses', 178.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB4258-601-71-Black-Green-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB4258-710-73-Havana-Dark-Brown-a.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB4258 Sunglasses now. Step out in classic style wearing Ray-Ban RB4258 sunglasses. These unisex sunglasses are made from hypoallergenic, lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to keep up on your busiest days. The wirecore temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears. Enjoy timeless aesthetic with modern performance when you opt for these classic rectangular sunglasses. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb4258-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
