(213, 'Dragon DR Count H20', 'Dragon', 'Sunglasses', 219.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/dragon-sunglasses-dr-count-h20-matte-green-ion.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/dragon-sunglasses-dr-count-h20-matte-sky-blue.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Dragon DR Count H20 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Dragon frames. Dragon DR Count H20 sunglasses offer a bold, retro-inspired look. The rectangular frames are made in lightweight, impact-resistant plastic that’s durable enough to last through your longest days on the water. The thick rims feature chunky brows for an imposing presence under the sunshine. If you\'re looking for classic shades with contemporary styling, reach for these from Dragon.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/dragon-dr-count-h20-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(214, 'Dragon DR COUNT LL COUNT', 'Dragon', 'Sunglasses', 140.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/dragon-sunglasses-dr512s-count-matte-black.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/dragon-sunglasses-dr512s-count-matte-black-blue.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Dragon DR COUNT LL COUNT Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Dragon frames. These DR COUNT LL COUNT sunglasses from Dragon boast a sporty, edgy look. The rectangular rims are made in lightweight, durable plastic that’s strong enough to keep up on your busiest days. The slim temples grow slightly at the tips for stability behind the ears, and feature a design near the brow end for added appeal. With their unique lens design these Dragon sunglasses offer optimal protection against glare while you\'re on the water or land, wherever adventure takes you.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/dragon-dr512s-count-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
