(219, 'Vera Bradley Charlene', 'Vera Bradley', 'Sunglasses', 160.89, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/vera-bradley-charlene-sunglasses-bhp.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Vera Bradley Charlene Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Vera Bradley frames. Kick back and relax in the Vera Bradley Charlene sunglasses. These square shades are made from a lightweight, durable plastic that’s comfortable to wear. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and boast added appeal. With chic styling and quality construction throughout, these Charlene sunglasses from Vera Bradley are sure to become one of your go-to pairs.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/vera-bradley-charlene-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(220, 'Ray-Ban RB3447N', 'Ray-Ban', 'Sunglasses', 218.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB3447N-Arista-Gold-001-Z2-Brown-Suglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Round-Flat-Lenses-001-Gold-Green-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Round-Flat-Lenses-001-3F-Gold-Blue-Gradient-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Round-Flat-Lenses-002-71-Black-Grey-Gradient-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Round-Flat-Lenses-004-51-Gunmetal-Brown-Gradient-a.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB3447N Sunglasses now. Reinvent your look with a pair of Ray-Ban RB3447N sunglasses for men. The round frames are made in a lightweight, corrosion-resistant metal that retains its shape through extended wear. The slim temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for stability behind the ears. Make an impression wherever you go wearing these timeless round Ray-Ban sunglasses for men. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb3447n-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(221, 'Vera Bradley Liz', 'Vera Bradley', 'Sunglasses', 183.89, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Vera-Bradley-sun-LIZ-garden.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Vera Bradley Liz Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Vera Bradley frames. These Liz sunglasses from Vera Bradley speak to the woman who appreciates timeless fashion. The rounded frames are crafted in plastic that’s lightweight, durable, and resistant to heat and cold. The slim temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, with additional appeal. Enjoy designer styling wherever you go wearing these cool Liz sunglasses from Vera Bradley.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/vera-bradley-liz-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(222, 'Maui Jim Barrier Reef-792', 'Maui Jim', 'Sunglasses', 289.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/maui-jim-sunglasses-barrier-reef-b792-06c.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Maui Jim Barrier Reef-792 Sunglasses now. Escape the ordinary with a pair of Maui Jim Barrier Reef-792 sunglasses. These unisex wrap around shades feature an unusual shape that’s both sporty and stylish. The lightweight plastic rims are durable, yet flexible enough to keep their shape over time. For comfort as well as style, choose these unique shades from Maui Jim. Maui Jim has led the eyewear industry by design and innovation since 1980, offering eyes everywhere superior protection from the harmful rays of the sun in its popular line of sunglasses. From iconic shades with patented technologies, to readers perfect for sunny-day pastimes, to the impressively stylish and comfortable daily-wear frames in the Optical line, Maui Jim creates men’s and women’s performance eyewear for any scenario. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Maui Jim dealer, selling only 100% authentic Maui Jim sunglasses frames and lenses. Polarized with an anti-reflective coating, Maui Jim lenses reveal the vibrant colors of the world while protecting your eyes from the effects of the sun\'s harsh glare and harmful rays. Satisfaction guaranteed. Additional Information: Maui Lens Colors Information (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/maui-jim-barrier-reef-792-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(223, 'Gucci GG0341S', 'Gucci', 'Sunglasses', 525.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Gucci-GG0341S-002-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/gucci-sunglasses-GG0341S-003.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Gucci GG0341S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Gucci frames. These men’s GG0341S sunglasses from Gucci are a perfect example of classic and stylish design. The rectangular frames are made in lightweight, lustrous plastic that\'s durable enough to stand up to your busy lifestyle. The slim temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, offering a clean look with timeless style. Enjoy these cool shades by Gucci. Founded in Florence, Italy, in 1921, Gucci is one of the world\'s leading luxury brands. Following the House\'s centenary, Gucci forges ahead into the next hundred years, continuing to redefine luxury while celebrating the creativity, Italian craftsmanship, and innovation at the core of its values. Gucci is part of the global luxury group Kering, which manages the development of a series of renowned Houses in fashion, leather goods, jewelry, and eyewear. Discover more about Gucci at www.gucci.com . The latest range of sunglasses and optical frames embodies Gucci\'s signature designs. Drawing inspiration from the archive of the House, the eyewear collection combines emblematic codes with new details in an unexpected selection of shapes and styles.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/gucci-gg0341s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(224, 'Ray-Ban RB3548N Hexagonal Collection', 'Ray-Ban', 'Sunglasses', 191.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Hexagonal-Flat-Lenses-001-Gold-Green-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Hexagonal-Flat-Lenses-002-58-Black-Green-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Hexagonal-Flat-Lenses-001-58-Gold-Green-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Hexagonal-Flat-Lenses-91233M-Gold-Blue-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Hexagonal-Flat-Lenses-001-30-Gold-Silver-Flash-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Hexagonal-Flat-Lenses-001-57-Gold-Brown-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Hexagonal-Flat-Lenses-9069A5-Copper-Brown-Gradient-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Hexagonal-Flat-Lenses-912443-Gold-Brown-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Hexagonal-Flat-Lenses-004-71-Gunmetal-Grey-Gradient-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Hexagonal-Flat-Lenses-001-R5-Gold-Blue-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Hexagonal-Flat-Lenses-9202AF-Rose-Gold-Violet-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Hexagonal-Flat-Lenses-Arista-Gold-001-Z2-Bronze-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Hexagonal-Flat-Lenses-Silver-003-02-Blue-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB3548N Hexagonal Collection Sunglasses now. Step outside your comfort zone and stand out from the crowd when you wear the Ray-Ban RB3548N Hexagonal Collection sunglasses. The square rims are unusual for a pair of shades, but their hexagonal centerpieces add extra visual interest. Crafted in lightweight metal, these frames are strong and sturdy, ready to keep up on your busiest days. A keyhole at the upper rims draws attention to your eyes, while coated temple tips ensure comfort behind the ears. With timeless good looks and modern styling cues, these Ray-Ban sunglasses make an enduring addition to your accessory collection. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb3548n-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(225, 'Carrera CA5046/S', 'Carrera', 'Sunglasses', 190.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/F-CA5046S0807QT.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Carrera CA5046/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Carrera frames. Carrera takes a fashion-forward step to combine sporty design with an adventurous style in these CA5046/S sunglasses. The round frames are made in a lightweight material that’s plenty sturdy for an active lifestyle. A pronounced double bridge lends a retro aesthetic. The inner temples are textured over the ears for a non-slip grip, and come with signature branding near the brow end for added appeal. Flexible spring hinges retain their initial balance and adjustment for a secure fit, and thoughtfully engineered side shields protect your eyes in the periphery. Indulge in these audacious sunglasses by Carrera if you\'re ready to take the next step on your fashion journey. Carrera eyewear for men, women, and children is easily identifiable by its bold sunglass silhouettes and streamlined eyeglass designs; this label has been a steadfast name in eyewear since 1956, first producing protective sports goggles.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/carrera-ca5046-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(226, 'Persol PO3210S', 'Persol', 'Sunglasses', 422.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/persol-sun-PO3210S-24-31.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/persol-sun-PO3210S-95-31.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/persol-sun-PO3210S-24-57.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Persol PO3210S Sunglasses now. The Persol PO3210S sunglasses for men exude a timeless look that’s both sophisticated and practical. The oval frames offer enhanced peripheral vision, making these shades ideal for active wearers. Crafted in lightweight plastic, the frames are durable enough to stand up to heavy use, yet gentle on the skin. The wirecore temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, adding appeal to these cool shades from Persol. Persol eyewear is among the most well respected and distinguished eyewear brands in the world. Each attractive and comfortable frame is expertly hand crafted in Lauriano, Italy. Persol eyewear is made of only the highest quality materials. Persol\'s Meflecto system gives each Persol frame a patented \"flexible stem\" that makes Persol glasses frames among the most comfortable on the market. Persol\'s ultra-stylish frames and unparalleled craftsmanship make Persol popular with musicians, actors, and cultural icons. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Persol retailer, selling only 100% authentic Persol eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you love: each Persol frame comes with original brand markings certified by Persol itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/persol-po3210s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(227, 'Dolce & Gabbana DG4338F - Alternate Fit', 'Dolce & Gabbana', 'Sunglasses', 460.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/dolce-gabbana-sun-DG4338F-501-87.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Dolce & Gabbana DG4338F - Alternate Fit Sunglasses now. The Dolce & Gabbana DG4338F - Alternate Fit sunglasses offer a fresh, modern interpretation of the classic square silhouette. The bold rims are crafted in hypoallergenic plastic for comfort and durability, with a subtle saddlebridge to keep them stable on low or high cheekbones. The slim temples feature wide tips for comfort behind the ears and come with coated socks over the ends for added grip when you\'re active. A metallic D&G emblem adorns the end of these alternate fit shades to lend an urban vibe to your everyday look. Luxury is all in the details, and Dolce & Gabbana eyewear for men and women has plenty to show off. Sleek eyeglasses and sunglasses frames accented with metallic embellishments, crystal ornamentation, and more, are as much jewelry as they are eyewear. D&G puts an haute couture spin on classic frames styles that stand out from the crowd.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/dolce-gabbana-dg4338f-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(228, 'Dolce & Gabbana DG4338', 'Dolce & Gabbana', 'Sunglasses', 460.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/dolce-gabbana-sun-DG4338-501-87.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Dolce & Gabbana DG4338 Sunglasses now. Unleash your inner fashionista wearing the Dolce & Gabbana DG4338 sunglasses. These square rims are made from hypoallergenic, lightweight plastic that’s comfortable to wear. The slim temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for stability behind the ears. Enjoy clean styling in these contemporary square-frame sunglasses from Dolce & Gabbana. Luxury is all in the details, and Dolce & Gabbana eyewear for men and women has plenty to show off. Sleek eyeglasses and sunglasses frames accented with metallic embellishments, crystal ornamentation, and more, are as much jewelry as they are eyewear. D&G puts an haute couture spin on classic frames styles that stand out from the crowd.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/dolce-gabbana-dg4338-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(229, 'Brooks Brothers BB 4040S', 'Brooks Brothers', 'Sunglasses', 115.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Brooks-Brothers-BB4040S-Black-167487-Solid-Grey-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Brooks Brothers BB 4040S Sunglasses now. Step out in style wearing the Brooks Brothers BB 4040S sunglasses. These rectangular shades offer a timeless look that’s appropriate for any occasion. The metal rims are lightweight but sturdy, with thin wire cores that keep the glasses comfortable despite their size. A subtle wingtip detail adds an elegant touch to these handsome frames. For exceptional quality in timeless rectangular sunglasses, choose these from Brooks Brothers. Brooks Brothers has been designing men\'s styles for over one hundred and fifty years, and men have relied on Brooks Brothers to outfit them in the best fashions and highest quality materials. Brooks Brothers eyewear is perfectly suited for discerning men who believe that fashion and masculinity are not mutually exclusive. The Brooks Brothers eyewear collections use clean lines and fashionably understated designs to add unwavering sophistication to any outfit.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/brooks-brothers-bb-4040s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(230, 'Versace VE4345BA', 'Versace', 'Sunglasses', 278.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Versace-VE4345BA-Black-GB1-11-Gray-Gradient-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Versace VE4345BA Sunglasses now. Extravagant designs and bold embellishments feature prominently on the frames in the Versace eyewear collection. Versace\'s haute couture expertise shines in this collection of designer sunglasses and prescription eyewear for men and women. Rx-ready frames in sun and optical styles offer an opportunity to showcase your personal style in eyewear tailored with your prescription. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Versace retailer, selling only 100% authentic Versace eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you love: each Versace frame comes with original brand markings certified by Versace itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/versace-ve4345ba-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(231, 'Vera Bradley Emery', 'Vera Bradley', 'Sunglasses', 183.89, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Vera-Bradley-sun-EMERY-java-navy-camo.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Vera Bradley Emery Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Vera Bradley frames. The Vera Bradley Emery sunglasses offer a fresh take on the aviator style. The metal rims are strong and corrosion-resistant, while the slim profile keeps these shades comfortable to wear. Wide metal brows grace the ends of the slender wirecore temples, adding elegance to an otherwise straightforward design. A floral print accents each lens to add subtle flair without overwhelming the overall look. These women’s Vera Bradley sunglasses live up to their maker\'s reputation for distinctive style and quality craftsmanship, they\'re ready to accompany you anywhere life takes you.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/vera-bradley-emery-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(232, 'Zeal Optics Bennett', 'Zeal Optics', 'Sunglasses', 159.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-sunglasses-bennett-tortoise-11534.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-sunglasses-bennett-lilactort-11535.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Zeal Optics Bennett Sunglasses now. These Bennett sunglasses from Zeal Optics feature a aesthetic that’s both bold and feminine. The rounded edges on the lenses soften the lines of a classic browline frame, while distinctive details like keyhole openings at each end add visual interest. Crafted in lightweight plastic, these versatile shades are comfortable to wear indoors and outdoors alike. Explore Zeal Optics and discover striking eyewear offered in classic and contemporary silhouettes, and designed for active wear. Sporty wraparounds and wraparound-inspired rectangles speak to wearers who want a sleek, modern look; those who prefer a more traditional profile will find squares and rounded-edged frames styles. This eyewear comes in an array of colors and patterns to suit a number of tastes; on-trend embellishments like metal accents on the frames, or distinctive cutaways on the temple arms, impart a hint of sophistication to Zeal Optics frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/zeal-optics-bennett-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
