(234, 'Persol PO3199S', 'Persol', 'Sunglasses', 486.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/persol-sun-PO3199S-1106M3.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/persol-sun-PO3199S-24-31.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Persol PO3199S Sunglasses now. Persol PO3199S sunglasses for men boast a timeless square silhouette made refined and sophisticated by the brand’s expert craftsmanship. The frames are crafted in hypoallergenic plastic that\'s lightweight but sturdy, with durable wire cores inside the thick rims for added strength. The skull temples curve inward gently to keep the shades from slipping during activity. Enjoy classic styling with modern design when you opt for these cool Persol sunglasses for men. Persol eyewear is among the most well respected and distinguished eyewear brands in the world. Each attractive and comfortable frame is expertly hand crafted in Lauriano, Italy. Persol eyewear is made of only the highest quality materials. Persol\'s Meflecto system gives each Persol frame a patented \"flexible stem\" that makes Persol glasses frames among the most comfortable on the market. Persol\'s ultra-stylish frames and unparalleled craftsmanship make Persol popular with musicians, actors, and cultural icons. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Persol retailer, selling only 100% authentic Persol eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you love: each Persol frame comes with original brand markings certified by Persol itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/persol-po3199s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL);
