(256, 'Costa Spearo', 'Costa', 'Sunglasses', 309.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Spearo-Blackout-900812-Blue-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Spearo-Blackout-900813-Green-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Spearo-Matte-Tortoise-900821-Green-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Spearo-Blackout-900802-Gray-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Costa Spearo Sunglasses now. Gear up for an active day in the sun with a pair of Costa Spearo sunglasses. These shades feature lightweight, eco-friendly plastic frames that stand up to wear and tear. The ergonomic temples curve inward gently to keep the sunglasses from slipping during water activities. Wide tips provide added stability behind the ears while you hike, camp, or fish your way to success. For eye-catching style, eco-friendly performance and long-term durability, opt for these Spearo sunglasses from Costa. Costa eyewear is made for those with an active lifestyle, bringing a healthy dose of fashion to the beach or trailhead. Polarized sunglasses, eyeglasses, and C-Mates bifocal readers by Costa will help you navigate in any direction your adventure leads. Created by fisherman for fisherman in the late 1980s, Costa continues to create quality sunglasses and eyeglasses with innovative technologies. These performance glasses were \"born on the water,\" and they’re made to last—each pair is a worthy investment. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Costa dealer, selling only 100% authentic Costa 580 polarized lenses with its sunglasses, prescription sunglasses, and readers frames. Costa brings you the best of both worlds—innovative lens technology paired with authentic Costa frames for any outdoor adventure. Additional Information: Costa Lens Colors and Materials (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/costa-spearo-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(257, 'Dragon DR Meridien LL Polar', 'Dragon', 'Sunglasses', 190.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Dragon-sun-DRMeridienLLPolar-RobMachadoLLBrownPolar960.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Dragon-Sun-DR-MERIDIEN-LL-POLAR-matte-black-022.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Dragon-sun-DR-MERIDIEN-LL-POLAR-crystal-benchetler-970.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Dragon DR Meridien LL Polar Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Dragon frames. Dragon offers a bold look with the DR Meridien LL Polar sunglasses. The rounded frames are made in lightweight, durable plastic that’s designed to stand up against wind and water. The wire-core rivet hinges keep these shades securely in place, even when you\'re enjoying your favorite water sport or other outdoor activity. With their distinctive double bridges, these cool shades lend retro styling to modern fashion looks.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/dragon-dr-meridien-polar-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(258, 'Oakley Replacement Lenses Holbrook XL (AOO9417LS)', 'Oakley Replacement Lenses', 'Sunglasses', 128.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Holbrook-XL-1-Prizm-Sapphire-Polarized-Accessories.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Holbrook-XL-5-Prizm-Deep-Water-Polarized-Accessories.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Holbrook-XL-16-Prizm-Tungsten-Accessories.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Holbrook-XL-14-Prizm-Shallow-Water-Polarized-Accessories.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Holbrook-XL-11-Prizm-Road-Accessories.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Holbrook-XL-2-Prizm-Sapphire-Accessories.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Holbrook-XL-13-Prizm-Ruby-Polarized-Accessories.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Holbrook-XL-4-Prizm-Black-Polarized-Accessories.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley Replacement Lenses Holbrook XL (AOO9417LS) Sunglasses now. Personalize your Oakley sunglasses with these Holbrook XL (AOO9417LS) replacement lenses. Crafted in lightweight but sturdy performance plastic, the square frames are rounded at the edges for a classic look. Oakley’s patented High Definition Optics eliminate distortion and offer 100% UV filtering for clear, sharp vision. Choose a brilliant color to upgrade your Holbrook XL sunglasses with these Oakley replacement lenses. Oakley makes it convenient to swap out and revive your sunglasses with replacement lenses, available for many of your favorite Oakley frames. Whether you need to replace scratched lenses, or you simply want to change up the look of your existing Oakleys, FramesDirect offers an impressive variety of genuine replacement lenses for Oakley sunglasses and eyeglasses, in a range of colors and lens types to fit your Oakley frames. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic replacement lenses. Shop confidently for the quality sports lenses you demand: each set of Oakely replacement lenses comes with original brand markings certified by Oakley itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-replacement-lenses-holbrook-xl-aoo9417ls-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(259, 'Ray-Ban RB4387', 'Ray-Ban', 'Sunglasses', 160.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB4387-601-71-Black-Green-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB4387-Light-Havana-710-73-B-15-Brown-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB4387-639980-Blue-Dark-Blue-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB4387-Transparent-647711-Grey-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB4387 Sunglasses now. Gear up for sunny-day adventures in a pair of Ray-Ban RB4387 sunglasses for men. These square frames are crafted from hypoallergenic, lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to your lifestyle. The slim temples curve inward gently for added appeal. With their square design, these Ray-Ban sunglasses keep sunlight out of your peripheral vision while you\'re enjoying outdoor activities. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb4387-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(260, 'Smith Lowdown XL 2', 'Smith', 'Sunglasses', 205.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Smith-Sun-Lowdown-XL-2-Matte-Gray-Bronze-Mirror-ACI60QE.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-sunglasses-lowdown-xl-2-003606N.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-sunglasses-lowdown-xl-2-00360QG.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-sunglasses-lowdown-xl-2-00360L7.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-sunglasses-lowdown-xl-2-HGC60L5.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Smith-Sun-Lowdown-XL-2-Vintage-Tortoise-Gray-Green-P6560L7.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Smith-Sun-Lowdown-XL-2-Matte-Black-Gray-Green-003601H.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Smith-Sun-Lowdown-XL-2-Matte-Tortoise-Brown-N9P60XC.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-sun-Lowdown-XL-2-Matte-Summit-Crystal-LPA60L7.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-sun-Lowdown-XL-2-Matte-Black-00360B6.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Smith Lowdown XL 2 Sunglasses now. Smith offers a modern take on an iconic silhouette with the Lowdown XL 2 sunglasses. The rounded edges give these shades a softer look that’s feminine and flattering. A unisex design, these sunglasses boast lightweight, durable frames for comfort and performance wear after wear. Their split browline adds visual interest to the lower half of your profile. For contemporary cool with retro styling, choose the Lowdown XL 2 from Smith.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/smith-lowdown-xl-2-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(261, 'Oakley Replacement Lenses Drop Point (AOO9367LS)', 'Oakley Replacement Lenses', 'Sunglasses', 128.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Drop-Pointa-25-Prizm-Shallow-Water-Polarized-Accessories.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley Replacement Lenses Drop Point (AOO9367LS) Sunglasses now. Step out in bold fashion wearing the Oakley Drop Point Replacement Lenses (AOO9367LS). These rimless sunglasses offer a wide field of view, so you can keep an eye on your surroundings while enjoying your entertainment. The lightweight O Matter plastic frame material keeps these shades comfortable through long days, and their durable construction stands up to heavy use. If you\'re ready for something unconventional, try these unique rectangular replacement lenses from Oakley. Oakley makes it convenient to swap out and revive your sunglasses with replacement lenses, available for many of your favorite Oakley frames. Whether you need to replace scratched lenses, or you simply want to change up the look of your existing Oakleys, FramesDirect offers an impressive variety of genuine replacement lenses for Oakley sunglasses and eyeglasses, in a range of colors and lens types to fit your Oakley frames. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic replacement lenses. Shop confidently for the quality sports lenses you demand: each set of Oakely replacement lenses comes with original brand markings certified by Oakley itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-replacement-lenses-drop-point-aoo9367ls-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(262, 'Vera Wang V478', 'Vera Wang', 'Sunglasses', 263.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD__0000s_0203_V478_TE.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Verawang-SUN-V478-white.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Vera Wang V478 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Vera Wang frames. Embrace timeless style and showcase your distinctive taste wearing Vera Wang V478 sunglasses. The rounded edges of these chic shades accentuate the eyes and prevent harsh lines at their corners, while metal rims around each lens add visual interest behind them. A metalcore wireframe keeps the bold frames lightweight but sturdy, so you can enjoy your look all day long. For designer shades with a sophisticated edge, reach for these V478 sunglasses by Vera Wang. The Vera Wang Optical Collection reflects Vera Wang\'s passion for couture fashion. From sophisticated and classic styles to designs that truly push the envelope, the collection\'s eclectic combination of colors, textures, and designs brings runway inspired styles to every woman who truly loves fashion. The Vera Wang collection is an artistic and modern illustration of how eyeglasses can be so much more than a necessary accessory; eyeglasses can become stunning fashion statements that accentuate any outfit.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/vera-wang-v478-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(263, 'Oakley Replacement Lenses Holston (AOO9334LS)', 'Oakley Replacement Lenses', 'Sunglasses', 128.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Holston-10-Prizm-Sapphire-Polarized-Accessories.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley Replacement Lenses Holston (AOO9334LS) Sunglasses now. Reach for the Holston and experience Oakley sunglasses at their best. The rimless frames in these men’s sunglasses offer a sleek, sophisticated profile that\'s appropriate on any occasion. The lightweight O Matter plastic provides comfort and durability, even when you\'re out in the elements all day long. Oakley makes it convenient to swap out and revive your sunglasses with replacement lenses, available for many of your favorite Oakley frames. Whether you need to replace scratched lenses, or you simply want to change up the look of your existing Oakleys, FramesDirect offers an impressive variety of genuine replacement lenses for Oakley sunglasses and eyeglasses, in a range of colors and lens types to fit your Oakley frames. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic replacement lenses. Shop confidently for the quality sports lenses you demand: each set of Oakely replacement lenses comes with original brand markings certified by Oakley itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-replacement-lenses-holston-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(264, 'Via Spiga 360-SC', 'Via Spiga', 'Sunglasses', 182.50, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/via-spiga-sun-360-sc-red.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Via Spiga 360-SC Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Via Spiga frames. These Via Spiga 360-SC sunglasses for women exemplify the brand’s commitment to impeccable craftsmanship. The rounded edges and slight wingtip of these sleek frames are flattering on a variety of facial profiles, while plastic materials provide durability and comfort. A subtle keyhole at the upper rims draws attention to your eyes, while slightly curved browline lenses protect them from glare. For sunglasses with designer flair, opt for these sophisticated shades by Via Spiga.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/via-spiga-360-sc-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(265, 'Via Spiga 359-SC', 'Via Spiga', 'Sunglasses', 182.50, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/via-spiga-sun-359-sc-tort.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Via Spiga 359-SC Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Via Spiga frames. These Via Spiga 359-SC sunglasses for women exude a fun, vintage vibe. The wayfarer-style frames are made in lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to wear after wear. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears and provide a stylish appeal. Go handsfree on your next adventure wearing these cool sunglasses from Via Spiga.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/via-spiga-359-sc-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(266, 'Vera Wang VAS1', 'Vera Wang', 'Sunglasses', 263.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/vera-wang-sun-vas1-blk-horn.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/vera-wang-sun-vas1-pearl-tort.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/vera-wang-sun-vas1-scarlet-tort.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Vera Wang VAS1 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Vera Wang frames. Bold and beautiful, the Vera Wang VAS1 sunglasses are a perfect example of high-fashion headwear. The rectangular frames are made in lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to your busy lifestyle. The thick rims feature a curved browline and come with coated temple tips for comfort behind the ears. A metallic band at each end of the slim saddle bridges adds elegance to these cool shades from Vera Wang. The Vera Wang Optical Collection reflects Vera Wang\'s passion for couture fashion. From sophisticated and classic styles to designs that truly push the envelope, the collection\'s eclectic combination of colors, textures, and designs brings runway inspired styles to every woman who truly loves fashion. The Vera Wang collection is an artistic and modern illustration of how eyeglasses can be so much more than a necessary accessory; eyeglasses can become stunning fashion statements that accentuate any outfit.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/vera-wang-vas1-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(267, 'Randolph Engineering P3 Fusion Inlay', 'Randolph Engineering', 'Sunglasses', 339.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/randolph-sunglasses-P3fusion-PI024.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/randolph-sunglasses-P3fusion-PI025.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Randolph Engineering P3 Fusion Inlay Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Randolph Engineering frames. The Randolph Engineering P3 Fusion Inlay sunglasses offer a bold, unique look. These unisex round frames are made in metal, which is both lightweight and sturdy. The metal rims feature an intricate design on the outside of each lens that adds visual interest to your everyday look. For sunglasses with a contemporary flair, reach for these P3 Fusion Inlay shades by Randolph Engineering. Crafted by hand, exceptional quality eyewear by Randolph Engineering boasts incredible durability and precise, crisp optics. Quality design and construction and superior performance are top priorities for this manufacturer of military standard-issue sunglasses. Find sunglasses—with or without prescription lenses—and eyeglasses in our collection of Randolph Engineering eyewear.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/randolph-engineering-p3-fusion-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(268, 'Vera Wang V480', 'Vera Wang', 'Sunglasses', 263.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD__0000s_0151_V480_BK.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD__0000s_0153_V480_AP.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD__0000s_0149_V480_TE.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Vera Wang V480 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Vera Wang frames. Step out in style wearing Vera Wang V480 sunglasses. These shades feature classic styling with modern touches, such as rounded edges and metal accents that add depth to the design. The metal rims are lightweight but sturdy, resulting in comfortable sunglasses you can wear all day long. For designer flair with enduring quality, choose these timeless sunglasses by Vera Wang. The Vera Wang Optical Collection reflects Vera Wang\'s passion for couture fashion. From sophisticated and classic styles to designs that truly push the envelope, the collection\'s eclectic combination of colors, textures, and designs brings runway inspired styles to every woman who truly loves fashion. The Vera Wang collection is an artistic and modern illustration of how eyeglasses can be so much more than a necessary accessory; eyeglasses can become stunning fashion statements that accentuate any outfit.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/vera-wang-v480-sunglasses', NULL, NULL);
