(269, 'Mont Blanc MB0013S', 'Mont Blanc', 'Sunglasses', 395.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/mont-blanc-sunglasses-MB0013S-001.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Mont Blanc MB0013S Sunglasses now. Step out in style wearing the MB0013S sunglasses by Mont Blanc. These chic rectangular sunglasses feature subtle angles that lend a modern feel to their timeless, classic design. The lightweight plastic rims are hypoallergenic and durable, with strong three-pointed hinges for added stability when you\'re on the go. A contrasting color pattern at the rim adds visual interest to these understated shades, while a unique design adds refinement and sportiness.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/mont-blanc-mb0013s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(270, 'Maui Jim Beaches-541', 'Maui Jim', 'Sunglasses', 399.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/maui-jim-sunglasses-beaches-541-2m.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Maui Jim Beaches-541 Sunglasses now. Step out in style wearing the Maui Jim Beaches-541 sunglasses. Their aviator silhouette is timeless, flattering, and functional, the deep-set lenses offer superior sun protection against glare and wind so you see clearly no matter where your adventures take you. Titanium metal provides these shades with lightweight comfort while also making them sturdy enough to last through years of use. A titanium plate at each temple bears the name “Maui Jim” for an added touch of elegance. Maui Jim has led the eyewear industry by design and innovation since 1980, offering eyes everywhere superior protection from the harmful rays of the sun in its popular line of sunglasses. From iconic shades with patented technologies, to readers perfect for sunny-day pastimes, to the impressively stylish and comfortable daily-wear frames in the Optical line, Maui Jim creates men’s and women’s performance eyewear for any scenario. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Maui Jim dealer, selling only 100% authentic Maui Jim sunglasses frames and lenses. Polarized with an anti-reflective coating, Maui Jim lenses reveal the vibrant colors of the world while protecting your eyes from the effects of the sun\'s harsh glare and harmful rays. Satisfaction guaranteed. Additional Information: Maui Lens Colors Information (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/maui-jim-beaches-541-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(271, 'Modo Delta', 'Modo', 'Sunglasses', 360.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-sun-delta-black.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-sun-delta-olive.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Modo Delta Sunglasses now. Modo combines classic styling with modern design in the Delta sunglasses. The rounded edges and split upper rim give these shades a retro look, but their metal construction makes them durable enough for everyday use. A skull-shaped accent at each end adds an edgy touch to this cool pair of Modo Delta sunglasses. The philosophy of Modo is that simplicity is the highest form of sophistication. Created in SoHo, the trendsetting Modo eyewear collection is \"eyewear for the individual.\" Modo eyewear offers a new type of luxury with uncompromising craftsmanship, design sensitivity and urban influences.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/modo-delta-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(272, 'Juicy Couture Ju 603/S', 'Juicy Couture', 'Sunglasses', 190.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/F-JU603S08079O.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/F-JU603S08XONQ.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Juicy Couture Ju 603/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Juicy Couture frames. Step out in style wearing the Ju 603/S sunglasses from Juicy Couture. The rounded edges and subtle angles of these shades give a retro look that’s glamorous yet sophisticated. Crafted from lightweight plastic, these frames are durable as well as comfortable to wear. With a combination of designer appeal and sporty styling, these stylish rectangular sunglasses are an appealing choice.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/juicy-couture-ju-603-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
