(294, 'Mont Blanc MB0006S', 'Mont Blanc', 'Sunglasses', 335.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/mont-blanc-sunglasses-MB0006S-004.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Mont Blanc MB0006S Sunglasses now. Gear up for adventure in on-trend fashion wearing the Mont Blanc MB0006S sunglasses. A full rimset of subtle details, from the contrasting temples to the logo at the temple tips, enhances their rugged cool. The lightweight acetate frames make these shades sturdy and flexible-a boon for an accessory that endures heavy use. Show your love of fine craftsmanship by opting for these stylish shades bearing the iconic Mont Blanc signature at their temple.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/mont-blanc-mb0006s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(295, 'Black Flys Flycoholic', 'Black Flys', 'Sunglasses', 110.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-flycoholic-shiny-black-smoke.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-flycoholic-matte-black-smoke.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-flycoholic-shiny-black-smoke-polarized.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-flycoholic-matte-black-smoke-polarized.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-flycoholic-tortoise-brown-lens.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-flycoholic-tortoise-brown-polarized-lens.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Black Flys Flycoholic Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Black Flys frames. Gear up for an active lifestyle in the Flycoholic sunglasses from Black Flys. These square frames made of plastic, are lightweight and impact-resistant, so they won\'t weigh you down at the end of a long day. The silicone ear socks keep these shades securely in place, whether you\'re on land or sea. For sporty style that stands out from the crowd, reach for these exceptional sunglasses from Black Flys.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/black-flys-flycoholic-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(296, 'Via Spiga 418-S', 'Via Spiga', 'Sunglasses', 182.50, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/via-spiga-sun-418-s-black.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/via-spiga-sun-418-s-brown.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/via-spiga-sun-418-s-burg.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Via Spiga 418-S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Via Spiga frames. These Via Spiga 418-S sunglasses capture the essence of timeless style. The rectangular frames are made in lightweight, corrosion-resistant metal that retains its shape throughout your day. The slim temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and boast elegant details like textural patterns and stripes at the tips for added appeal. Enjoy effortlessness every day when you step out in these chic sunglasses from Via Spiga.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/via-spiga-418-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(297, 'HUGO Hg 1047/S', 'HUGO', 'Sunglasses', 180.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/hugo-sunglasses-Hg1047S-0003-IR.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore HUGO Hg 1047/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on HUGO frames. HUGO presents these Hg 1047/S sunglasses for men, a classic rectangular design with a sleek silhouette. The lightweight plastic rims are strong and durable, with sturdy double bridges for an elegant look. The flexible wire cores allow these frames to adjust for optimal fit and comfort. With no-slip socks at the tips of the earsocks, these sunglasses stay put whether you\'re on or off shore.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/hugo-hg-1047-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(298, 'Fossil Fos 3095/S', 'Fossil', 'Sunglasses', 74.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/fossil-sunglasses-Fos3095S-0807-9O.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/fossil-sunglasses-Fos3095S-0086-HA.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Fossil Fos 3095/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Fossil frames. These Fos 3095/S sunglasses reflect the fun, fashionable style that Fossil is known for. The oval frames are made in lightweight plastic that’s strong enough to keep up on your busiest days. The rectangular rims feature a subtle wingtip shape for an elegant look. For eye-catching sunglasses with vintage styling, opt for these fabulous Fos 3095/S shades by Fossil. Fossil eyewear for men and women draws from vintage and contemporary urban style influences for inspired frames that lend a distinctive panache to any look. Discover casual looks you’ll love to wear for sunny day driving and weekdays at the office in our collection of Fossil eyewear: These frames elevate your everyday style.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/fossil-fos-3095-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(299, 'Black Flys Racer Fly Christian Fletcher Model', 'Black Flys', 'Sunglasses', 110.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-RACER-FLY-CHRISTIAN-FLETCHER-MODEL-shiny-black-smoke-polarized-lens.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-RACER-FLY-CHRISTIAN-FLETCHER-MODEL-blue-stripe-smoke-polarized-lens.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-racerfly-christian-fletcher-shiny-black-smoke.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-racerfly-christian-fletcher-matte-black-smoke.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-racerfly-christian-fletcher-matte-black-smoke-polarized.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-RACER-FLY-CHRISTIAN-FLETCHER-MODEL-blue-stripe-smoke-lens.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Black Flys Racer Fly Christian Fletcher Model Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Black Flys frames. These Racer Fly Christian Fletcher Model sunglasses for men from Black Flys feature a vintage-inspired, rectangular silhouette with rims that curve inward slightly at the top and bottom. The sturdy, lightweight plastic frames are durable enough to stand up to your active lifestyle. The wirecore temples curve gently behind the ears and boast signature branding near the brow end for added appeal for these Black Flys glasses.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/black-flys-racer-fly-christian-fletcher-model-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(300, 'Oakley Goggles O Frame 2.0 Pro XL Snow', 'Oakley Goggles', 'Sunglasses', 125.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-O-Frame-20-Matte-Black-711201-Fire-Iridium-Goggles.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/oakley-goggles-o-frame2ProXL-03.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley Goggles O Frame 2.0 Pro XL Snow Sunglasses now. Reach for a pair of Oakley Goggles O Frame 2.0 Pro XL Snow unisex sunglasses and enjoy enhanced visual acuity in any challenging environment. These wrap-around shades offer ultra-wide lenses that provide an expansive field of view, while the no-slip grip at the tips provides stability on windy days or when you\'re skiing with your head down. Constructed with a lightweight O Matter plastic frame material that absorbs impact and is durable enough to last through seasons of rugged use, opt for these snow goggles from Oakley. The Oakley brand is universally recognized and is synonymous with innovative, quality craftsmanship. Oakley is a leading name in sports sunglasses & goggles because it offers athletes stylish shades that are made with cutting edge design and technology so that it not only looks good but can also withstand harsh environments and truly extreme conditions. Oakley has perfected sporty wrap sunglasses, goggles, and shields and has modernized interpretations of other classic designs. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic Oakley Goggles and goggle lenses. Shop confidently for the quality sports eyewear you demand: each Oakley goggle comes with original brand markings and Oakley authentic lenses, both certified by Oakley itself. Additional Information: Oakley Lens Color Guide (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-goggles-o-frame-2.0-pro-xl-snow-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(301, 'Oakley Goggles Fall Line XM Snow', 'Oakley Goggles', 'Sunglasses', 239.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Fall-Line-M-Matte-Black-710312-Prizm-Sapphire-Iridium-Goggles.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley Goggles Fall Line XM Snow Sunglasses now. Oakley Goggles Fall Line XM Snow sunglasses offer a fresh take on the classic wrap-around style. In this case, it’s an extreme makeover, because these shades are anything but ordinary. The wraparound lens design provides maximum protection from wind and glare, with added coverage that cuts down on eye contact even as it increases the wearer\'s field of view. And for athletes who demand peak performance in their gear, the O Matter plastic frame material delivers lightweight durability you can rely on through all your adventures. The Oakley brand is universally recognized and is synonymous with innovative, quality craftsmanship. Oakley is a leading name in sports sunglasses & goggles because it offers athletes stylish shades that are made with cutting edge design and technology so that it not only looks good but can also withstand harsh environments and truly extreme conditions. Oakley has perfected sporty wrap sunglasses, goggles, and shields and has modernized interpretations of other classic designs. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic Oakley Goggles and goggle lenses. Shop confidently for the quality sports eyewear you demand: each Oakley goggle comes with original brand markings and Oakley authentic lenses, both certified by Oakley itself. Additional Information: Oakley Lens Color Guide (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-goggles-fall-line-xm-snow-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(302, 'Marc Jacobs Marc 415/S', 'Marc Jacobs', 'Sunglasses', 195.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/marc-jacobs-sunglasses-Marc415S-02M2-IR.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Marc Jacobs Marc 415/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Marc Jacobs frames. Marc Jacobs adds a touch of vintage glamour to the classic aviator in these men’s Marc 415/S sunglasses. The metal rims are strong and corrosion-resistant, while plastic temples are lightweight and durable. A metal skull imprint on the ends of the earpieces adds chic appeal. For effortlessness in urban styling, choose these cool shades from Marc Jacobs. The Marc Jacobs eyewear line has the perfect frames for men and women with eclectic tastes. Marc Jacobs eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses incorporate whimsical touches—think sculptural flowers at the temples, or frames shapes transformed from oval to cat-eye with an artful arc of metal around the lenses. Go bold or go subtle with Marc Jacobs eyewear, with chunky, oversized sunglasses in the mix alongside streamlined everyday glasses that transition effortlessly from work to weekend.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/marc-jacobs-marc-415-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(303, 'Zeal Optics Boone', 'Zeal Optics', 'Sunglasses', 159.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-sunglasses-boone-mtblack.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-sunglasses-boone-tortoise.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-sunglasses-boone-maple.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Zeal Optics Boone Sunglasses now. Show off your eye for style with a pair of Boone sunglasses from Zeal Optics. These unisex shades feature rectangular frames made from eco-friendly plastic that’s lightweight and durable enough for your outdoor adventures. The skull temples curve inward to keep the glasses from slipping during your activities, and come with coated tips for comfort behind the ears. A keyhole Bridge keeps the lenses stable while allowing air to flow between them, keeping these cool shades from fogging up on you during exertions in warm weather. For sunglasses that look great wherever you go, reach for Boone by Zeal Optics. Explore Zeal Optics and discover striking eyewear offered in classic and contemporary silhouettes, and designed for active wear. Sporty wraparounds and wraparound-inspired rectangles speak to wearers who want a sleek, modern look; those who prefer a more traditional profile will find squares and rounded-edged frames styles. This eyewear comes in an array of colors and patterns to suit a number of tastes; on-trend embellishments like metal accents on the frames, or distinctive cutaways on the temple arms, impart a hint of sophistication to Zeal Optics frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/zeal-optics-boone-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(304, 'Marc Jacobs Marc 421/S', 'Marc Jacobs', 'Sunglasses', 146.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/marc-jacobs-sunglasses-Marc421S-0DXH-IR.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Marc Jacobs Marc 421/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Marc Jacobs frames. These Marc Jacobs Marc 421/S sunglasses are chic and sophisticated, perfect for women who prefer a retro look. The cat-eye frames are made from hypoallergenic plastic that’s lightweight and durable, ideal for glasses worn on a day-to-day basis. The slim temples curve inward softly to keep the glasses from slipping during active pursuits. Enjoy cat-eye styling with vintage flair when you opt for these sunglasses from Marc Jacobs. The Marc Jacobs eyewear line has the perfect frames for men and women with eclectic tastes. Marc Jacobs eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses incorporate whimsical touches—think sculptural flowers at the temples, or frames shapes transformed from oval to cat-eye with an artful arc of metal around the lenses. Go bold or go subtle with Marc Jacobs eyewear, with chunky, oversized sunglasses in the mix alongside streamlined everyday glasses that transition effortlessly from work to weekend.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/marc-jacobs-marc-421-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL);
