(341, 'Coach HC7111', 'Coach', 'Sunglasses', 181.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/coach-sun-HC7111-900513.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/coach-sun-HC7111-9001T3.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Coach HC7111 Sunglasses now. These HC7111 sunglasses from Coach offer a classic aesthetic that’s universally flattering. The oval frames are made in lightweight, corrosion-resistant metal that retains its shape through prolonged wear. The slim temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears. Enjoy understated style with enduring appeal wearing these chic sunglasses from Coach. Women’s designer eyewear by Coach exudes a distinctive big-city vibe in chic frames that blend modern sophistication with vintage-inspired style. The result is a collection of daring luxury eyewear that complements a wide range of wardrobes. Browse oversized frames in bold colors, or sleek silhouettes in subtle neutral hues. Coach uses modern color palettes in two-tone frames, but also includes the classics, drawing inspiration from vintage eyewear styles in black or tortoiseshell to create elegant frames that appeal to contemporary tastes.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/coach-hc7111-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(342, 'Michael Kors MK1062', 'Michael Kors', 'Sunglasses', 105.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/michael-kors-sun-MK1062-11086G.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Michael Kors MK1062 Sunglasses now. A glamorous cat-eye silhouette is reimagined in these lustrous MK1062 sunglasses from Michael Kors. The distinctive metal rims are made in a lightweight, corrosion-resistant alloy that retains its shape and durability. The sleek temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears. Enjoy classic styling with modern flair wearing these chic cat-eye sunglasses from Michael Kors. The sophisticated Michael Kors eyewear collection presents classic elegance to suit a variety of tastes. Frames by this celebrated designer exude a timeless appeal to complement modern wardrobes, but plenty of daring, trendsetting styles appear throughout the collection. From the modern, clean eyeglasses to the chic, wearable outerwear parading down the runways, Michael Kors continues to be a popular choice with those seeking accessible luxury.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/michael-kors-mk1062-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(343, 'Dolce & Gabbana DG4373', 'Dolce & Gabbana', 'Sunglasses', 415.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/dolce-gabbana-sun-DG4373-325613.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/dolce-gabbana-sun-DG4373-32468G.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Dolce & Gabbana DG4373 Sunglasses now. The Dolce & Gabbana DG4373 sunglasses flaunt a glamorous square silhouette. These bold, sophisticated shades are made in lightweight, lustrous plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to frequent wear. The skull-shape frames add visual interest to your look while providing a comfortable fit, and metallic details at the brow end lend elegance throughout. A coated temple tip offers comfort behind the ear. Enjoy contemporary Italian glamour when you slip on these timeless square sunglasses from Dolce & Gabbana. Luxury is all in the details, and Dolce & Gabbana eyewear for men and women has plenty to show off. Sleek eyeglasses and sunglasses frames accented with metallic embellishments, crystal ornamentation, and more, are as much jewelry as they are eyewear. D&G puts an haute couture spin on classic frames styles that stand out from the crowd.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/dolce-gabbana-dg4373-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(344, 'Lafont Francesca', 'Lafont', 'Sunglasses', 445.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Lafont-sun-FRANCESCA-red-6080.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Lafont Francesca Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Lafont frames. The Francesca sunglasses from Lafont offer a look that’s classic and glamorous. The cat-eye frames are made in lightweight, durable plastic that\'s strong enough to keep up on your busiest days. The slim temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and offer added appeal. Enjoy an timeless aesthetic when you opt for these Francesca sunglasses from Lafont. The Lafont eyewear collection features refined silhouettes with a bit of attitude—discover designer eyewear to suit your tastes, whether your style leans retro, contemporary, or classic. Chic in any shape, Lafont frames come in round, rectangular, oval, square, wayfarer, and cat-eye silhouettes. The carefully chosen materials Lafont uses in its designs include acetate, carbon fiber, impact-resistant plastic, stainless steel, metal inlay, and others. This eyewear collection boasts playful patterns and florals, tortoiseshell, and solids in bright or subtle hues, many of which are Lafont exclusives.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/lafont-francesca-sunglasses', NULL, NULL);
