(356, 'RALPH by Ralph Lauren RA5265', 'RALPH by Ralph Lauren', 'Sunglasses', 106.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ralph-by-ralph-lauren-sun-RA5265-575225.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ralph-by-ralph-lauren-sun-RA5265-583613.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore RALPH by Ralph Lauren RA5265 Sunglasses now. These women\'s RALPH by Ralph Lauren RA5265 sunglasses are stylish and functional. The square frames are made in hypoallergenic plastic that is lightweight yet durable, allowing you to wear them all day. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for a secure fit behind the ears, and the design adds effortless appeal. Enjoy these shades by Ralph Lauren every day. Ralph by Ralph Lauren lends compelling drama to the brand’s Ivy League-inspired roots. Discover oversized sunglasses frames, chunky styles, and sleek silhouettes, all with the effortless sophistication perfected by Ralph Lauren. The designer first shared his pioneering style in 1967 with the release of a line of men’s striped ties. They became an immediate hit and Lauren grew his business into a global fashion and lifestyle brand that includes his sunglasses and prescription sunglasses collection.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ralph-by-ralph-lauren-ra5265-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
