(362, 'Maui Jim Readers Breakwall Reader-422', 'Maui Jim Readers', 'Sunglasses', 239.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/maui-jim-sunglasses-breakwall-422-02.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/maui-jim-sunglasses-breakwall-422-02.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/maui-jim-sunglasses-breakwall-422-02.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/maui-jim-sunglasses-breakwall-h422-26.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/maui-jim-sunglasses-breakwall-h422-26.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/maui-jim-sunglasses-breakwall-h422-26.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Maui Jim Readers Breakwall Reader-422 Sunglasses now. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Maui Jim dealer, selling only 100% authentic Maui Jim sunglasses frames and lenses. Polarized with an anti-reflective coating, Maui Jim lenses reveal the vibrant colors of the world while protecting your eyes from the effects of the sun\'s harsh glare and harmful rays. Satisfaction guaranteed.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/maui-jim-readers-breakwall-422-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
