(365, 'Kate Spade Augusta/G/S', 'Kate Spade', 'Sunglasses', 215.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/katespade-augustags-sunglasses-03h2wj-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/kate-spade-sunglasses-Augusta-G-S-02NL-LA.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Kate Spade Augusta/G/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Kate Spade frames. Kate Spade Augusta/G/S sunglasses offer a modern interpretation of the classic ’60s silhouette. The rounded edges and wingtips recall that era’s popular styles, while the slim profile offers a contemporary look. Crafted from lightweight, durable plastic, these frames are comfortable to wear. The Kate Spade New York name at the temple announces your good taste in fashion. The sunglasses and eyeglasses in our Kate Spade collection offer the brand\'s defining mix of colors, patterns, and bold femininity. The Kate Spade eyewear line is perfect for women who appreciate an elegant look with a dash of playfulness. From sunglasses to prescription eyeglasses and sunglasses frames, the Kate Spade collection includes a spectacular array of hues, whimsical patterns, and charming shapes.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/kate-spade-augusta-g-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
