(367, 'Gucci GG0765SA - Alternate Fit', 'Gucci', 'Sunglasses', 305.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/gucci-sunglasses-GG0765SA-002.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Gucci GG0765SA - Alternate Fit Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Gucci frames. These GG0765SA - Alternate Fit sunglasses from Gucci are designed with women in mind. The rectangular frames are made in plastic, which is lightweight and durable. The skull temples curve inward for stability behind the ears, and boast a subtle design near the brow end for added appeal. If you\'re looking to make a statement while enjoying high-quality design elements, reach for these alternate fit Gucci sunglasses. Founded in Florence, Italy, in 1921, Gucci is one of the world\'s leading luxury brands. Following the House\'s centenary, Gucci forges ahead into the next hundred years, continuing to redefine luxury while celebrating the creativity, Italian craftsmanship, and innovation at the core of its values. Gucci is part of the global luxury group Kering, which manages the development of a series of renowned Houses in fashion, leather goods, jewelry, and eyewear. Discover more about Gucci at www.gucci.com . The latest range of sunglasses and optical frames embodies Gucci\'s signature designs. Drawing inspiration from the archive of the House, the eyewear collection combines emblematic codes with new details in an unexpected selection of shapes and styles.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/gucci-gg0765sa-alternate-fit-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
