(384, 'Polaroid Pld 4107/S', 'Polaroid', 'Sunglasses', 74.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/polaroid-sunglasses-pld-4107s-0086-la.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/polaroid-sunglasses-pld-4107s-0807-wj.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/polaroid-sunglasses-pld-4107s-0jbw-c3.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Polaroid Pld 4107/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Polaroid frames. Step out in style wearing the women’s Polaroid Pld 4107/S sunglasses. These cat-eye frames are made from plastic that\'s lightweight and durable, perfect for shades you wear often. The wirecore temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, with added appeal. With chic cat-eye styling at once classic and contemporary, these sunglasses make it easy to add your own twist on vintage glamour.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/polaroid-pld-4107-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(385, 'Polaroid Pld 2109/S', 'Polaroid', 'Sunglasses', 74.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/polaroid-sunglasses-pld-2109s-0086-uc.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/polaroid-sunglasses-pld-2109s-0807-m9.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Polaroid Pld 2109/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Polaroid frames. These men’s Pld 2109/S sunglasses from Polaroid feature rectangular frames made in lightweight, durable plastic that\'s strong enough to keep up on your busiest days. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and boast a subtle design which provides designer appeal. Go casual cool when you slip on these timeless rectangular sunglasses from Polaroid.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/polaroid-pld-2109-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(386, 'Dolce & Gabbana DG2270', 'Dolce & Gabbana', 'Sunglasses', 292.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/dolce-gabbana-sun-DG2270-327687.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/DolceeGabbana-DG2270-Matte-Black-1106K1-Grey-Silver-Gold-Graffiti-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Dolce & Gabbana DG2270 Sunglasses now. The Dolce & Gabbana DG2270 sunglasses for men make a bold statement. The rectangular rims are crafted in metal, which is both lightweight and durable. The skull temples curve inward gently to protect the ears and feature subtle detailing near the brow end for added appeal. A metal band around the rims adds further appeal to these cool shades from Dolce & Gabbana. Luxury is all in the details, and Dolce & Gabbana eyewear for men and women has plenty to show off. Sleek eyeglasses and sunglasses frames accented with metallic embellishments, crystal ornamentation, and more, are as much jewelry as they are eyewear. D&G puts an haute couture spin on classic frames styles that stand out from the crowd.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/dolce-gabbana-dg2270-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(387, 'Zeal Optics Quandary', 'Zeal Optics', 'Sunglasses', 159.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-sunglasses-quandary-11854.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-sunglasses-quandary-11855.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-sunglasses-quandary-11856.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-sunglasses-quandary-11857.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Zeal Optics Quandary Sunglasses now. Zeal Optics Quandary sunglasses offer an adventurous take on a classic rectangular frame. The bold rims are made in a lightweight, durable plastic that\'s surprisingly resistant to breakage and permanent deformation, even if you lose them in the water! With their ergonomic design and flexible temples, these shades stay comfortable at the beach or on land. Look cool wearing Zeal Optics Quandary sunglasses. Explore Zeal Optics and discover striking eyewear offered in classic and contemporary silhouettes, and designed for active wear. Sporty wraparounds and wraparound-inspired rectangles speak to wearers who want a sleek, modern look; those who prefer a more traditional profile will find squares and rounded-edged frames styles. This eyewear comes in an array of colors and patterns to suit a number of tastes; on-trend embellishments like metal accents on the frames, or distinctive cutaways on the temple arms, impart a hint of sophistication to Zeal Optics frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/zeal-optics-quandary-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(388, 'Burberry BE4341 Miller', 'Burberry', 'Sunglasses', 346.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/burberry-sun-BE4341-3001T8.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/burberry-eye-BE4341-3002SB.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Burberry BE4341 Miller Sunglasses now. Reach for the Miller BE4341 sunglasses and enjoy a classic look with modern styling. The rectangular frames are made in lightweight, hypoallergenic plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to heavy use. The slim temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for added stability behind the ears. A metallic band near the brow end adds elegance to these cool shades. Throughout Burberry\'s 150 year history, it has become one of the most famous and recognizable names in fashion, not to mention eyewear. Burberry is dedicated to providing the highest quality products and materials so that its eyeglass frames maintain the legacy of fashion, elegance, and style for which Burberry is known. Classic styling and traditional designs are meshed with modern accents and youthful influences to make Burberry a company that never sacrifices style to maintain its high standards.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/burberry-be4341-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(389, 'Burberry BE4337F Carnaby - Alternate Fit', 'Burberry', 'Sunglasses', 284.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/burberry-sun-BE4337F-379887.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Burberry BE4337F Carnaby - Alternate Fit Sunglasses now. These BE4337F Carnaby - Alternate Fit men’s sunglasses from Burberry are crafted in lightweight, durable plastic that\'s strong enough to keep up on your busiest days. The square frames feature an elegant center-set browline and comfort-coated tips for a comfortable fit behind the ears. A subtle twist at each end adds visual interest to these classic shades from Burberry. Throughout Burberry\'s 150 year history, it has become one of the most famous and recognizable names in fashion, not to mention eyewear. Burberry is dedicated to providing the highest quality products and materials so that its eyeglass frames maintain the legacy of fashion, elegance, and style for which Burberry is known. Classic styling and traditional designs are meshed with modern accents and youthful influences to make Burberry a company that never sacrifices style to maintain its high standards.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/burberry-be4337f-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(390, 'Polaroid Pld 4108/S', 'Polaroid', 'Sunglasses', 74.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/polaroid-sunglasses-pld-4108s-0807-wj.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/polaroid-sunglasses-pld-4108s-0086-la.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Polaroid Pld 4108/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Polaroid frames. The women’s Polaroid Pld 4108/S sunglasses offer a vintage-inspired square silhouette. These frames are made from plastic, which is lightweight and durable, perfect for glasses you wear every day. The square rims feature a subtle wingtip for added appeal. If you\'re looking for classic styling with contemporary flair, reach for these chic shades by Polaroid.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/polaroid-pld-4108-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
