(392, 'Dolce & Gabbana DG6144', 'Dolce & Gabbana', 'Sunglasses', 384.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/dolce-gabbana-sun-DG6144-501-8G.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Dolce & Gabbana DG6144 Sunglasses now. These women’s DG6144 sunglasses from Dolce & Gabbana are a stylish, on-trend update of the classic cat-eye silhouette. The dramatic lenses are gently curved at the sides, emphasizing your high cheekbones and creating a distinctive “cats-eye” look. Crafted in hypoallergenic plastic, these glasses are lightweight but durable, with sturdy wire core temples that adjust for comfort behind the ears. A subtle metallic band above each lens adds elegance to these cool shades from Dolce & Gabbana. Luxury is all in the details, and Dolce & Gabbana eyewear for men and women has plenty to show off. Sleek eyeglasses and sunglasses frames accented with metallic embellishments, crystal ornamentation, and more, are as much jewelry as they are eyewear. D&G puts an haute couture spin on classic frames styles that stand out from the crowd.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/dolce-gabbana-dg6144-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(393, 'Tory Burch TY9062U', 'Tory Burch', 'Sunglasses', 188.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/tory-burch-sun-TY9062U-11458E.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Tory Burch TY9062U Sunglasses now. Our collection of Tory Burch designer eyewear for women offers bold, stunning frames that blend classic and contemporary influences. Discover sunglasses and eyeglasses frames in a range of chic silhouettes, including oval, cat-eye, rectangular, square, and round styles. Tory Burch eyewear comes in lustrous acetate, corrosion-resistant Monel metal, and other durable and lightweight materials. Within our Tory Burch eyewear line you\'ll find versatile solid hues, refined two-toned glasses, and vibrant color combinations that capture attention.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/tory-burch-ty9062u-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
