(395, 'O\'Neill Harlyn 2.0', 'O\'Neill', 'Sunglasses', 69.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oneill-sun-HARLYN2.0-127p.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oneill-sun-HARLYN2.0-102p.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oneill-sun-HARLYN2.0-165p.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oneill-sun-HARLYN2.0-193p.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore O\'Neill Harlyn 2.0 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on O\'Neill frames. Gear up for an action-packed day in the O\'Neill Harlyn 2.0 sunglasses. These rectangular shades offer optimum protection against wind and glare, thanks to their wraparound design and hydrophilic rubber grips at the tips of the arms for added stability behind the ears. The lightweight plastic frames come with sturdy double bridges to maintain a rugged profile, even when you\'re surfing or snowboarding all day long. For exceptional performance in extreme conditions, choose these Harlyn sunglasses from O\'Neill.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oneill-harlyn-2.0-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(396, 'Marc Jacobs Marc 526/S', 'Marc Jacobs', 'Sunglasses', 146.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/marc-jacobs-sunglasses-marc-526s-0807-9o.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Marc Jacobs Marc 526/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Marc Jacobs frames. These Marc 526/S sunglasses for women exude a chic, downtown vibe that’s unmistakably Marc Jacobs. The square frames are made in lightweight, lustrous plastic that\'s durable enough to stand up to heavy wear. The sleek skull temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for stability behind the ears. A metallic band gracefully encircles each brow end, adding elegance to these cool shades from Marc Jacobs. The Marc Jacobs eyewear line has the perfect frames for men and women with eclectic tastes. Marc Jacobs eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses incorporate whimsical touches—think sculptural flowers at the temples, or frames shapes transformed from oval to cat-eye with an artful arc of metal around the lenses. Go bold or go subtle with Marc Jacobs eyewear, with chunky, oversized sunglasses in the mix alongside streamlined everyday glasses that transition effortlessly from work to weekend.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/marc-jacobs-marc-526-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(397, 'Under Armour UA 0005/S', 'Under Armour', 'Sunglasses', 100.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/under-armour-sunglasses-UA0005-S-0RC2-UZ.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Under-Armour-sun-UA-0005S-black-grey-008A-V8.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/UA-sun-UA0005S-matte-black-01T.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/under-armour-sunglasses-UA0005-S-0MNG-Z9.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Under Armour UA 0005/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Under Armour frames. Step outside your comfort zone and stand out from the crowd when you wear the bold, sporty style of these Under Armour UA 0005/S sunglasses for men. The oversized frames are made in lightweight, durable plastic that\'s strong enough to keep up on your busiest days. The wire cores of the flexible temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and boast added appeal. If you\'re looking for head-turning sunglasses with flair to spare, reach for these from Under Armour.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/under-armour-ua-0005-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(398, 'Ted Baker TBM081', 'Ted Baker', 'Sunglasses', 235.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/tedBaker-sun-TBM081-BlackBLK.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ted Baker TBM081 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Ted Baker frames. These TBM081 frames from Ted Baker are an ideal way to add a touch of modern style to classic sunglasses. The rectangular rims are made in hypoallergenic, lightweight plastic that’s sturdy enough to stand up to everyday wear. The slim temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for added stability behind the ears. Enjoy impeccable quality when you opt for these Ted Baker sunglasses. From it\'s beginning as a clothier in Glasglow, Ted Baker has had an unwavering focus on attention to detail, fine quality, and a unique sense of fashion. Ted Baker\'s strong style convictions are obvious in all of Ted Baker\'s eyewear designs. Ted Baker frames cover every aspect of eyewear styling, from timeless sophistication to quirky retro revival and everything in between.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ted-baker-tbm081-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(399, 'Burberry BE4334 Myrtle', 'Burberry', 'Sunglasses', 265.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Burberry-BE4334-Yellow-393173-Brown-Eyeglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Burberry BE4334 Myrtle Sunglasses now. The Burberry BE4334 Myrtle sunglasses attract the bold fashion maven with an eye for elevated style. These are no ordinary square frames: The chunky full rims and angular edges make for a daring look that draws attention to your eyes. The wide shark fin temples exude retro-chic appeal, and their flexible wire cores adjust easily for a secure, custom fit. Crafted in hypoallergenic acetate, the Myrtle sunglasses from Burberry come with easy-to-repair conventional hinges for extra durability. Throughout Burberry\'s 150 year history, it has become one of the most famous and recognizable names in fashion, not to mention eyewear. Burberry is dedicated to providing the highest quality products and materials so that its eyeglass frames maintain the legacy of fashion, elegance, and style for which Burberry is known. Classic styling and traditional designs are meshed with modern accents and youthful influences to make Burberry a company that never sacrifices style to maintain its high standards.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/burberry-be4334-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(400, 'Ralph Lauren RL7069', 'Ralph Lauren', 'Sunglasses', 235.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ralph-lauren-sun-RL7069-942373.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ralph Lauren RL7069 Sunglasses now. These men’s Ralph Lauren RL7069 sunglasses reflect the style that made aviator shades a classic, with metal rims and plastic frames. The metal accents on the endpieces add elegance, while plastic lenses make these shades lightweight and comfortable to wear. For effortlessness in your everyday fashion, reach for these aviator-style sunglasses from Ralph Lauren. The Ralph Lauren brand has been creating sophisticated and timeless styles since its inception in 1970. Ralph Lauren designs celebrate the refined luxury and understated elegance that is at the heart of American fashion. Ralph Lauren makes eyewear that is attractive and elegant, and Ralph Lauren\'s distinctive luxury is reflected in every frame. Ralph Lauren\'s contemporary styles and homage to vintage designs contribute to each frame\'s clean lines, subtle glamour, and uncomplicated class.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ralph-lauren-rl7069-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(401, 'Versace VE2232', 'Versace', 'Sunglasses', 473.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/versace-sun-VE2232-143887.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/versace-sun-VE2232-147187.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Versace VE2232 Sunglasses now. Embrace glamorous sophistication with Versace VE2232 sunglasses for women. These aviator-style frames are made from strong, corrosion-resistant metal that stands up to wear and tear. The slim temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and boast a classic design near the brow end. Wide rims grace these Versace shades with a touch of vintage flair, while their coated lenses filter out blinding sunlight on sunny days and glow under streetlights at night, keeping your eyes safe wherever you go. Unparalleled quality makes these aviator sunglasses by Versace exceptionally comfortable to wear despite their grand stature. Extravagant designs and bold embellishments feature prominently on the frames in the Versace eyewear collection. Versace\'s haute couture expertise shines in this collection of designer sunglasses and prescription eyewear for men and women. Rx-ready frames in sun and optical styles offer an opportunity to showcase your personal style in eyewear tailored with your prescription. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Versace retailer, selling only 100% authentic Versace eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you love: each Versace frame comes with original brand markings certified by Versace itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/versace-ve2232-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(402, 'O\'Neill Godrevy 2.0', 'O\'Neill', 'Sunglasses', 69.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oneill-sun-GODREVY2.0-127p.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oneill-sun-GODREVY2.0-113p.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oneill-sun-GODREVY2.0-151p.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oneill-sun-GODREVY2.0-165p.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore O\'Neill Godrevy 2.0 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on O\'Neill frames. Reach for a pair of O\'Neill Godrevy 2.0 sunglasses and enjoy life by the ocean. These unisex shades offer classic good looks with modern styling flourishes, making them ideal for anyone who appreciates timeless design with contemporary details. The oval frames come in lightweight plastic that\'s strong and durable, the perfect combination of comfort and utility in sunglasses designed to see lots of use throughout the seasons. Subtle wingtips at the endpoints add flair without overwhelming your look. Enjoy an active lifestyle outdoors wearing these cool O\'Neill sunglasses.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oneill-godrevy-2.0-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(403, 'Black Flys Fly Kitten', 'Black Flys', 'Sunglasses', 110.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-FLY-KITTEN-shiny-black-white-black-smoke-lens.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-FLY-KITTEN-shiny-black-white-black-smoke-gradient-lens.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-FLY-KITTEN-tortoise-pink-brown-lens.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-FLY-KITTEN-tortoise-pink-brown-gradient-lens.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-FLY-KITTEN-tortoise-pink-flash-brown-polarized-lens.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Black Flys Fly Kitten Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Black Flys frames. For women who enjoy the high fashion of cat-eye sunglasses, the Black Flys Fly Kitten delivers an elegant look with a sporty spin. The oversized lenses make these shades ideal for sunny weather, and they come in plastic frames that are lightweight and comfortable on your face. The wide temples provide stability behind the ears. Signature branding on the temple adds a designer touch to these cool shades from Black Flys.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/black-flys-fly-kitten-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(404, 'Giorgio Armani AR6080', 'Giorgio Armani', 'Sunglasses', 387.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Giorgio-Armani-AR6080-Gunmetal-300387-Grey-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Giorgio Armani AR6080 Sunglasses now. Discover a new standard for men’s sunglasses with the Giorgio Armani AR6080. These rectangular frames are made in metal, which is both lightweight and durable. The skull-shaped rims feature chameleon lenses that adjust to changing light conditions, while metallic accents on the endpoints add elegance. The adjustable-fit comfort collars of these handsome shades provide a secure fit. Famed Italian designer Giorgio Armani offers eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses in elevated styles for men and women. Popular eyewear silhouettes boast clean lines and attention to detail to complement your black tie, professional, or everyday attire. Crafted in Italy from high-quality materials in subdued neutrals or lively colors, Giorgio Armani eyewear speaks to the sartorial-minded wearer.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/giorgio-armani-ar6080-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
