(408, 'Dragon DR MARI LL ION', 'Dragon', 'Sunglasses', 139.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/DragonSundrMariLlIon-RobMachadoResin-LlGunBlue-963.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Dragon DR MARI LL ION Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Dragon frames. Dragon makes a bold fashion statement with these DR MARI LL ION sunglasses for men. The square frames are crafted in hypoallergenic plastic that’s lightweight and durable, ideal for long days in the sun. The distinctive browline adds interest to the classic square silhouette, while the wirecore temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears. Dragon emblazoned on the lenses add an additional touch of designer appeal to these cool shades from Marilli .', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/dragon-dr-mari-ll-ion-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
