(410, 'Lulu Guinness L172', 'Lulu Guinness', 'Sunglasses', 306.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/lulu-sunglasses-l172-gld.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Lulu Guinness L172 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Lulu Guinness frames. Lulu Guinness adds a touch of vintage style to these L172 sunglasses for women. The aviator-style frames are made in metal that’s lightweight and durable, ideal for long days in the sun. The skull temples curve inward gently to keep the glasses from slipping during activity. A metallic emblem with the brand\'s name at the temple adds an elegant finishing touch to these cool shades by Lulu Guinness.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/lulu-guinness-l172-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
