(413, 'Chloe CH0046S', 'Chloe', 'Sunglasses', 525.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/chloe-sunglasses-CH0046S-001.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/chloe-sunglasses-CH0046S-003.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Chloe CH0046S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Chloe frames. These CH0046S women\'s sunglasses from Chloe epitomize glamour with a touch of edginess. These fashionable frames come in an eye-catching shape: rounded edges, but with a slight downturn at the outer corner for a subtle lift to your gaze. The lightweight metal rims are durable, and the coated temple tips provide comfort even on extended wear. For designer shades that stand out from the crowd, choose these cool Chloe sunglasses. Founded in Paris in 1952 by Gaby Aghion, Chloé has always drawn inspiration from a romantic, feminine aesthetic to inform its design. Reaching worldwide popularity as part one of the biggest fashion brands of the 1970s, Chloé continues its legacy as an influential, timelessly feminine design house today. Chloé eyewear leans heavily on its history, with many of its early eyewear designs referencing popular 1970s styles, and simultaneously leading the way in modern fashion eyewear creations.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/chloe-ch0046s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
