(423, 'Lulu Guinness L176', 'Lulu Guinness', 'Sunglasses', 306.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/lulu-sunglasses-l176-blk.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Lulu Guinness L176 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Lulu Guinness frames. Accessorize your look with a pair of Lulu Guinness L176 sunglasses. Crafted in lightweight, durable plastic, these round frames are designed to stand up to the wear and tear of a busy day. The thick rims feature an elegant keyhole design at the upper rim and come coated with non-slip tips for comfort behind the ears. Enjoy urban style wherever you go wearing these chic sunglasses by Lulu Guinness.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/lulu-guinness-l176-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(424, 'Armani Exchange AX4112SU', 'Armani Exchange', 'Sunglasses', 91.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Armani-Exchange-AX4112SU-Matte-Black-80788G-Grey-Blue-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/armani-exchange-sun-AX4112SU-818180.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Armani Exchange AX4112SU Sunglasses now. A|X—or Armani Exchange—eyeglasses for men and women feature an assortment of high-end frames in contemporary styles. The brand is the playful, youthful sibling of the famed Italian brand Giorgio Armani. In stark contrast to the clean-cut, sophisticated tailoring of the luxury Armani label, A|X cites \"street-chic culture, fashionable dance music, freedom, and personal styles\" as its inspirations. Those trendy influences show in this versatile eyewear line that provides luxury in every detail. From a longtime leader in the high-end fashion industry, Armani Exchange makes no compromises on style.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/armani-exchange-ax4112su-sunglasses', NULL, NULL);
