(427, 'Black Flys Steel Pulse Flys/Collab', 'Black Flys', 'Sunglasses', 130.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-STEEL-PULSE-FLYS-COLLAB-matte-black-rasta-green-smoke-polarized-lens.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Black-Flys-sun-STEEL-PULSE-FLYS-COLLAB-matte-black-rasta-green-smoke-lens.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Black Flys Steel Pulse Flys/Collab Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Black Flys frames. Reach for Black Flys Steel Pulse Flys/Collab sunglasses and enjoy performance-driven style wherever your adventures take you. These durable, lightweight frames are made in a hypoallergenic material that won\'t irritate even the most sensitive skin. The square rims are crafted in a flexible but sturdy plastic that retains its shape through extended wear, while coated temple tips offer comfort behind the ears. Signature branding on the lens adds appeal to these cool shades from Black Flys.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/black-flys-steel-pulse-flys-collab-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
