(485, 'Fossil Fos 2115/G/S', 'Fossil', 'Sunglasses', 84.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Fossil-sun-2115-G-S-black-0807-9O.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Fossil-sun-2115-G-S-crystal-grey-063M-9O.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Fossil Fos 2115/G/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Fossil frames. The Fossil Fos 2115/G/S sunglasses combine a classic cat-eye silhouette with modern, subtle details. The thick plastic rims are hypoallergenic and sturdy, while the slim steel cores keep the glasses lightweight but durable. Wide set rivet detail at the endpoints adds retro appeal to these chic shades. For effortlessness every day, reach for these cool cat-eye sunglasses from Fossil. Fossil eyewear for men and women draws from vintage and contemporary urban style influences for inspired frames that lend a distinctive panache to any look. Discover casual looks you’ll love to wear for sunny day driving and weekdays at the office in our collection of Fossil eyewear: These frames elevate your everyday style.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/fossil-fos-2115-g-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(486, 'Armani Exchange AX4118S', 'Armani Exchange', 'Sunglasses', 82.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Armani-Exchange-AX4118S-Shiny-Black-81586X-Light-Violet-Mirror-Rose-Gold-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Armani Exchange AX4118S Sunglasses now. Step out in style wearing the Armani Exchange AX4118S unisex sunglasses. These rounded shades are flattering on the wearer, and their thick browline and wingtip add visual interest to an otherwise basic silhouette. The lightweight plastic frames keep these shades comfortable while coated edges help ensure they don\'t slip or slide on your nose. For effortlessly cool style every day, reach for these Armani Exchange sunglasses. A|X—or Armani Exchange—eyeglasses for men and women feature an assortment of high-end frames in contemporary styles. The brand is the playful, youthful sibling of the famed Italian brand Giorgio Armani. In stark contrast to the clean-cut, sophisticated tailoring of the luxury Armani label, A|X cites \"street-chic culture, fashionable dance music, freedom, and personal styles\" as its inspirations. Those trendy influences show in this versatile eyewear line that provides luxury in every detail. From a longtime leader in the high-end fashion industry, Armani Exchange makes no compromises on style.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/armani-exchange-ax4118s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(487, 'Wiley X WX Alfa', 'Wiley X', 'Sunglasses', 196.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/WileyX-sunglasses-Alfa-AC6ALF04-Gloss-Crystal-Olive-Bronze-Mirror.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/wileyx-alfa-sunglasses-ac6alf02-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/WileyX-Sunglasses-Alfa-AC6ALF09-Gloss-Clear-Crystal-Polarized-Blue-Mirror-Lenses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/wileyx-alfa-sunglasses-ac6alf18-angle.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Wiley X WX Alfa Sunglasses now. Tough, lightweight, and built for the wild, the WX ALFA delivers ANSI Z87.1+ protection and clear vision for wherever the trail takes you. Wiley X offers multiple collections of eyewear to address eye protection in specific environments. Start with the contemporary frames silhouettes in our collection of Wiley X eyewear, and find options ready for work or play. Browse the Black Ops collection for sleek, modern sunglasses in conventional and prescription-ready styles—or reach for wraparound Wiley X Goggles for the ultimate in eye protection outdoors. Safeguarding your eyes on the job, at home or in the workplace, demands the full-rim frames from Wiley X WorkSight, in lightweight performance materials made to take a beating. Give your active child the same benefits in Wiley X Youth Force eyeglasses and prescription sunglasses, engineered to endure the rough-and-tumble lifestyle of kids. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Wiley X dealer, selling only 100% authentic Wiley X sunglasses frames and lenses. WX lenses, engineered and manufactured to the highest standard, offer sharper, crisper vision for better visual acuity and set the industry standard for toughness. Additional Information: About Wiley X Lenses (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/wiley-x-wx-alfa-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
