(496, 'Vera Wang Chaunte', 'Vera Wang', 'Sunglasses', 303.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/vera-wang-sun-chaunte-matte-black.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/vera-wang-sun-chaunte-rose-gold.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/vera-wang-sun-chaunte-shiny-gold.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Vera Wang Chaunte Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Vera Wang frames. Evoke a glamorous Hollywood starlet in Vera Wang’s Chaunte sunglasses. The frames are made in lightweight metal that\'s strong and durable, with flexible temples that curve inward for a comfortable fit behind the ears. The lenses are coated to block glare while allowing through enough light for optimal vision. With their distinctive browline design, these shades speak to women who prefer an edgy aesthetic with classic roots. For designer sunglasses with vintage style, reach for these Chaunte from Vera Wang. The Vera Wang Optical Collection reflects Vera Wang\'s passion for couture fashion. From sophisticated and classic styles to designs that truly push the envelope, the collection\'s eclectic combination of colors, textures, and designs brings runway inspired styles to every woman who truly loves fashion. The Vera Wang collection is an artistic and modern illustration of how eyeglasses can be so much more than a necessary accessory; eyeglasses can become stunning fashion statements that accentuate any outfit.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/vera-wang-chaunte-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(497, 'Vera Wang Laila', 'Vera Wang', 'Sunglasses', 303.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/vera-wang-sun-laila-bordeaux.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/vera-wang-sun-laila-horn.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Vera Wang Laila Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Vera Wang frames. These Laila sunglasses from Vera Wang are a bold fashion statement. The square frames are made in plastic, which is lightweight and durable. The thick rims feature a unique cutout design around the eyes for an edgy look. For refined taste with an urban vibe, reach for these cool shades by Vera Wang. The Vera Wang Optical Collection reflects Vera Wang\'s passion for couture fashion. From sophisticated and classic styles to designs that truly push the envelope, the collection\'s eclectic combination of colors, textures, and designs brings runway inspired styles to every woman who truly loves fashion. The Vera Wang collection is an artistic and modern illustration of how eyeglasses can be so much more than a necessary accessory; eyeglasses can become stunning fashion statements that accentuate any outfit.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/vera-wang-laila-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(498, 'Ted Baker TWS163', 'Ted Baker', 'Sunglasses', 235.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ted-Baker-sun-TWS163-blush-BLS.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ted Baker TWS163 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Ted Baker frames. Dress to impress with a pair of Ted Baker TWS163 sunglasses. The cat-eye frames on these flattering shades are crafted in hypoallergenic plastic that’s lightweight, durable, and resistant to corrosion and breakage. The sleek temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, bringing out your inner fashionista wearing these chic sunglasses from Ted Baker. From it\'s beginning as a clothier in Glasglow, Ted Baker has had an unwavering focus on attention to detail, fine quality, and a unique sense of fashion. Ted Baker\'s strong style convictions are obvious in all of Ted Baker\'s eyewear designs. Ted Baker frames cover every aspect of eyewear styling, from timeless sophistication to quirky retro revival and everything in between.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ted-baker-tws163-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(499, 'Ted Baker TWS164', 'Ted Baker', 'Sunglasses', 235.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ted-Baker-sun-TWS164-yellow-YEL.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ted Baker TWS164 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Ted Baker frames. Ted Baker puts a bold contemporary spin on the classic cat-eye in these TWS164 sunglasses for women. The oversized frames are made in lightweight, lustrous plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to heavy use. The robust temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for stability behind the ears. These chic shades from Ted Baker add elegance. From it\'s beginning as a clothier in Glasglow, Ted Baker has had an unwavering focus on attention to detail, fine quality, and a unique sense of fashion. Ted Baker\'s strong style convictions are obvious in all of Ted Baker\'s eyewear designs. Ted Baker frames cover every aspect of eyewear styling, from timeless sophistication to quirky retro revival and everything in between.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ted-baker-tws164-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
