(501, 'Ted Baker TWS162', 'Ted Baker', 'Sunglasses', 235.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ted-Baker-sun-TWS162-Gold-Ivory-GLD.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ted Baker TWS162 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Ted Baker frames. From it\'s beginning as a clothier in Glasglow, Ted Baker has had an unwavering focus on attention to detail, fine quality, and a unique sense of fashion. Ted Baker\'s strong style convictions are obvious in all of Ted Baker\'s eyewear designs. Ted Baker frames cover every aspect of eyewear styling, from timeless sophistication to quirky retro revival and everything in between.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ted-baker-tws162-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(502, 'Police SPLD46', 'Police', 'Sunglasses', 200.20, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/police-sunglasses-SPLD46-silver.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/police-sunglasses-SPLD46-gold-crystal.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/police-sunglasses-SPLD46-black-gold.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Police SPLD46 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Police frames. Police offers a bold and distinctive look with the SPLD46 sunglasses for men. These square frames are made in metal, which is lightweight and durable, perfect for sunglasses you\'ll wear every day. The thick rims feature an intricate wirecore construction that keeps them rigid while maintaining a comfortable feel. A keyhole at the upper rim draws attention to your mouth, while thin bands around each lens adds visual interest to these Police sunglasses. For eye-catching style wherever you go, opt for these square Police shades.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/police-spld46-sunglasses', NULL, NULL);
