(503, 'Chopard SCH319M', 'Chopard', 'Sunglasses', 649.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Chopard-sun-SCH319M-shiny-grey-havana-0BLK.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Chopard-sun-SCH319M-brown0745.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Chopard-sun-SCH319M-white09ff.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Chopard SCH319M Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Chopard frames. These stylish SCH319M sunglasses from Chopard offer a retro aesthetic that’s both sophisticated and eye-catching. The square rims are crafted in hypoallergenic metal that\'s strong, durable, and corrosion-resistant. The metal temples grow slightly wider at the tips for added stability behind the ears, with soft plastic socks over the ears for increased warmth and comfort. Get an elegant touch with these exceptional shades from Chopard.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/chopard-sch319m-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
