(507, 'Via Spiga 425-SC', 'Via Spiga', 'Sunglasses', 182.50, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/via-spiga-sun-425sc-black-gold500.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Via Spiga 425-SC Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Via Spiga frames. These Via Spiga 425-SC sunglasses are the perfect combination of style and function. The round frames are crafted in metal, which is both lightweight and durable. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and boast a sleek design near the brow end for added appeal. With chic rims and sleek lines, these women’s round sunglasses from Via Spiga speak to the fashion-forward designer wearer, a modern take on timeless style that\'s unmistakably cool.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/via-spiga-425-sc-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(508, 'Saint Laurent SL 534', 'Saint Laurent', 'Sunglasses', 505.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/saint-laurent-sunglasses-SL534-001.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Saint Laurent SL 534 Sunglasses now. Maison Saint Laurent offers a fashion-forward approach to classic rectangular sunglasses in these SL 534 frames. The unusual lens shape is inspired by the vintage look but designed for modern tastes, more squared than circular, with slightly curved upper rims that complement high cheekbones and a strong jawline. The plastic frames are lightweight and comfortable, yet sturdy enough to last through years of wear. An elegant touch is added to these timeless shades from Saint Laurent. The Saint Laurent eyewear collection places minimalist and convention-dodging glasses designs side by side. This acclaimed luxury fashion house infuses each piece with the glamour of Paris, and Saint Laurent sunglasses and eyeglasses for men and women are no exception.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/saint-laurent-sl-534-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(509, 'Costa Paunch', 'Costa', 'Sunglasses', 272.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Paunch-Matte-Smoke-Crystal-904904-Green-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Paunch-Black-904903-Gray-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Paunch-Black-904909-Gold-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Paunch-Black-904901-Blue-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Paunch-Tortoise-904907-Gray-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Paunch-Tortoise-904906-Green-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Paunch-Black-904908-Gray-Gradient-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Costa-Paunch-Matte-Smoke-Crystal-904905-Blue-Mirror-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Costa Paunch Sunglasses now. Costa delivers a bold, fashion-forward silhouette in the Paunch sunglasses for men. The rectangular frames are made in lightweight, durable plastic that’s designed to stand up to wear and tear throughout your busy days. The thick temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, with added appeal. With their large rims, these sunglasses offer excellent protection against glare while you enjoy outdoor activities or relax by the water on sunny days. Costa eyewear is made for those with an active lifestyle, bringing a healthy dose of fashion to the beach or trailhead. Polarized sunglasses, eyeglasses, and C-Mates bifocal readers by Costa will help you navigate in any direction your adventure leads. Created by fisherman for fisherman in the late 1980s, Costa continues to create quality sunglasses and eyeglasses with innovative technologies. These performance glasses were \"born on the water,\" and they’re made to last—each pair is a worthy investment. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Costa dealer, selling only 100% authentic Costa 580 polarized lenses with its sunglasses, prescription sunglasses, and readers frames. Costa brings you the best of both worlds—innovative lens technology paired with authentic Costa frames for any outdoor adventure. Additional Information: Costa Lens Colors and Materials (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/costa-paunch-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(510, 'Ted Baker TMS091', 'Ted Baker', 'Sunglasses', 235.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ted-Baker-sun-TMS091-red-tort-RED.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ted Baker TMS091 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Ted Baker frames. Ted Baker crafts these TMS091 sunglasses for the man who appreciates high-quality designer accessories. The square rims are crafted in strong, lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to heavy wear. The slim temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for stability behind the ears. A subtle stitch pattern adds visual interest to the shiny opaque shades while helping to reduce glare when you\'re on sunny patrol. For hip style with staying power, step out in these Ted Baker sunglasses. From it\'s beginning as a clothier in Glasglow, Ted Baker has had an unwavering focus on attention to detail, fine quality, and a unique sense of fashion. Ted Baker\'s strong style convictions are obvious in all of Ted Baker\'s eyewear designs. Ted Baker frames cover every aspect of eyewear styling, from timeless sophistication to quirky retro revival and everything in between.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ted-baker-tms091-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(511, 'Kaenon Lido', 'Kaenon', 'Sunglasses', 100.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Kaenon-sun-Lido-073MBMBGN-G120.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Kaenon-sun-Lido-073DPTOGN-B120.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Kaenon-sun-Lido-073DPTOGN-G120.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/kaenon-lido-sunglasses-073totoglgren-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/kaenon-lido-sunglasses-073totoglb120-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/kaenon-lido-sunglasses-073totoglgdgd-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Kaenon-sun-Lido-073CHPAGL-B120.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/kaenon-lido-sunglasses-seaglassug12-angle.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Kaenon Lido Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Kaenon frames. Kaenon Lido sunglasses offer a unique square profile. These unisex sunglasses are constructed from plastic, which makes them lightweight and durable, ideal for sunny days on the beach or by the pool. The skull temples curve inward gently to keep the Lidos in place even when you\'re swimming. A keyhole at each corner of the lenses reveals your eye color while protecting it from glare and wind-caused eyesight problems. For comfortable square sunglasses with a vintage vibe, choose the Kaenon Lido.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/kaenon-lido-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(512, 'Ralph Lauren RL8202B', 'Ralph Lauren', 'Sunglasses', 264.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ralph-lauren-sun-RL8202B-5544V6.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ralph-Lauren-RL8202B-Shiny-Navy-Blue-546519-Gradient-Blue-Clear-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ralph-lauren-sun-RL8202B-5001V6.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ralph Lauren RL8202B Sunglasses now. The Ralph Lauren RL8202B sunglasses for women offer a fashionable take on the classic 1980s-style rounded silhouette. The metal rims are strong and corrosion-resistant, while plastic temples are lightweight and durable. These stylish shades draw attention to their cool aesthetic, round edges and all. For timeless style that endures through the years, reach for these chic sunglasses. The Ralph Lauren brand has been creating sophisticated and timeless styles since its inception in 1970. Ralph Lauren designs celebrate the refined luxury and understated elegance that is at the heart of American fashion. Ralph Lauren makes eyewear that is attractive and elegant, and Ralph Lauren\'s distinctive luxury is reflected in every frame. Ralph Lauren\'s contemporary styles and homage to vintage designs contribute to each frame\'s clean lines, subtle glamour, and uncomplicated class.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ralph-lauren-rl8202b-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
