(547, 'Michael Kors MK1128J', 'Michael Kors', 'Sunglasses', 193.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Michael-Kors-MK1128J-10148G-Sunglasses_030A.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Michael Kors MK1128J Sunglasses now. Love the look of classic sunglasses but hate all the fuss and muss that comes with them? Michael Kors has a solution: glamour-meets-function in these MK1128J sunglasses. The metal frames are hypoallergenic, lightweight, and durable for lasting beauty. Their wingtips curve inward for stability behind the ears, and come coated with socks over the tips to keep them from slipping during active pursuits. Step out in style wearing these cool shades from Michael Kors. The sophisticated Michael Kors eyewear collection presents classic elegance to suit a variety of tastes. Frames by this celebrated designer exude a timeless appeal to complement modern wardrobes, but plenty of daring, trendsetting styles appear throughout the collection. From the modern, clean eyeglasses to the chic, wearable outerwear parading down the runways, Michael Kors continues to be a popular choice with those seeking accessible luxury.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/michael-kors-mk1128j-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
