(553, 'Tory Burch TY7187U', 'Tory Burch', 'Sunglasses', 191.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Tory-Burch-TY7187U-170987-Sunglasses_030A.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Tory-Burch-TY7187U-189073-Sunglasses_030A.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Tory-Burch-TY7187U-Black-170981-Dark-Grey-Polar-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Tory Burch TY7187U Sunglasses now. A modern take on a ’60s silhouette, the Tory Burch TY7187U sunglasses are perfect for women who appreciate designer style with timeless elements. The rectangular rims are graceful and sophisticated, while double bridges add retro appeal. Crafted in lightweight plastic, these comfortable shades offer optimal flexibility and durability, even when you\'re on-the-go. Chic appeal is added to these cool sunnies. Our collection of Tory Burch designer eyewear for women offers bold, stunning frames that blend classic and contemporary influences. Discover sunglasses and eyeglasses frames in a range of chic silhouettes, including oval, cat-eye, rectangular, square, and round styles. Tory Burch eyewear comes in lustrous acetate, corrosion-resistant Monel metal, and other durable and lightweight materials. Within our Tory Burch eyewear line you\'ll find versatile solid hues, refined two-toned glasses, and vibrant color combinations that capture attention.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/tory-burch-ty7187u-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
