(571, 'Vera Wang V611', 'Vera Wang', 'Sunglasses', 263.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD__0000s_0277_V611_BK.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD__0000s_0279_V611_TO.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD__0000s_0283_V611_CT.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD__0000s_0281_V611_IV.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Vera Wang V611 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Vera Wang frames. The Vera Wang Optical Collection reflects Vera Wang\'s passion for couture fashion. From sophisticated and classic styles to designs that truly push the envelope, the collection\'s eclectic combination of colors, textures, and designs brings runway inspired styles to every woman who truly loves fashion. The Vera Wang collection is an artistic and modern illustration of how eyeglasses can be so much more than a necessary accessory; eyeglasses can become stunning fashion statements that accentuate any outfit.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/vera-wang-v611-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(572, 'Vera Wang V607', 'Vera Wang', 'Sunglasses', 263.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD__0000s_0276_V607_GR.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD__0000s_0272_V607_TO.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD__0000s_0274_V607_HN.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Vera Wang V607 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Vera Wang frames. The Vera Wang Optical Collection reflects Vera Wang\'s passion for couture fashion. From sophisticated and classic styles to designs that truly push the envelope, the collection\'s eclectic combination of colors, textures, and designs brings runway inspired styles to every woman who truly loves fashion. The Vera Wang collection is an artistic and modern illustration of how eyeglasses can be so much more than a necessary accessory; eyeglasses can become stunning fashion statements that accentuate any outfit.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/vera-wang-v607-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(573, 'Vera Wang V609', 'Vera Wang', 'Sunglasses', 263.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD__0000s_0290_V609_GR.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD__0000s_0286_V609_TO.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD__0000s_0292_V609_CT.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD__0000s_0288_V609_IV.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Vera Wang V609 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Vera Wang frames. The Vera Wang Optical Collection reflects Vera Wang\'s passion for couture fashion. From sophisticated and classic styles to designs that truly push the envelope, the collection\'s eclectic combination of colors, textures, and designs brings runway inspired styles to every woman who truly loves fashion. The Vera Wang collection is an artistic and modern illustration of how eyeglasses can be so much more than a necessary accessory; eyeglasses can become stunning fashion statements that accentuate any outfit.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/vera-wang-v609-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(574, 'Trina Turk Micalo', 'Trina Turk', 'Sunglasses', 207.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/trina-turk-MICALO-azul.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Trina Turk Micalo Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Trina Turk frames. Trina Turk combines a classic square silhouette and retro wingtip details in these Micalo sunglasses for women. The thick, plastic rims are robust, while metal accents on the ends of the slim temples add elegance. A row of small rhinestones adds eye-catching glamour to the brow end of the frames. For distinctive style that stands out from the crowd, choose these cool shades from Trina Turk.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/trina-turk-micalo-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
