(582, 'Badgley Mischka Angelie', 'Badgley Mischka', 'Sunglasses', 225.40, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/badgley-sun-ANGELIE-blue.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/badgley-sun-ANGELIE-mauve.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Badgley Mischka Angelie Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Badgley Mischka frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/badgley-mischka-angelie-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(583, 'Maui Jim One Way - 875', 'Maui Jim', 'Sunglasses', 289.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/One-Way-875-14-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/One-Way-RM875-02-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/One-Way-B875-03-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/One-Way-H875-10-Quarter.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Maui Jim One Way - 875 Sunglasses now. Maui Jim has led the eyewear industry by design and innovation since 1980, offering eyes everywhere superior protection from the harmful rays of the sun in its popular line of sunglasses. From iconic shades with patented technologies, to readers perfect for sunny-day pastimes, to the impressively stylish and comfortable daily-wear frames in the Optical line, Maui Jim creates men’s and women’s performance eyewear for any scenario. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Maui Jim dealer, selling only 100% authentic Maui Jim sunglasses frames and lenses. Polarized with an anti-reflective coating, Maui Jim lenses reveal the vibrant colors of the world while protecting your eyes from the effects of the sun\'s harsh glare and harmful rays. Satisfaction guaranteed. Additional Information: Maui Lens Colors Information (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/maui-jim-one-way-875-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
