(636, 'Chopard SCH354V', 'Chopard', 'Sunglasses', 850.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/chopard-SCH354V-shiny-black-700.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/chopard-SCH354V-brown-yellow-havana-0743.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Chopard SCH354V Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Chopard frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/chopard-sch354v-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(637, 'Persol PO1935S', 'Persol', 'Sunglasses', 333.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Persol-PO1935S-95-31-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Persol-PO1935S-108-56-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Persol PO1935S Sunglasses now. Persol eyewear is among the most well respected and distinguished eyewear brands in the world. Each attractive and comfortable frame is expertly hand crafted in Lauriano, Italy. Persol eyewear is made of only the highest quality materials. Persol\'s Meflecto system gives each Persol frame a patented \"flexible stem\" that makes Persol glasses frames among the most comfortable on the market. Persol\'s ultra-stylish frames and unparalleled craftsmanship make Persol popular with musicians, actors, and cultural icons. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Persol retailer, selling only 100% authentic Persol eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you love: each Persol frame comes with original brand markings certified by Persol itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/persol-po1935s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
