(649, 'Lafont Merveille', 'Lafont', 'Sunglasses', 769.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/lafont-sun-MERVEILLE-golden-1521.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/lafont-sun-MERVEILLE-black-1518.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/lafont-sun-MERVEILLE-red-6531.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/LaFont-Sun-Lafont-Merveille-Blue-035.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Lafont Merveille Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Lafont frames. The Lafont eyewear collection features refined silhouettes with a bit of attitude—discover designer eyewear to suit your tastes, whether your style leans retro, contemporary, or classic. Chic in any shape, Lafont frames come in round, rectangular, oval, square, wayfarer, and cat-eye silhouettes. The carefully chosen materials Lafont uses in its designs include acetate, carbon fiber, impact-resistant plastic, stainless steel, metal inlay, and others. This eyewear collection boasts playful patterns and florals, tortoiseshell, and solids in bright or subtle hues, many of which are Lafont exclusives.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/lafont-merveille-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
