(656, 'Gucci GG0998S', 'Gucci', 'Sunglasses', 430.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Gucci-GG0998S-001-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Gucci-GG0998S-005-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Gucci GG0998S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Gucci frames. Founded in Florence, Italy, in 1921, Gucci is one of the world\'s leading luxury brands. Following the House\'s centenary, Gucci forges ahead into the next hundred years, continuing to redefine luxury while celebrating the creativity, Italian craftsmanship, and innovation at the core of its values. Gucci is part of the global luxury group Kering, which manages the development of a series of renowned Houses in fashion, leather goods, jewelry, and eyewear. Discover more about Gucci at www.gucci.com . The latest range of sunglasses and optical frames embodies Gucci\'s signature designs. Drawing inspiration from the archive of the House, the eyewear collection combines emblematic codes with new details in an unexpected selection of shapes and styles.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/gucci-gg0998s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL);
