(709, 'Oakley Encoder Strike', 'Oakley', 'Sunglasses', 314.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Encoder-Strike-Black-Ink-923517-Prizm-Road-Black-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Encoder-Strike-Fern-Swirl-923514-Prizm-Road-Black-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Encoder-Strike-Matte-Black-923501-Prizm-Black-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Encoder-Strike-Matte-Black-923502-Prizm-Road-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Encoder-Strike-Gamma-Green-923504-Prizm-Jade-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Encoder-Strike-Matte-Black-923505-Prizm-Sapphire-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Encoder-Strike-Matte-Copper-Patina-923515-Prizm-Black-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Encoder-Strike-Matte-Carbon-923506-Prizm-24K-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley Encoder Strike Sunglasses now. The Oakley Encoder Strike sunglasses offer a bold, sporty look. The monochromatic frames are made from O Matter, a lightweight plastic that provides durability and comfort. Three stripes of ceramic at the top of the lens add color to these shades while also making them more resistant to high temperatures and impact. With Unobtainium components at the tips, these men’s sunglasses stay securely in place as you move through your day. The Oakley brand is universally recognized and is synonymous with innovative, quality craftsmanship. Oakley is a leading name in sports sunglasses because it offers athletes stylish shades that are made with cutting edge design and technology so that it not only looks good but can also withstand harsh environments and truly extreme conditions. Oakley has perfected sporty wrap sunglasses and shields and has modernized interpret