(735, 'Fila Sunglasses SFI447', 'Fila Sunglasses', 'Sunglasses', 98.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/fila-sun-SFI447-black-0700.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/fila-sun-SFI447-havana-OC10.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Fila Sunglasses SFI447 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Fila Sunglasses frames. Gear up for an active day in the sun wearing the Fila Sunglasses SFI447 sunglasses. These square frames are made from a lightweight, durable plastic that’s designed to stand up to wear and tear over time. The skull temples curve inward gently to keep the shades from slipping during your activities. A subtle keyhole at the top of each lens shows off your facial features while protecting them from glare on sunny days outdoors, or when you’re sitting near a bright window indoors. For stylish sunglasses that perform as well as they look, reach for these cool shades.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/fila-sunglasses-sfi447-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(736, 'Lilly Pulitzer Cape Cod', 'Lilly Pulitzer', 'Sunglasses', 243.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD-0000s-0316-Cape-Cod-CN.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD-0000s-0312-Cape-Cod-YG.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD-0000s-0314-Cape-Cod-SI.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Lilly Pulitzer Cape Cod Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Lilly Pulitzer frames. These Cape Cod sunglasses from Lilly Pulitzer are a perfect example of the designer’s playful, feminine aesthetic. The rounded edges and slightly upswept browline lend an air of sophistication to this chic design. Crafted in metal, these frames are lightweight but sturdy, ensuring that you enjoy comfort throughout your day wearing these sunnies. A banded upper rim adds visual interest to the lenses behind it while keeping them safely set against the cheekbone. For glamour with a touch of fun, reach for these Cape Cod sunglasses from Lilly Pulitzer.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/lilly-pulitzer-cape-cod-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(737, 'Police SPLL36', 'Police', 'Sunglasses', 200.20, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/police-sun-SPLL36-dark-green-06WT.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/police-sun-SPLL36-black-700.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/police-sun-SPLL36-multilayeyr-havana-0993.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Police SPLL36 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Police frames. Police SPLL36 sunglasses for women exude a stylish, sporty look. The square frames are made in lightweight, durable plastic that’s strong enough to keep up on your busiest days. The thin temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for added stability behind the ears. Enjoy elevated styling wherever you go wearing these square-frame SPLL36 shades from Police.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/police-spll36-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(738, 'Vera Bradley Seville', 'Vera Bradley', 'Sunglasses', 160.89, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/verabradley-SEVILLE-cloud-vine-multi.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/verabradley-SEVILLE-enchated-mandala.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Vera Bradley Seville Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Vera Bradley frames. Step out in style wearing the Vera Bradley Seville sunglasses. These square shades are crafted from lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to your busy lifestyle. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, with added appeal. Show off your refined taste in designer fashion when you opt for these chic sunglasses from Vera Bradley.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/vera-bradley-seville-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(739, 'Vera Bradley Paloma', 'Vera Bradley', 'Sunglasses', 160.89, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/verabradley-PALOMA-sunlight-garden-sage.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/verabradley-PALOMA-cloud-vine-multi.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Vera Bradley Paloma Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Vera Bradley frames. These Paloma sunglasses from Vera Bradley ensure your look is on-trend and sophisticated. The round frames are made in lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to wear after wear. The slim temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears. Enjoy effortlessness every day when you opt for these stylish sunglasses by Vera Bradley.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/vera-bradley-paloma-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(740, 'Police SPLL35', 'Police', 'Sunglasses', 200.20, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/police-sun-SPLL35-black-700.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/police-sun-SPLL35-havana-green-07NV.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Police SPLL35 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Police frames. Police SPLL35 sunglasses for women are cool and comfortable. These oval frames are made in lightweight, durable plastic that’s designed to stand up to wear and tear over time. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears. If you\'re looking for shades that offer both style and substance, reach for these Police sunglasses.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/police-spll35-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(741, 'Carrera CARDUC-006/S', 'Carrera', 'Sunglasses', 250.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/carrera-sun-CARDUC006S-matte-black-0003M9.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/carrera-sun-CARDUC006S-black-0807IR.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Carrera CARDUC-006/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Carrera frames. These men’s Carrera CARDUC-006/S sunglasses boast a sporty aesthetic. The oval frames are made in a lightweight metal that\'s durable enough to keep up on your busiest days. The slim temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for stability behind the ears. Make a statement wearing these cool sunglasses. Carrera eyewear for men, women, and children is easily identifiable by its bold sunglass silhouettes and streamlined eyeglass designs; this label has been a steadfast name in eyewear since 1956, first producing protective sports goggles.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/carrera-carduc-006-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(742, 'Lulu Guinness L184', 'Lulu Guinness', 'Sunglasses', 316.50, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/lulu-sun-L184-slate-pink.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/lulu-sun-L184-red-black.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Lulu Guinness L184 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Lulu Guinness frames. For a bold look with retro flair, reach for the Lulu Guinness L184 sunglasses. These square frames are made in lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to everyday wear. The slim temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for stability behind the ears. Enjoy sunny weather in comfort wearing these stylish sunglasses from Lulu Guinness.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/lulu-guinness-l184-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(743, 'Harley-Davidson HD0983X', 'Harley-Davidson', 'Sunglasses', 130.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/harley-davidson-sun-HD0983X-matte-blue-smoke-91D.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/harley-davidson-sun-HD0983X-grey-smoke-20D.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/harley-davidson-sun-HD0983X-matte-black-smoke-02D.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Harley-Davidson HD0983X Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Harley-Davidson frames. Gear up for adventure with the Harley-Davidson HD0983X sunglasses. These bold, rectangular shades are made from strong, lightweight plastic that’s designed to stand up to wear and tear. The skull temples curve inward gently to keep the glasses from slipping during your extreme activities, these shades will stay put. A subtle keyhole at the upper rim adds interest to an otherwise classic rectangular silhouette. For eye-catching style wherever you go, opt for these cool sunglasses bearing the iconic H-D insignia from Harley-Davidson. Our Harley-Davidson optical and sunwear collections embody the gritty appeal of Harley-Davidson and the sharp, stylish designs of a culture that truly represents cutting edge American fashion. The Harley-Davidson collection pays homage to iconic American styles while adding its own twists and accents. Most frames come with either a classic Harley-Davidson bar-and-shield logo or with the Willie G. skull collection logo. Harley-Davidson offers a variety of frame shapes and colors in order for each Harley rider and fanatic to clearly express what styles drives them.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/harley-davidson-hd0983x-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(744, 'Lulu Guinness L186', 'Lulu Guinness', 'Sunglasses', 316.50, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/lulu-sun-L186-blush-pink.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Lulu Guinness L186 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Lulu Guinness frames. These L186 frames from Lulu Guinness add a touch of vintage glamour to everyday sunglasses. The cat-eye frames are made in lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to wear after wear. The slim stems feature an eye-catching pattern and curve inward gently for added stability behind the ears. With designer fashion and style, these sunglasses can take you through sunny skies and raindrops.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/lulu-guinness-l186-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(745, 'Lilly Pulitzer Huntington', 'Lilly Pulitzer', 'Sunglasses', 243.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD-0000s-0310-Huntington-BK.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD-0000s-0308-Huntington-BL.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD-0000s-0306-Huntington-PK.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Lilly Pulitzer Huntington Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Lilly Pulitzer frames. The Lilly Pulitzer Huntington sunglasses offer a fun, on-trend aesthetic. The square frames are made in lightweight plastic that’s strong enough to keep up on your sunny day adventures. The slim wire cores and coated temple tips ensure these shades stay put while you enjoy outdoor activities like beach volleyball or deep sea fishing. For sunny days filled with adventure, reach for the Huntington from Lilly Pulitzer.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/lilly-pulitzer-huntington-sunglasses', NULL, NULL);
