(746, 'Lulu Guinness L187', 'Lulu Guinness', 'Sunglasses', 316.50, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/lulu-sun-L187-black-white.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Lulu Guinness L187 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Lulu Guinness frames. These L187 frames from Lulu Guinness are an aviator-style pair of sunglasses, with a classic silhouette. The metal rims are hypoallergenic, lightweight, and durable, with curved sides for a feminine look. The slim wirecore temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears. With unique floral detailing on the lensbridge, these sunglasses exude vintage style wherever you go.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/lulu-guinness-l187-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
