(749, 'Polo PH4192', 'Polo', 'Sunglasses', 186.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Polo-PH4192-541387-Sunglasses_030A.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Polo-PH4192-608487-Sunglasses_030A.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Polo-Ralph-Lauren-PH4192-Shiny-Transparent-Pinot-Grey-503480-Light-Azure-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Polo PH4192 Sunglasses now. For a fresh, on-trend look, reach for these Polo PH4192 sunglasses for men. The round rims are crafted in lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to wear after wear. The thick temples curve inward softly and widen at the tips for added stability behind the ears. Enjoy clean design when you step out in these Polo sunglasses. Unmatched attention to detail and exacting production standards result in designer frames that are beautiful and comfortable to wear, and that last through weekday and weekend living. Explore our line of Polo eyewear for men, women, and kids featuring stylish frames in rectangular, oval, and square shapes to suit your preferred style. Cat-eye frames in flirty hues make a charming accessory, while round tortoiseshell glasses lend a dapper touch.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/polo-ph4192-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(750, 'Electric Marin', 'Electric', 'Sunglasses', 175.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/electric-sun-MARIN-gloss-black-grey-EE20701642.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/electric-sun-MARIN-darkside-tort-grey-EE20762342.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/electric-sun-MARIN-gloss-tort-bronze-EE20710643.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/electric-sun-MARIN-EE20775843.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Electric Marin Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Electric frames. The Electric Marin sunglasses offer a fun, youthful look. The square frames are made in lightweight plastic that’s strong enough to keep up on your busiest days. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears and feature a unique design near the brow end for added appeal. With their unique square silhouette, these cool shades from Electric add some pop to your everyday look.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/electric-marin-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(751, 'Vogue Junior VJ2020', 'Vogue Junior', 'Sunglasses', 52.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Vogue-Jr-VJ2020-303287-Sunglasses_030A.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Vogue-Jr-VJ2020-306473-Sunglasses_030A.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Vogue Junior VJ2020 Sunglasses now. Vogue Junior VJ2020 sunglasses add a touch of youthful style to your look. These cat-eye shades feature plastic rims, making them lightweight and comfortable to wear. The flexible frames adjust easily for a custom fit, while coated temple tips ensure these shades stay put when you\'re on the move. Show off your impeccable taste in fashion wearing these chic sunglasses designed for children by Vogue Junior. Explore the Vogue collection to find fashion-forward eyewear that suits any woman’s wardrobe—from refined to daring, Vogue makes a frame style for every taste. The collection, including sunglasses and eyeglasses styles from the Gigi Hadid X Vogue collaboration, is a study in contrasts: Vogue includes bold, oversized frames in striking colors together with sleek metal frames in narrow silhouettes. A variety of styles meet in the middle with the perfect combination of classic, uncomplicated, and chic elements.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/vogue-junior-vj2020-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(752, 'Versace VE4444U', 'Versace', 'Sunglasses', 363.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Versace-VE4444U-5355AK-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Versace-VE4444U-5408V9-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Versace VE4444U Sunglasses now. Wear Versace VE4444U sunglasses for women to stand out from the crowd. The bold rectangular frames are made in lightweight, durable plastic that is strong enough to keep up on your busiest days. The distinctive head-turning design features a metallic band at the brow end, showcasing your impeccable taste and sophistication when you step out. Extravagant designs and bold embellishments feature prominently on the frames in the Versace eyewear collection. Versace\'s haute couture expertise shines in this collection of designer sunglasses and prescription eyewear for men and women. Rx-ready frames in sun and optical styles offer an opportunity to showcase your personal style in eyewear tailored with your prescription. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Versace retailer, selling only 100% authentic Versace eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you love: each Versace frame comes with original brand markings certified by Versace itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/versace-ve4444u-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(753, 'Carolina Herrera CH-0061/S', 'Carolina Herrera', 'Sunglasses', 216.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Carolina-Herrera-sun-CH-0061S-burgundy-nude-0C193X.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Carolina-Herrera-sun-CH-0061S-black-nude-0KDX9O.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Carolina Herrera CH-0061/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Carolina Herrera frames. The Carolina Herrera CH-0061/S sunglasses for women exude a classic Hollywood vibe. These glamorous shades feature elegant lines and chic details, resulting in an unmistakably sophisticated look. The rounded rims are made in hypoallergenic plastic that’s lightweight but sturdy, with double rivet details at the endpoints for added appeal. The slim temples grow slightly wider at the tips for added stability behind the ears. Enjoy timeless style when you opt for these chic Carolina Herrera sunglasses.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/carolina-herrera-ch-0061-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
