(779, 'Burberry BE4389 -Joni', 'Burberry', 'Sunglasses', 373.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Burberry-BE4389-300187-Sunglasses_030A.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Burberry-BE4389-406113-Sunglasses_030A.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Burberry-Joni-Spotted-Horn-350173-Bronze-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Burberry BE4389 -Joni Sunglasses now. These BE4389 -Joni sunglasses from Burberry boast square rims crafted in hypoallergenic plastic. The lightweight frames make these shades comfortable to wear, while their thick ribs provide durability and strength. These cool square sunglasses for women offer a modern twist on a retro vibe. Throughout Burberry\'s 150 year history, it has become one of the most famous and recognizable names in fashion, not to mention eyewear. Burberry is dedicated to providing the highest quality products and materials so that its eyeglass frames maintain the legacy of fashion, elegance, and style for which Burberry is known. Classic styling and traditional designs are meshed with modern accents and youthful influences to make Burberry a company that never sacrifices style to maintain its high standards.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/burberry-be4389-joni-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(780, 'Chloe CH0120S', 'Chloe', 'Sunglasses', 375.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/chloe-ch0120s-sunglasses-004.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/chloe-ch0120s-sunglasses-003.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Chloe CH0120S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Chloe frames. These women’s CH0120S sunglasses from Chloe are stylish and functional. The square rims are crafted in hypoallergenic plastic that\'s lightweight but sturdy, resulting in comfortable sunglasses you can wear all day long. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and offer classic styling near the brow end for added appeal. Enjoy clean design when you opt for these chic glasses from Chloe. Founded in Paris in 1952 by Gaby Aghion, Chloé has always drawn inspiration from a romantic, feminine aesthetic to inform its design. Reaching worldwide popularity as part one of the biggest fashion brands of the 1970s, Chloé continues its legacy as an influential, timelessly feminine design house today. Chloé eyewear leans heavily on its history, with many of its early eyewear designs referencing popular 1970s styles, and simultaneously leading the way in modern fashion eyewear creations.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/chloe-ch0120s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(781, 'Burberry BE4390 - Meadow', 'Burberry', 'Sunglasses', 352.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Burberry-BE4390-408680-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Burberry-BE4390-30018G-Sunglasses_030A.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Burberry-BE4390-406793-Sunglasses_030A.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Burberry BE4390 - Meadow Sunglasses now. Step out in style wearing the Burberry BE4390 Meadow sunglasses. The round rims are crafted from hypoallergenic plastic that’s lightweight and durable, perfect for someone who enjoys outdoor activities like hiking or skiing. The slim temples grow slightly wider at the tips for stability behind the ears, with added appeal. Embrace luxury fashion with these chic shades from Burberry, maker of fine accessories since 1856. Throughout Burberry\'s 150 year history, it has become one of the most famous and recognizable names in fashion, not to mention eyewear. Burberry is dedicated to providing the highest quality products and materials so that its eyeglass frames maintain the legacy of fashion, elegance, and style for which Burberry is known. Classic styling and traditional designs are meshed with modern accents and youthful influences to make Burberry a company that never sacrifices style to maintain its high standards.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/burberry-be4390-meadow-sunglasses', NULL, NULL);
