(782, 'Versace VE4432U', 'Versace', 'Sunglasses', 384.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Versace-VE4432U-GB187-Sunglasses_030A.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Versace-VE4432U-10873-Sunglasses_030A.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Versace-VE4432U-538887-Sunglasses_030A.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Versace VE4432U Sunglasses now. The women’s Versace VE4432U sunglasses exude a bold attitude that says “I\'m ready to take on the world.” The cat-eye frames are made in lightweight, lustrous plastic that\'s durable enough for your daily wear. The distinctive headrail and Medusa medallions at each end draw attention to your eyes while adding a fashion-forward look. Showcase your taste for luxury when you reach for these unique Versace sunglasses. Extravagant designs and bold embellishments feature prominently on the frames in the Versace eyewear collection. Versace\'s haute couture expertise shines in this collection of designer sunglasses and prescription eyewear for men and women. Rx-ready frames in sun and optical styles offer an opportunity to showcase your personal style in eyewear tailored with your prescription. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Versace retailer, selling only 100% authentic Versace eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you love: each Versace frame comes with original brand markings certified by Versace itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/versace-ve4432u-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(783, 'Arnette AN4318', 'Arnette', 'Sunglasses', 111.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Arnette-AN4318-Black-121487-Dark-Grey-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Arnette-AN4318-Blue-12392H-Fifty-Blue-Orange-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Arnette AN4318 Sunglasses now. Arnette AN4318 sunglasses provides an edgy look for the urbanite. These men’s sunglasses feature rectangular frames made from hypoallergenic, lightweight plastic that\'s durable enough to stand up to wear after wear. The slim temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for added stability behind the ears. Make a statement wearing these Arnette sunglasses. Rebellious, individual, underground, cool: Arnette eyewear captures subversive \'70s Cali surf-skate style with bold lines and audacious shapes. A favored brand of artists, designers, and action-adventurers, Arnette creates daring eyewear for bold personalities.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/arnette-an4318-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(784, 'Armani Exchange AX4133S', 'Armani Exchange', 'Sunglasses', 91.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Armani-Exchange-AX4133S-Matte-Black-807887-Dark-Grey-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Armani-Exchange-AX4133S-Matte-Blue-818180-Dark-Blue-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Armani Exchange AX4133S Sunglasses now. These Armani Exchange AX4133S round-frame sunglasses are the perfect combination of style and practicality. The plastic frames are hypoallergenic, lightweight, and strong, ideal for prolonged wear. The skull temples curve inward gently to keep the sunglasses from slipping during your active lifestyle. They offer a clean design with a subtle hint of elegance, appealing to those who appreciate designer fashion but prefer understated style when it comes to their accessories. A|X—or Armani Exchange—eyeglasses for men and women feature an assortment of high-end frames in contemporary styles. The brand is the playful, youthful sibling of the famed Italian brand Giorgio Armani. In stark contrast to the clean-cut, sophisticated tailoring of the luxury Armani label, A|X cites \"street-chic culture, fashionable dance music, freedom, and personal styles\" as its inspirations. Those trendy influences show in this versatile eyewear line that provides luxury in every detail. From a longtime leader in the high-end fashion industry, Armani Exchange makes no compromises on style.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/armani-exchange-ax4133s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(785, 'Burberry BE4395 -Peter', 'Burberry', 'Sunglasses', 308.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Burberry-BE4395-405880-Sunglasses_030A.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Burberry BE4395 -Peter Sunglasses now. The Burberry BE4395 -Peter sunglasses are a perfect example of the classic square men’s frame. The bold, thick frames are made in hypoallergenic plastic that\'s lightweight, durable, and resistant to heat and cold. The skull temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears and feature a unique design near the brow end for added appeal. For effortlessness every day, reach for these Peter sunglasses from Burberry. Throughout Burberry\'s 150 year history, it has become one of the most famous and recognizable names in fashion, not to mention eyewear. Burberry is dedicated to providing the highest quality products and materials so that its eyeglass frames maintain the legacy of fashion, elegance, and style for which Burberry is known. Classic styling and traditional designs are meshed with modern accents and youthful influences to make Burberry a company that never sacrifices style to maintain its high standards.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/burberry-be4395-peter-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(786, 'Burberry BE4396U - Wren', 'Burberry', 'Sunglasses', 268.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Burberry-BE4396U-300187-Sunglasses_030A.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Burberry-Wren-Blue-405825-Dark-Grey-Ar-Blue-Ext-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Burberry-BE4396U-346487-Sunglasses_030A.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Burberry BE4396U - Wren Sunglasses now. The Burberry BE4396U Wren sunglasses for men exude a classic square silhouette. The bold, thick frames are made in lightweight hypoallergenic plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to heavy wear. The wire-core temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for stability behind the ears, with an added fashion appeal. If you\'re looking to make a statement while enjoying some sunshine outdoors, opt for these cool shades from Burberry. Throughout Burberry\'s 150 year history, it has become one of the most famous and recognizable names in fashion, not to mention eyewear. Burberry is dedicated to providing the highest quality products and materials so that its eyeglass frames maintain the legacy of fashion, elegance, and style for which Burberry is known. Classic styling and traditional designs are meshed with modern accents and youthful influences to make Burberry a company that never sacrifices style to maintain its high standards.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/burberry-be4396u-wren-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(787, 'Armani Exchange AX4130SU', 'Armani Exchange', 'Sunglasses', 76.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Armani-Exchange-AX4130SU-824069-Sunglasses_030A.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Armani Exchange AX4130SU Sunglasses now. Bring out your inner fashionista wearing the Armani Exchange AX4130SU sunglasses. These chic shades flaunt classic cat-eye frames made in hypoallergenic plastic that\'s lightweight and durable, for comfort and longevity. The robust construction keeps the thick rims from warping or losing their shape over time. These cool cat-eye sunglasses from Armani Exchange offer a designer touch. A|X—or Armani Exchange—eyeglasses for men and women feature an assortment of high-end frames in contemporary styles. The brand is the playful, youthful sibling of the famed Italian brand Giorgio Armani. In stark contrast to the clean-cut, sophisticated tailoring of the luxury Armani label, A|X cites \"street-chic culture, fashionable dance music, freedom, and personal styles\" as its inspirations. Those trendy influences show in this versatile eyewear line that provides luxury in every detail. From a longtime leader in the high-end fashion industry, Armani Exchange makes no compromises on style.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/armani-exchange-ax4130su-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(788, 'Persol PO3311S', 'Persol', 'Sunglasses', 370.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Persol-PO3311S-Dark-Burgundy-118753-Violet-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Persol PO3311S Sunglasses now. These Persol PO3311S sunglasses feature a classic aviator-style silhouette with a retro flair. The thick, sturdy rims are made in lightweight, durable plastic for strength and stability. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for a secure fit behind the ears, and their timeless design ensures they are both functional and stylish. Persol eyewear is among the most well respected and distinguished eyewear brands in the world. Each attractive and comfortable frame is expertly hand crafted in Lauriano, Italy. Persol eyewear is made of only the highest quality materials. Persol\'s Meflecto system gives each Persol frame a patented \"flexible stem\" that makes Persol glasses frames among the most comfortable on the market. Persol\'s ultra-stylish frames and unparalleled craftsmanship make Persol popular with musicians, actors, and cultural icons. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Persol retailer, selling only 100% authentic Persol eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you love: each Persol frame comes with original brand markings certified by Persol itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/persol-po3311s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(789, 'Brooks Brothers BB 5048', 'Brooks Brothers', 'Sunglasses', 97.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Brooks-Brothers-BB5048-Olive-Horn-Transparent-Brown-616473-Brown-Solid-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Brooks Brothers BB 5048 Sunglasses now. These men’s BB 5048 sunglasses from Brooks Brothers are a great addition to your everyday look. The square frames are made in hypoallergenic, lightweight plastic that\'s strong and durable. The skull temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and feature coated tips for comfort against the skin. A subtle keyhole at the upper rim adds interest to these classic shades from Brooks Brothers. Enjoy timeless style wherever you go wearing these square-frame sunglasses by Brooks Brothers. Brooks Brothers has been designing men\'s styles for over one hundred and fifty years, and men have relied on Brooks Brothers to outfit them in the best fashions and highest quality materials. Brooks Brothers eyewear is perfectly suited for discerning men who believe that fashion and masculinity are not mutually exclusive. The Brooks Brothers eyewear collections use clean lines and fashionably understated designs to add unwavering sophistication to any outfit.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/brooks-brothers-bb-5048-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(790, 'Zeal Optics Skyway', 'Zeal Optics', 'Sunglasses', 199.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-skyway-sunglasses-12722-quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-skyway-sunglasses-12723-quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-skyway-sunglasses-12724-Quarter.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Zeal Optics Skyway Sunglasses now. Whether you’re going for a casual or sporty look, the Zeal Optics Skyway sunglasses fit the bill. These unisex frames feature metal rims that are both lightweight and durable. The slimline temples curve inward gently to provide stability behind the ears, and boast an innovative texturized rubber coating on the tips for added grip. Show off your adventurous side wearing these bold yet practical sunglasses from Zeal Optics. Explore Zeal Optics and discover striking eyewear offered in classic and contemporary silhouettes, and designed for active wear. Sporty wraparounds and wraparound-inspired rectangles speak to wearers who want a sleek, modern look; those who prefer a more traditional profile will find squares and rounded-edged frames styles. This eyewear comes in an array of colors and patterns to suit a number of tastes; on-trend embellishments like metal accents on the frames, or distinctive cutaways on the temple arms, impart a hint of sophistication to Zeal Optics frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/zeal-optics-skyway-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(791, 'Zeal Optics Hondo', 'Zeal Optics', 'Sunglasses', 179.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-hondo-sunglasses-12678-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-hondo-sunglasses-12679-Quarter.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Zeal Optics Hondo Sunglasses now. Step out in style wearing the Zeal Optics Hondo sunglasses. These unisex shades feature metal rims that are strong and lightweight, with a comfortable fit thanks to their flexible temples. The wirecore construction keeps the lenses thin while maintaining their durability. A coated lens offers increased visibility by blocking glare while allowing through enough light for clear vision, regardless of whether it\'s sunny or snowy. Enjoy your next adventure in comfort and confidence when you slip on these protective Hondo sunglasses from Zeal Optics. Explore Zeal Optics and discover striking eyewear offered in classic and contemporary silhouettes, and designed for active wear. Sporty wraparounds and wraparound-inspired rectangles speak to wearers who want a sleek, modern look; those who prefer a more traditional profile will find squares and rounded-edged frames styles. This eyewear comes in an array of colors and patterns to suit a number of tastes; on-trend embellishments like metal accents on the frames, or distinctive cutaways on the temple arms, impart a hint of sophistication to Zeal Optics frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/zeal-optics-hondo-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(792, 'Marc Jacobs Marc 586/S', 'Marc Jacobs', 'Sunglasses', 236.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Marc-Jacobs-sun-586S-black-08079O.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Marc Jacobs Marc 586/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Marc Jacobs frames. The Marc 586/S sunglasses for men reflect the designer flair and innovation of Marc Jacobs. These square frames are made in lightweight, durable plastic that’s strong enough to keep up on your busiest days. The slim temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for added stability behind the ears. Enjoy innovative design every day when you opt for these square-frame sunglasses by Marc Jacobs. The Marc Jacobs eyewear line has the perfect frames for men and women with eclectic tastes. Marc Jacobs eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses incorporate whimsical touches—think sculptural flowers at the temples, or frames shapes transformed from oval to cat-eye with an artful arc of metal around the lenses. Go bold or go subtle with Marc Jacobs eyewear, with chunky, oversized sunglasses in the mix alongside streamlined everyday glasses that transition effortlessly from work to weekend.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/marc-jacobs-marc-586-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(793, 'Persol PO3307S', 'Persol', 'Sunglasses', 370.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Persol-PO3307S-95-31-Sunglasses_030A.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Persol-PO3307S-Havana-24-31-Green-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Persol-PO3307S-Brown-11743R-Dark-Blue-Polarized-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Persol-PO3307S-Grey-117333-Brown-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Persol PO3307S Sunglasses now. These Persol PO3307S sunglasses offer the wearer a classic look that’s as timeless today as it was when first popularized in the 1940s. The oval frames are made in lightweight, durable plastic that\'s sturdy enough to stand up to wear after wear. The thin temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for added stability behind the ears. If you\'re looking for sunglasses that exude vintage style while staying on-trend today, opt for these timeless oval shades from Persol. Persol eyewear is among the most well respected and distinguished eyewear brands in the world. Each attractive and comfortable frame is expertly hand crafted in Lauriano, Italy. Persol eyewear is made of only the highest quality materials. Persol\'s Meflecto system gives each Persol frame a patented \"flexible stem\" that makes Persol glasses frames among the most comfortable on the market. Persol\'s ultra-stylish frames and unparalleled craftsmanship make Persol popular with musicians, actors, and cultural icons. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Persol retailer, selling only 100% authentic Persol eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you love: each Persol frame comes with original brand markings certified by Persol itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/persol-po3307s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(794, 'Zeal Optics Fillmore', 'Zeal Optics', 'Sunglasses', 199.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-fillmore-sunglasses-12717-quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-fillmore-sunglasses-12716-quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-fillmore-sunglasses-12718-Quarter.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Zeal Optics Fillmore Sunglasses now. The Zeal Optics Fillmore sunglasses offer a classic look with modern flair. The metal frames are lightweight and corrosion-resistant, with sturdy temples that keep their shape through extended wear. The skull temples curve inward for stability behind the ears, and boast a fun design element at their tips: small rivet details on the endpoints add an urban vibe to these shades. If you\'re looking to make a statement while staying true to your roots, reach for these Fillmore sunglasses from Zeal Optics. Explore Zeal Optics and discover striking eyewear offered in classic and contemporary silhouettes, and designed for active wear. Sporty wraparounds and wraparound-inspired rectangles speak to wearers who want a sleek, modern look; those who prefer a more traditional profile will find squares and rounded-edged frames styles. This eyewear comes in an array of colors and patterns to suit a number of tastes; on-trend embellishments like metal accents on the frames, or distinctive cutaways on the temple arms, impart a hint of sophistication to Zeal Optics frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/zeal-optics-fillmore-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(795, 'Zeal Optics Cumulus', 'Zeal Optics', 'Sunglasses', 179.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-cumulus-sunglasses-12682-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-cumulus-sunglasses-12683-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-cumulus-sunglasses-12684-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-cumulus-sunglasses-12685-Quarter.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Zeal Optics Cumulus Sunglasses now. Zeal Optics Cumulus sunglasses provide a unique aesthetic for outdoor enthusiasts. These unisex sunglasses feature a wraparound design for enhanced protection against wind and glare, while the lightweight plastic material makes them comfortable to wear. The skull temples curve inward slightly to keep the shades from slipping during activities. A keyhole at the upper corner adds visual interest to these eye-catching Cumulus sunglasses by Zeal Optics. Explore Zeal Optics and discover striking eyewear offered in classic and contemporary silhouettes, and designed for active wear. Sporty wraparounds and wraparound-inspired rectangles speak to wearers who want a sleek, modern look; those who prefer a more traditional profile will find squares and rounded-edged frames styles. This eyewear comes in an array of colors and patterns to suit a number of tastes; on-trend embellishments like metal accents on the frames, or distinctive cutaways on the temple arms, impart a hint of sophistication to Zeal Optics frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/zeal-optics-cumulus-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(796, 'Dolce & Gabbana DG4414', 'Dolce & Gabbana', 'Sunglasses', 384.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/dolcegabbana-dg4144-sunglasses-5018g.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Dolce-Gabbana-DG4414-Havana-On-Brown-502-13-Brown-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Dolce & Gabbana DG4414 Sunglasses now. These Dolce & Gabbana DG4414 sunglasses are a glamorous example of timeless Italian style. The bold, oversized frames are made in lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to wear after wear. The slim temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for stability behind the ears. Enjoy effortlessness every day when you slip on these chic sunglasses from Dolce & Gabbana. Luxury is all in the details, and Dolce & Gabbana eyewear for men and women has plenty to show off. Sleek eyeglasses and sunglasses frames accented with metallic embellishments, crystal ornamentation, and more, are as much jewelry as they are eyewear. D&G puts an haute couture spin on classic frames styles that stand out from the crowd.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/dolce-gabbana-dg4414-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(797, 'Ted Baker TWS204', 'Ted Baker', 'Sunglasses', 235.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ted-baker-sun-TWS204-black.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ted-baker-sun-TWS204-ivory-tortoise.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ted Baker TWS204 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Ted Baker frames. Ted Baker women’s TWS204 sunglasses offer a bold, distinctive take on the cat-eye style. The thick rims are made in lightweight plastic that\'s strong enough to keep up on your busy days, no matter where they take you. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears and feature detail near the brow end for added appeal. With chic good looks and contemporary styling, these Ted Baker sunglasses make an exceptional fashion accessory no matter where life takes you. From it\'s beginning as a clothier in Glasglow, Ted Baker has had an unwavering focus on attention to detail, fine quality, and a unique sense of fashion. Ted Baker\'s strong style convictions are obvious in all of Ted Baker\'s eyewear designs. Ted Baker frames cover every aspect of eyewear styling, from timeless sophistication to quirky retro revival and everything in between.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ted-baker-tws204-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(798, 'Giorgio Armani AR8171', 'Giorgio Armani', 'Sunglasses', 452.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Giorgio-Armani-AR8171-Black-5875B1-Dark-Grey-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Giorgio Armani AR8171 Sunglasses now. The Giorgio Armani AR8171 sunglasses for men are a modern update of a timeless rectangular style. The large lenses and thick rims draw attention to your eyes, while the refined details add sophistication. These shades offer excellent protection against glare and wind so you can see clearly even on bright sunny days. Crafted in hypoallergenic plastic, these glasses resist moisture and heat, so they\'re as comfortable at the beach as they are on the tennis court. These timeless rectangular sunglasses from Giorgio Armani add designer appeal to your look. Famed Italian designer Giorgio Armani offers eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses in elevated styles for men and women. Popular eyewear silhouettes boast clean lines and attention to detail to complement your black tie, professional, or everyday attire. Crafted in Italy from high-quality materials in subdued neutrals or lively colors, Giorgio Armani eyewear speaks to the sartorial-minded wearer.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/giorgio-armani-ar8171-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(799, 'Kensie Suite Sun', 'Kensie', 'Sunglasses', 150.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD-0000s-0268-Suite-Sun-YG.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD-0000s-0270-Suite-Sun-SI.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Kensie Suite Sun Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Kensie frames. Bring a little sunshine into your day wearing the Kensie Suite Sun sunglasses. The square rims are crafted in metal, which is both lightweight and sturdy, perfect for protecting your eyes against wind and glare while you’re outdoors. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears. With chic styling that\'s functional as well, these sunglasses from Kensie won\'t leave you hanging when you\'re out in the sun.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/kensie-suite-sun-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(800, 'Kensie Every Summer', 'Kensie', 'Sunglasses', 150.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD-0000s-0265-Every-Summer-CT.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD-0000s-0263-Every-Summer-GR.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Kensie Every Summer Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Kensie frames. Stand out in the crowd wearing the Every Summer sunglasses by Kensie. The oval frames are crafted in lightweight, durable plastic that’s designed to stand up to summer fun. The slim rims feature a subtle keyhole at the upper rim for an elegant look. For sunny days spent outdoors, reach for these chic shades by Kensie.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/kensie-every-summer-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(801, 'Zeal Optics Hawker', 'Zeal Optics', 'Sunglasses', 199.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-hawker-sunglasses-12719-quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-hawker-sunglasses-12721-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/zeal-hawker-sunglasses-12720-quarter.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Zeal Optics Hawker Sunglasses now. Zeal Optics offers a fresh new take on classic metal sunglasses in the Hawker. These unisex frames are made from lightweight metal that’s strong and durable, perfect for your active lifestyle. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and boast a sleek silhouette near the brow end. With their squared lenses, these sunglasses exude an urban cool vibe that\'s all your own. Explore Zeal Optics and discover striking eyewear offered in classic and contemporary silhouettes, and designed for active wear. Sporty wraparounds and wraparound-inspired rectangles speak to wearers who want a sleek, modern look; those who prefer a more traditional profile will find squares and rounded-edged frames styles. This eyewear comes in an array of colors and patterns to suit a number of tastes; on-trend embellishments like metal accents on the frames, or distinctive cutaways on the temple arms, impart a hint of sophistication to Zeal Optics frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/zeal-optics-hawker-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(802, 'Kensie Justify', 'Kensie', 'Sunglasses', 150.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD-0000s-0256-Justify-TO.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD-0000s-0258-Justify-SH.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Kensie Justify Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Kensie frames. Modern meets retro in the Kensie Justify sunglasses. These cat-eye frames are crafted from plastic, a lightweight material that’s durable enough to stand up to wear after wear. The slim temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, with added appeal. Make a statement wearing these chic sunglasses from Kensie.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/kensie-justify-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(803, 'Maui Jim Pailolo-603', 'Maui Jim', 'Sunglasses', 209.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Pailolo-RM603-14-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Pailolo-603-02-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Pailolo-B603-03-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Pailolo-H603-10-Quarter.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Maui Jim Pailolo-603 Sunglasses now. Maui Jim has led the eyewear industry by design and innovation since 1980, offering eyes everywhere superior protection from the harmful rays of the sun in its popular line of sunglasses. From iconic shades with patented technologies, to readers perfect for sunny-day pastimes, to the impressively stylish and comfortable daily-wear frames in the Optical line, Maui Jim creates men’s and women’s performance eyewear for any scenario. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Maui Jim dealer, selling only 100% authentic Maui Jim sunglasses frames and lenses. Polarized with an anti-reflective coating, Maui Jim lenses reveal the vibrant colors of the world while protecting your eyes from the effects of the sun\'s harsh glare and harmful rays. Satisfaction guaranteed. Additional Information: Maui Lens Colors Information (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/maui-jim-pailolo-603-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(804, 'Kensie Just Enough', 'Kensie', 'Sunglasses', 150.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD-0000s-0262-Just-Enough-CA.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/FD-0000s-0260-Just-Enough-RO.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Kensie Just Enough Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Kensie frames. The Kensie Just Enough sunglasses offer a chic twist on the classic square silhouette. The thick rims are made in lightweight plastic that’s strong enough to keep up on your busiest days, when you need shades that stay put, these do. The slim wire-core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and feature detailing near the brow end for added appeal. With their square frames and sleek lenses, these sunglasses from Kensie exude an urban look with fashionable flair.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/kensie-just-enough-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(805, 'Maui Jim Alulu-878', 'Maui Jim', 'Sunglasses', 369.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Alulu-878-02-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Alulu-878-05-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Alulu-H878-10-Quarter.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Maui Jim Alulu-878 Sunglasses now. Maui Jim has led the eyewear industry by design and innovation since 1980, offering eyes everywhere superior protection from the harmful rays of the sun in its popular line of sunglasses. From iconic shades with patented technologies, to readers perfect for sunny-day pastimes, to the impressively stylish and comfortable daily-wear frames in the Optical line, Maui Jim creates men’s and women’s performance eyewear for any scenario. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Maui Jim dealer, selling only 100% authentic Maui Jim sunglasses frames and lenses. Polarized with an anti-reflective coating, Maui Jim lenses reveal the vibrant colors of the world while protecting your eyes from the effects of the sun\'s harsh glare and harmful rays. Satisfaction guaranteed. Additional Information: Maui Lens Colors Information (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/maui-jim-alulu-878-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(806, 'Coach HC8362U', 'Coach', 'Sunglasses', 196.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Coach-HC8362U-574080-Sunglasses_030A.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Coach-HC8362U-50028G-Sunglasses_030A.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Coach HC8362U Sunglasses now. Reach for the chic style and superior quality of these women’s HC8362U sunglasses from Coach. The frames are made in lightweight, durable plastic that\'s strong enough to stand up to wear after wear. The slim arms feature a subtle upsweep at the tips for an elegant look. Subtle detailing on the brow end adds interest to these understated shades. For effortlessness in urban sophistication wherever you go, reach for these sunglasses from Coach. Women’s designer eyewear by Coach exudes a distinctive big-city vibe in chic frames that blend modern sophistication with vintage-inspired style. The result is a collection of daring luxury eyewear that complements a wide range of wardrobes. Browse oversized frames in bold colors, or sleek silhouettes in subtle neutral hues. Coach uses modern color palettes in two-tone frames, but also includes the classics, drawing inspiration from vintage eyewear styles in black or tortoiseshell to create elegant frames that appeal to contemporary tastes.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/coach-ch563-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(807, 'Burberry BE4372U', 'Burberry', 'Sunglasses', 335.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Burberry-BE4372U-3316-5-Sunglasses_030A.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/burberry-be4372u-sunglasses-396180.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Burberry BE4372U Sunglasses now. These BE4372U sunglasses from Burberry are fine examples of contemporary fashion. The cat-eye frames are made in hypoallergenic plastic that’s lightweight and durable, with a sturdy squared browline and slim temples for an edgy look. Enjoy exceptional quality when you opt for these chic sunglasses from Burberry. Throughout Burberry\'s 150 year history, it has become one of the most famous and recognizable names in fashion, not to mention eyewear. Burberry is dedicated to providing the highest quality products and materials so that its eyeglass frames maintain the legacy of fashion, elegance, and style for which Burberry is known. Classic styling and traditional designs are meshed with modern accents and youthful influences to make Burberry a company that never sacrifices style to maintain its high standards.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/burberry-be4372u-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(808, 'Black Flys Aqua Fly', 'Black Flys', 'Sunglasses', 60.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/black-flys-sun-AQUA-FLY-matte-black-smoke-pol.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/black-flys-sun-AQUA-FLY-matte-black-redorg.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/black-flys-sun-AQUA-FLY-matte-black-blue.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Black Flys Aqua Fly Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Black Flys frames. These Aqua Fly sunglasses from Black Flys are perfect for the man who appreciates a classic look. The square-shaped frames are made in lightweight, durable plastic that’ll stand up to your outdoor adventures, whether you\'re on land or water. The thick temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears and feature a unique design near the brow end for added appeal. Enjoy timeless styling with modern performance when you step out in these Aqua Fly sunglasses from Black Flys.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/black-flys-aqua-fly-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(809, 'Ray-Ban RB0316S', 'Ray-Ban', 'Sunglasses', 202.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB0316S-Black-On-Gold-901-31-G-15-Green-Sunglasses-1.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB0316S-Tortoise-On-Gold-990-31-G-15-Green-Sunglasses-1.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB0316S-Havana-On-Blue-On-Gunmetal-13163M-Blue-Sunglasses-1.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB0316S-Green-On-Gold-136851-Light-Brown-Sunglasses-1.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB0316S-Blue-On-Silver-136678-Blue-Sunglasses-1.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB0316S-Black-On-Gold-901-GG-Clear-Blue-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB0316S Sunglasses now. Reach for a pair of Ray-Ban RB0316S sunglasses and enjoy the head start on an effortlessly stylish look. The square frames are made from hypoallergenic plastic that’s lightweight and durable, resulting in sunglasses you can wear all day with no discomfort or worry about them falling apart. The slim temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, with added appeal. Enjoy cool style wherever you go wearing these timeless square sunglasses from Ray-Ban. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb3165-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(810, 'Modo 697', 'Modo', 'Sunglasses', 275.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-sun-697-black.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-sun-697-brown-tortoise.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-sun-697-bright-blue.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-sun-697-silver.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Modo 697 Sunglasses now. Round frames made in lightweight and durable plastic that is resistant to heat and sudden impacts make Modo 697 sunglasses for men a stylish choice for outdoor activities. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears and with quality craftsmanship and an appealing design, these sunglasses live up to their reputation as headwear fit for any occasion, even if you\'re just kicking back on the beach with your friends. The philosophy of Modo is that simplicity is the highest form of sophistication. Created in SoHo, the trendsetting Modo eyewear collection is \"eyewear for the individual.\" Modo eyewear offers a new type of luxury with uncompromising craftsmanship, design sensitivity and urban influences.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/modo-697-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(811, 'Maui Jim Aeko-886', 'Maui Jim', 'Sunglasses', 319.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Aeko-B886-03-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Aeko-886-17-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Aeko-H886-01-Quarter.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Maui Jim Aeko-886 Sunglasses now. Maui Jim has led the eyewear industry by design and innovation since 1980, offering eyes everywhere superior protection from the harmful rays of the sun in its popular line of sunglasses. From iconic shades with patented technologies, to readers perfect for sunny-day pastimes, to the impressively stylish and comfortable daily-wear frames in the Optical line, Maui Jim creates men’s and women’s performance eyewear for any scenario. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Maui Jim dealer, selling only 100% authentic Maui Jim sunglasses frames and lenses. Polarized with an anti-reflective coating, Maui Jim lenses reveal the vibrant colors of the world while protecting your eyes from the effects of the sun\'s harsh glare and harmful rays. Satisfaction guaranteed. Additional Information: Maui Lens Colors Information (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/maui-jim-aeko-886-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(812, 'Modo 695', 'Modo', 'Sunglasses', 275.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-sun-695-black.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-sun-695-light-blue.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-sun-695-crystal.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-sun-695-navy.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Modo 695 Sunglasses now. Modo 695 sunglasses offer an edgy look. The square frames are made in lightweight, durable plastic that’s strong enough to keep up on your adventures. The thick rims feature a subtle wingtip design for added appeal. With their coated temple tips, these shades stay put, whether you\'re exploring the outdoors or city streets. The philosophy of Modo is that simplicity is the highest form of sophistication. Created in SoHo, the trendsetting Modo eyewear collection is \"eyewear for the individual.\" Modo eyewear offers a new type of luxury with uncompromising craftsmanship, design sensitivity and urban influences.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/modo-695-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(813, 'Modo 475', 'Modo', 'Sunglasses', 275.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-sun-475-tortoise.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-sun-475-grey.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-sun-475-petrol.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Modo 475 Sunglasses now. Modo 475 sunglasses offer an edgy aesthetic that’s unmistakably hipster. The square frames are made in metal and plastic, materials that make these shades lightweight but sturdy. Metal accents on the endpoints add contrast to the otherwise monochromatic design. For those who prefer their fashion with a side of irony, try on these Modo sunglasses. The philosophy of Modo is that simplicity is the highest form of sophistication. Created in SoHo, the trendsetting Modo eyewear collection is \"eyewear for the individual.\" Modo eyewear offers a new type of luxury with uncompromising craftsmanship, design sensitivity and urban influences.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/modo-475-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(814, 'Persol PO3310S', 'Persol', 'Sunglasses', 393.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Persol-PO3310S-9531-Sunglasses_030A.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Persol-PO3310S-Dusty-Blue-11893R-Dark-Blue-Polarized-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Persol PO3310S Sunglasses now. Step out in style wearing the Persol PO3310S sunglasses. These unisex oval shades offer a timeless look that’s also distinctive. The thin plastic rims provide ample protection against wind and glare while keeping weight low, so they feel comfortable all day long. These refined oval sunglasses by Persol are a stylish addition to any ensemble. Persol eyewear is among the most well respected and distinguished eyewear brands in the world. Each attractive and comfortable frame is expertly hand crafted in Lauriano, Italy. Persol eyewear is made of only the highest quality materials. Persol\'s Meflecto system gives each Persol frame a patented \"flexible stem\" that makes Persol glasses frames among the most comfortable on the market. Persol\'s ultra-stylish frames and unparalleled craftsmanship make Persol popular with musicians, actors, and cultural icons. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Persol retailer, selling only 100% authentic Persol eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you love: each Persol frame comes with original brand markings certified by Persol itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/persol-po3310s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(815, 'L.A.M.B. LA587 - KELSEY', 'L.A.M.B.', 'Sunglasses', 180.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/lamb-sun-LA587-black-blush.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore L.A.M.B. LA587 - KELSEY Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on L.A.M.B. frames. The LA587 - KELSEY sunglasses series from L.A.M.B. adds edgy style to a timeless silhouette in these sunglasses for women. The rectangular frames are made in lightweight, durable plastic that’s strong enough to keep up on your busiest days, and their sturdy construction means these shades will last through years of wear. The slim temples feature wide tips for stability behind the ears, and boast an engraved metallic LAMB log near the brow end for added appeal. Enjoy urban styling at its finest when you opt for these cool Kelsey sunglasses from L.A.M.B.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/l.a.m.b.-la587-kelsey-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(816, 'Goliath Goliath XXXV', 'Goliath', 'Sunglasses', 780.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/goliath-sun-GOLIATHXXXV-black.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/goliath-sun-GOLIATHXXXV-gold.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Goliath Goliath XXXV Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Goliath frames. Gear up for an action-packed day in the Goliath XXXV sunglasses. These square frames are constructed from metal, which makes them sturdy enough to stand up to tough environments and conditions. The wire cores of the flexible temples allow these shades to adapt to your facial features for a custom fit. You can rely on these sunglasses from Goliath to protect your eyes while you enjoy outdoor activities such as fishing or kayaking, they\'re especially suited for water sports because they won\'t float away!', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/goliath-goliath-xxxv-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
