(819, 'Modo 696', 'Modo', 'Sunglasses', 275.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-sun-696-black.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-sun-696-aqua-green.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Modo 696 Sunglasses now. Modo 696 sunglasses for men exude a fun, youthful vibe. The rectangular frames are made in lightweight plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to wear and tear over time. The thick rims feature a subtle wingtip design for added appeal. With their distinctive skull temples, these shades draw attention wherever you go. The philosophy of Modo is that simplicity is the highest form of sophistication. Created in SoHo, the trendsetting Modo eyewear collection is \"eyewear for the individual.\" Modo eyewear offers a new type of luxury with uncompromising craftsmanship, design sensitivity and urban influences.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/modo-696-sunglasses', NULL, NULL);
