(820, 'Polaroid Pld 4117/G/S/X', 'Polaroid', 'Sunglasses', 128.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Polaroid-sun-PLD-4117GSX-grey-KB7.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/polaroid-sun-PLD4117GSX-black-0807M9.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Polaroid Pld 4117/G/S/X Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Polaroid frames. Reach for a pair of Polaroid Pld 4117/G/S/X sunglasses and enjoy the attention you receive. The bold, thick frames are made from plastic that’s lightweight and durable, with rounded edges that keep them comfortable to wear. The skull temples curve inward gently to keep the shades from slipping during your active lifestyle. A keyhole at each end of these men\'s sunglasses invites interest: With or without lenses, they\'re eye-catching fashion accessories.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/polaroid-pld-4117-g-s-x-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(821, 'Goliath Goliath XXXII', 'Goliath', 'Sunglasses', 620.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/goliath-sun-GOLIATHXXXII-black.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Goliath Goliath XXXII Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Goliath frames. Command attention in the Goliath XXXII sunglasses for men. These bold shades feature metal rims and plastic temples, creating a durable design that stands up to active lifestyles. Metal accents on the ends of the brow edges add contrast for an appealing look, while rounded tips offer comfort behind the ears. To make these sunglasses yours, log on to eBay to find them at a discounted rate through your favorite online retailer.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/goliath-goliath-xxxii-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(822, 'Goliath Goliath XXVII', 'Goliath', 'Sunglasses', 636.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/goliath-sun-GOLIATHXXVII-black.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/goliath-sun-GOLIATHXXVII-gold.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Goliath Goliath XXVII Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Goliath frames. Step out in style wearing the Goliath XXVII sunglasses. The rounded edges of these shades offer a softer look that’s perfect for men with soft features. A metal frame offers strength and durability, while thin wire cores at the edges provide flexibility to help the glasses stay put while you work outdoors or play indoors. Topped with distinctive brow ends and sleek lines, these handsome sunglasses from Goliath XXVII make it easy to add an edgy vibe to your everyday look.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/goliath-goliath-xxvii-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(823, 'Vera Bradley Sylvie', 'Vera Bradley', 'Sunglasses', 183.89, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/verabradley-SYLVIE-enchated-mandala.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/verabradley-SYLVIE-sunlight-garden-sage.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Vera Bradley Sylvie Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Vera Bradley frames. These Sylvie sunglasses by Vera Bradley make an ideal fashion accessory for women. The cat-eye frames are made in metal that’s lightweight but sturdy, with plastic rims that are durable and attractive. The metal components feature corrosion-resistant construction for lasting beauty over time. With their classic silhouette, these stylish shades exude urban sophistication wherever you go.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/vera-bradley-sylvie-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(824, 'Furla SFU690V', 'Furla', 'Sunglasses', 311.30, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/furla-sun-SFU690V-shiny-rose-gold.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/furla-sun-SFU690V-shiny-copper-gold.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Furla SFU690V Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Furla frames. Reach for a pair of Furla SFU690V sunglasses and enjoy the cat-eye style at its finest. These chic shades are made in lightweight metal that’s strong enough to keep up on your busiest days. The slim temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, with added appeal. With exceptional design and quality construction throughout, these charming cat-eye sunglasses from Furla will become a go-to accessory in your wardrobe.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/furla-sfu690v-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(825, 'L.A.M.B. LA583 - CHELSEA', 'L.A.M.B.', 'Sunglasses', 180.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/lamb-sun-LA583-black.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/lamb-sun-LA583-purple.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore L.A.M.B. LA583 - CHELSEA Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on L.A.M.B. frames. L.A.M.B. adds a touch of glam to the classic aviator in these LA583 Chelsea sunglasses. The metal rims are strong and lightweight, resulting in comfortable frames that won\'t cause discomfort after hours in the sun. The robust hinges allow these shades to pivot securely without slipping, so you can adjust them according to the angle of the sun or an oncoming breeze. For effortlessness and sophistication wherever you go, reach for these chic aviator sunglasses by L.A.M.B.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/l.a.m.b.-la583-chelsea-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(826, 'Maui Jim Pehu-602', 'Maui Jim', 'Sunglasses', 209.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Pehu-602-02-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Pehu-B602-03-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Pehu-H602-10-Quarter.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Pehu-RM602-14-Quarter.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Maui Jim Pehu-602 Sunglasses now. Discover a new look wearing the unisex Pehu-602 sunglasses from Maui Jim. These bold, thick frames feature an unusual shape that’s both retro and modern at once. The sturdy plastic construction keeps these shades light and comfortable, while the double rivet detailing adds eye-catching appeal at the corners of the lenses. For exceptional quality in sunglasses designed for everyday wear, choose these Pehu-602 shades by Maui Jim. Maui Jim has led the eyewear industry by design and innovation since 1980, offering eyes everywhere superior protection from the harmful rays of the sun in its popular line of sunglasses. From iconic shades with patented technologies, to readers perfect for sunny-day pastimes, to the impressively stylish and comfortable daily-wear frames in the Optical line, Maui Jim creates men’s and women’s performance eyewear for any scenario. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Maui Jim dealer, selling only 100% authentic Maui Jim sunglasses frames and lenses. Polarized with an anti-reflective coating, Maui Jim lenses reveal the vibrant colors of the world while protecting your eyes from the effects of the sun\'s harsh glare and harmful rays. Satisfaction guaranteed. Additional Information: Maui Lens Colors Information (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/maui-jim-pehu-602-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(827, 'Tommy Hilfiger Th 1904/S', 'Tommy Hilfiger', 'Sunglasses', 150.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/tommy-hilfiger-sun-TH1904S-matteblack-0003IR.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/tommy-hilfiger-sun-TH1904S-matteblue-0FLLKU.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Tommy Hilfiger Th 1904/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Tommy Hilfiger frames. Tommy Hilfiger crafts these Th 1904/S sunglasses for men in a classic, rectangular design. The rims are made in metal, which is strong and durable, ideal for functional sunglasses that you wear every day. The wire-core temples grow wider at the tips for added stability behind the ears. Enjoy clean styling when you step out in these cool Tommy Hilfiger shades. Tommy Hilfiger presents the same “preppy with a twist” vibe in its eyewear collection for men and women, as seen in this celebrated designer’s apparel and accessories collections. Men’s and women’s sunglasses and eyeglasses frames from Tommy Hilfiger offer the ideal combination of classic style and modern trends.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/tommy-hilfiger-th-1904-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
