(837, 'Cazal 8045', 'Cazal', 'Sunglasses', 852.50, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/cazal-sun-8045-black-gold-001.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/cazal-sun-8045-cyrstal-bicolour-002.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/cazal-sun-8045-grey-silver-grey-003.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Cazal 8045 Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Cazal frames. These Cazal 8045 sunglasses for men are crafted in a lightweight, durable plastic that’s designed to withstand the elements. The square frames come with thick sides and thin temples for a sporty look. For comfort as well as style, opt for these sunglasses from Cazal . Cazal Eyewear, the label once directed by legendary designer Cari Zalloni, has a long history of producing eyeglasses and sunglasses for men and women, favored by hip hop artists and the Hollywood elite. Daring Cazal frames showcase intricate patterns and over-the-top design elements for a ‘more is more\' appeal. Cazal frames serve as a canvas for showy gold, flashy silver, and crystal clear styling, together with classic tortoiseshell and gorgeous marbled coloring. The most exquisite frames in the Cazal collection are gold or silver plated, for a jewelry-like quality.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/cazal-8045-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(838, 'Marc Jacobs Marc 577/S', 'Marc Jacobs', 'Sunglasses', 195.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Marc-Jacob-sun-MARC577S-black-08079O.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Marc Jacobs Marc 577/S Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Marc Jacobs frames. These Marc 577/S sunglasses exude the same urban chic aesthetic that has made designer Marc Jacobs a household name. The square frames are crafted in lightweight, durable plastic that’s designed to stand up to wear and tear over time. The slim temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for stability behind the ears. An engraved metallic band adorns the brow end of these cool shades from Marc Jacobs, adding an element of elegance wherever you go wearing them. The Marc Jacobs eyewear line has the perfect frames for men and women with eclectic tastes. Marc Jacobs eyeglasses, sunglasses, and prescription sunglasses incorporate whimsical touches—think sculptural flowers at the temples, or frames shapes transformed from oval to cat-eye with an artful arc of metal around the lenses. Go bold or go subtle with Marc Jacobs eyewear, with chunky, oversized sunglasses in the mix alongside streamlined everyday glasses that transition effortlessly from work to weekend.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/marc-jacobs-marc-577-s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
