(844, 'Trina Turk Lundy', 'Trina Turk', 'Sunglasses', 207.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/trina-turk-LUNDY-indigo.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/trina-turk-LUNDY-pink-tortoise.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Trina Turk Lundy Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Trina Turk frames. Enjoy an on-trend aesthetic when you wear the Trina Turk Lundy sunglasses. These rounded, rimmed sunglasses feature plastic rims that are lightweight and durable, resulting in comfortable frames you can wear all day long. The thickened temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, and boast a stylish look near the brow end for added appeal. Make a statement wearing these fun sunglasses from Trina Turk.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/trina-turk-lundy-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(845, 'Ray-Ban RB4393M', 'Ray-Ban', 'Sunglasses', 240.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB4393M-Scuderia-Ferrari-Collection-F68087-Green-On-Black-Grey-a.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB4393M Sunglasses now. Update your look with a pair of Ray-Ban RB4393M sunglasses. These unisex rectangular frames are constructed from lightweight, durable plastic that’s designed to stand up to wear and tear over time. The unique design of the temples features a curved inner edge for increased stability behind the ears and come with coated tips for comfort behind the neck. With their timeless silhouette, these cool shades from Ray-Ban will add some vintage style to your everyday look. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb4393m-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(846, 'Dolce & Gabbana DG6179', 'Dolce & Gabbana', 'Sunglasses', 386.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Dolce-Gabbana-DG6179-Matte-3395M1-Green-To-Dark-Green-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/dolcegabbana-dg4144-sunglasses-252581.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Dolce & Gabbana DG6179 Sunglasses now. These DG6179 sunglasses from Dolce & Gabbana are perfect for the man who appreciates classic aviator style. The distinctive keyhole bridges lend an air of sophistication, while the skull temples add a rugged feel. Constructed in lightweight plastic, these shades weigh little yet still provide good protection from glare and wind at high speeds. A metallic plate engraved with the brand name appears at each side of the slim silhouette, adding designer appeal to these timeless aviator sunglasses from Dolce & Gabbana. Luxury is all in the details, and Dolce & Gabbana eyewear for men and women has plenty to show off. Sleek eyeglasses and sunglasses frames accented with metallic embellishments, crystal ornamentation, and more, are as much jewelry as they are eyewear. D&G puts an haute couture spin on classic frames styles that stand out from the crowd.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/dolce-gabbana-dg6179-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
