(898, 'Smith Lowdown Metal', 'Smith', 'Sunglasses', 215.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-LOWDOWN-METAL-matte-black-silver-gray-green-TI754L7.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-LOWDOWN-METAL-matte-black-black-003546N.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-LOWDOWN-METAL-brushed-gunmetal-bronze-mirror-KJ154QE.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Smith Lowdown Metal Sunglasses now. Command attention in the Smith Lowdown Metal sunglasses. These square frames are made in a lightweight metal that’s strong enough to keep up on your busiest days. The metal rims feature an eye-catching twist design for added style. For sunny days when you need to make an impression, reach for these cool shades from Smith.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/smith-lowdown-metal-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(899, 'Smith Lake Shasta', 'Smith', 'Sunglasses', 205.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-LAKE-SHASTA-matte-black-grey-green-00356L7.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-LAKE-SHASTA-tortoise-rose-gold-mirror-086569V.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-LAKE-SHASTA-tortoise-brown-08656L5.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Smith-Sun-Lake-Shasta-Pacific-Crystal-Gray-Green-QM456L7.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-sun-Lake-Shasta-Rosewood-Crystal-YL356L5.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Smith Lake Shasta Sunglasses now. Smith offers a bold, sporty take on the classic round-frame sunglasses in the Lake Shasta. The thick frames are made from Propel plastic, which is lightweight and durable, ideal for glasses you wear often. The skull temples curve inward gently to keep the shades from slipping during activities such as surfing or snowboarding. A subtle keyhole at the top of the rims allows air to circulate around your eyes, keeping them cool and comfortable even on sunny days. An adjustable wire core allows you to customize these Smith sunglasses for your head size so they stay put no matter where your adventure takes you.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/smith-lake-shasta-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(900, 'Smith Shift XL MAG', 'Smith', 'Sunglasses', 285.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-SHIFT-XL-MAG-white-violet-mirror-VK699DI.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-SHIFT-XL-MAG-matte-black-003991C.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-SHIFT-XL-MAG-black-red-mirror-80799X6.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-SHIFT-XL-MAG-matte-bone-black-gold-mirror-Z1P990K.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Smith-Sun-Shift-XL-MAG-Black-Gray-807992W.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-sun-Shift-XL-Mag-Matte-Tortoise-Photochromic-N9P99GH.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Smith Shift XL MAG Sunglasses now. These Smith Shift XL MAG sunglasses offer an edgy look that’s sure to turn heads. The wrap-around design offers enhanced protection against wind and glare, while the skull temples add a little edge to your style. These unisex shades are made from lightweight plastic that\'s durable enough to last through your longest days on the water or trail.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/smith-shift-xl-mag-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(901, 'Smith Whitney', 'Smith', 'Sunglasses', 205.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-WHITNEY-matte-black-polarized-gray-green-00361L7.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-WHITNEY-tortoise-polarized-brown-08661L5.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-WHITNEY-tortoise-polarized-rose-gold-mirror-086619V.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Smith-Sun-Whitney-Opal-Fade-Opal-Mirror-LJT61QG.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Smith Whitney Sunglasses now. Live life on the wild side wearing the Smith Whitney sunglasses. These shades boast a fun, retro-inspired design with colors and patterns that stand out in a crowd. The plastic frames are lightweight and durable, perfect for long days in the sun. The thick temples curve inward gently to keep the glasses from slipping during activities, and come coated with socks over tips for comfort behind the ears. With their rounded edges and distinctive skull patterns at each end of the rims, these cool sunglasses bring a touch of urban flair wherever you go.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/smith-whitney-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(902, 'Original Penguin The Brooks Sun', 'Original Penguin', 'Sunglasses', 243.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Original-Penguin-sun-THE-BROOKS-electric-purple.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Original-Penguin-sun-THE-BROOKS-omphalodes.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Original Penguin The Brooks Sun Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Original Penguin frames. The Brooks Sun sunglasses series from Original Penguin are an ideal choice for the fashion-conscious man. With their rounded edges and lightweight plastic construction, these sunglasses lend a youthful look, while the distinctive browline adds sophistication. Their sleek silhouette exudes urban cool whether you’re relaxing on the beach or exploring a new city. Drawing from the eyewear fashion of the 1950s, our collection of Original Penguin showcases timeless silhouettes in full-rim and semi-rimless styles, paired with contemporary details. Clubmaster-inspired frames are the focus, in rounded-edge and square variations. Traditional round and aviator shapes are represented for a classically cool profile; modern ovals and rectangles present a more tailored look. This designer eyewear offers frames styles to suit a number of tastes, in shapes made to complement any face.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/original-penguin-the-brooks-sun-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(903, 'Smith Boomtown', 'Smith', 'Sunglasses', 215.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-sun-Boomtown-Matte-Dark-Tortoise-B0Q99QE.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-BOOMTOWN-matte-tortoise-opal-mirror-HGC99QG.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-BOOMTOWN-matte-black-chromapop-black-003991C.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-BOOMTOWN-matte-black-blue-mirror-00399XX.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-BOOMTOWN-matte-blac-red-mirror-00399X6.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Smith-Sun-Boomtown-Matte-Black-Polarized-Black-00399Z1.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/smith-sun-Boomtown-Matte-Black-00399ZY.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Smith Boomtown Sunglasses now. Stand out from the crowd in Smith Boomtown sunglasses. The wrap-around frames on these unisex shades provide extra protection against glare and wind so you can enjoy an unobstructed view of your surroundings. An adjustable wirecore provides a customized fit, while durable plastic rims stand up to heavy use. With their sporty styling, these sunglasses from Smith are perfect for outdoor adventures.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/smith-boomtown-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(904, 'Original Penguin The Tommy Sun', 'Original Penguin', 'Sunglasses', 243.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Original-Penguin-sun-THE-TOMMY-highrise.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Original-Penguin-sun-THE-TOMMY-crystal.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Original-Penguin-sun-THE-TOMMY-safari.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Original Penguin The Tommy Sun Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Original Penguin frames. The Tommy Sun series from Original Penguin adds a touch of vintage style to the classic shades in these sunglasses for men. The rounded edges and strong lines of the rims recall styles favored by movie stars of decades past, while plastic provides lightweight, durable frames that are comfortable to wear. Crafted from high-quality materials, these frames won\'t lose their luster over time. Drawing from the eyewear fashion of the 1950s, our collection of Original Penguin showcases timeless silhouettes in full-rim and semi-rimless styles, paired with contemporary details. Clubmaster-inspired frames are the focus, in rounded-edge and square variations. Traditional round and aviator shapes are represented for a classically cool profile; modern ovals and rectangles present a more tailored look. This designer eyewear offers frames styles to suit a number of tastes, in shapes made to complement any face.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/original-penguin-the-tommy-sun-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
