(906, 'Kaenon El Cap', 'Kaenon', 'Sunglasses', 100.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/kaenon-elcap-sunglasses-076mbmbgng120-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/kaenon-elcap-sunglasses-076memeglb120-angle.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/kaenon-elcap-sunglasses-076mbmbgnice-angle.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Kaenon El Cap Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Kaenon frames. Kaenon delivers high-quality, innovative style in these El Cap sunglasses. The unisex frame material is lightweight and durable plastic that\'s designed to stand up to the elements. The slim temples curve inward gently for stability, and boast wide tips for added comfort behind the ears. Enjoy cutting-edge design when you opt for these cool Kaenon El Cap sunglasses.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/kaenon-el-cap-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
