(910, 'Badgley Mischka Elania', 'Badgley Mischka', 'Sunglasses', 232.30, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/bm-ELANIA-black.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/bm-ELANIA-blue.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/bm-ELANIA-ruby.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Badgley Mischka Elania Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Badgley Mischka frames. Crafted in lightweight, durable plastic, the Badgley Mischka Elania sunglasses offer square frames that are sturdy enough to stand up to wear after wear. The skull temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears and for timeless style with modern flair, reach for these chic sunglasses from Badgley Mischka. Add a touch of glamour to your everyday look with the Badgley Mischka Elania sunglasses.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/badgley-mischka-elania-sunglasses', NULL, NULL);
