(991, 'Modo 469', 'Modo', 'Sunglasses', 275.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-469-black.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-469-teal.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-469-dark-rose.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/modo-469-yellow.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Modo 469 Sunglasses now. Modo 469 sunglasses for women exude a fun, youthful style. The cat-eye frames are made in metal and plastic, materials that allow these glasses to be lightweight while still durable. Metal rims accentuate the shape of the eyes, drawing attention to your beautiful features. A slim metal band encircles the browline of these Modo sunglasses for a touch of elegance. Enjoy sunny weather in comfort when you slip on these flattering shades from Modo. The philosophy of Modo is that simplicity is the highest form of sophistication. Created in SoHo, the trendsetting Modo eyewear collection is \"eyewear for the individual.\" Modo eyewear offers a new type of luxury with uncompromising craftsmanship, design sensitivity and urban influences.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/modo-469-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(992, 'Maui Jim Mano-877', 'Maui Jim', 'Sunglasses', 399.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/MauiJim-sun-mano-877-02.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/MauiJim-sun-mano-877-03.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/MauiJim-sun-mano-877-01.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Maui Jim Mano-877 Sunglasses now. The Maui Jim Mano-877 sunglasses offer a fun, youthful look. The square rims are made in a lightweight metal that’s sturdy enough to keep up on your adventures. These frames come with coated temple tips for comfort behind the ears, and feature an elegant saddlebridge design for an appealing appearance when you lift them to speak or listen. If you\'re looking for shades with personality, opt for these from Maui Jim. Maui Jim has led the eyewear industry by design and innovation since 1980, offering eyes everywhere superior protection from the harmful rays of the sun in its popular line of sunglasses. From iconic shades with patented technologies, to readers perfect for sunny-day pastimes, to the impressively stylish and comfortable daily-wear frames in the Optical line, Maui Jim creates men’s and women’s performance eyewear for any scenario. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Maui Jim dealer, selling only 100% authentic Maui Jim sunglasses frames and lenses. Polarized with an anti-reflective coating, Maui Jim lenses reveal the vibrant colors of the world while protecting your eyes from the effects of the sun\'s harsh glare and harmful rays. Satisfaction guaranteed. Additional Information: Maui Lens Colors Information (PDF)', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/maui-jim-mano-877-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(993, 'Ralph Lauren RL8206U', 'Ralph Lauren', 'Sunglasses', 236.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ralph-Lauren-RL8206U-Shiny-Havana-530373-Dark-Brown-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ralph-lauren-sun-RL8206U-50018G.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ralph-Lauren-RL8206U-Light-Havana-605173-Brown-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ralph-Lauren-RL8206U-Cream-Horn-608413-Gradient-Brown-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ralph Lauren RL8206U Sunglasses now. Step out in sophisticated style wearing the women’s Ralph Lauren RL8206U sunglasses. The cat-eye frames are made from hypoallergenic plastic that\'s lightweight and durable, with a skull shape for an edgy look. The slim temples curve inward slightly for stability behind the ears and boast an appealing shape near the brow end. With decades of design experience, Ralph Lauren takes sunglasses beyond their functional roots to make them beautiful accessories as well as protective gear. The Ralph Lauren brand has been creating sophisticated and timeless styles since its inception in 1970. Ralph Lauren designs celebrate the refined luxury and understated elegance that is at the heart of American fashion. Ralph Lauren makes eyewear that is attractive and elegant, and Ralph Lauren\'s distinctive luxury is reflected in every frame. Ralph Lauren\'s contemporary styles and homage to vintage designs contribute to each frame\'s clean lines, subtle glamour, and uncomplicated class.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ralph-lauren-rl8206u-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(994, 'Ray-Ban RB0880S', 'Ray-Ban', 'Sunglasses', 202.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB0880S-Black-901-31-Green-Sunglasses-1.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-RB0880S-Transparent-Green-66353R-Dark-Blue-Sunglasses-1.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban RB0880S Sunglasses now. Reach for a pair of Ray-Ban RB0880S sunglasses and enjoy the attention you\'ll receive. The square, unisex frames are crafted in lightweight, durable plastic that\'s designed to stand up to your busy lifestyle. Wear these shades when you want to make a statement: they feature thick bands with finely textured ends for an elegant look. A keyhole at the end of each band adds interest to the otherwise simple silhouette of these sunglasses from Ray-Ban. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-rb0880s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(995, 'Ray-Ban Junior RJ9565S - Jack Kids', 'Ray-Ban Junior', 'Sunglasses', 97.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Junior-Jack-Kids-291-8H-Rose-Gold-Gradient-Dark-Violet-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Junior-Jack-Kids-212-80-Silver-Dark-Blue-a.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ray-Ban-Junior-Jack-Kids-223-71-Gold-Green-a.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ray-Ban Junior RJ9565S - Jack Kids Sunglasses now. These Ray-Ban Junior RJ9565S Jack Kids sunglasses have a fun, youthful look that’s sure to please. The round frames are made in a lightweight metal that\'s durable enough to keep up on your kid\'s active days. The skull temples curve inward for stability behind the ears and feature tips that widen for added comfort. A keyhole at the temple end adds interest to these cool shades from Ray-Ban Junior. Ray-Ban eyewear has long set industry style standards for its timeless, retro aesthetic, setting itself apart from lesser makers with the original Wayfarer Classic—arguably the most recognizable and iconic silhouette in the history of sunglasses. From the likes of General Douglas MacArthur to movie star Peter Fonda, denizens of celebrities the world over have defined their personal style by their Ray-Ban eyewear, and still prefer these instantly recognizable frames today. As a Ray-Ban Certified Store, FramesDirect.com sells only 100% authentic Ray-Ban sunglasses, eyeglasses, and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the eyewear you love: each Ray-Ban frame comes in its original packaging with original brand markings, certified by Ray-Ban itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ray-ban-junior-rj9565s-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(996, 'RALPH by Ralph Lauren RA5292', 'RALPH by Ralph Lauren', 'Sunglasses', 90.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ralph-by-ralph-lauren-sun-RA5292-50018G.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ralph-by-ralph-lauren-sun-RA5292-601113.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore RALPH by Ralph Lauren RA5292 Sunglasses now. These women’s RALPH by Ralph Lauren RA5292 sunglasses are a perfect example of timeless style. The rectangular frames are made in hypoallergenic, lightweight plastic that\'s durable enough to stand up to your hard-working lifestyle. The wire-core temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, with added appeal. Enjoy sophisticated styling when you opt for these cool shades. Ralph by Ralph Lauren lends compelling drama to the brand’s Ivy League-inspired roots. Discover oversized sunglasses frames, chunky styles, and sleek silhouettes, all with the effortless sophistication perfected by Ralph Lauren. The designer first shared his pioneering style in 1967 with the release of a line of men’s striped ties. They became an immediate hit and Lauren grew his business into a global fashion and lifestyle brand that includes his sunglasses and prescription sunglasses collection.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ralph-by-ralph-lauren-ra5292-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(997, 'Ralph Lauren RL8205', 'Ralph Lauren', 'Sunglasses', 208.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ralph-lauren-sun-RL8205-513480.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Ralph Lauren RL8205 Sunglasses now. For a fresh, fashion-forward look, reach for the Ralph Lauren RL8205 sunglasses. These cool shades feature rectangular frames made in lightweight, lustrous plastic that’s durable enough to stand up to heavy wear. The distinctive rims are crafted in a double brow line with contrasting details at the inner corners for added appeal. For effortlessness and sophistication wherever you go, choose these eye-catching RL sunglasses from Ralph Lauren. The Ralph Lauren brand has been creating sophisticated and timeless styles since its inception in 1970. Ralph Lauren designs celebrate the refined luxury and understated elegance that is at the heart of American fashion. Ralph Lauren makes eyewear that is attractive and elegant, and Ralph Lauren\'s distinctive luxury is reflected in every frame. Ralph Lauren\'s contemporary styles and homage to vintage designs contribute to each frame\'s clean lines, subtle glamour, and uncomplicated class.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ralph-lauren-rl8205-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(998, 'RALPH by Ralph Lauren RA5293', 'RALPH by Ralph Lauren', 'Sunglasses', 96.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ralph-VVCV-Shiny-Dark-Havana-50033B-Brown-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ralph-VVCV-Shiny-Black-6037T3-Polar-Brown-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ralph-RA5293-Shiny-Havana-Yellow-6148T5-Polar-Brown-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/ralph-by-ralph-lauren-sun-RA5293-60378E.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ralph-RA5293-Shiny-Transparent-Brown-6072T5-Polar-Gradient-Brown-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ralph-RA5293-Striped-Purple-603662-Violet-Polar-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Ralph-RA5293-Shiny-Striped-Purple-60368H-Gradient-Violet-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore RALPH by Ralph Lauren RA5293 Sunglasses now. Reach for the RALPH by Ralph Lauren RA5293 sunglasses and enjoy the retro vibe of stylish square rims. The thick, solid frames are made in hypoallergenic plastic that’s lightweight but sturdy enough to last through extended wear. The elegant keyhole at the upper rims draws attention to your eyes, while subtle wingtips provide balance and stability behind the ears. For luxurious sunglasses with vintage styling, reach for these square-framed shades. Ralph by Ralph Lauren lends compelling drama to the brand’s Ivy League-inspired roots. Discover oversized sunglasses frames, chunky styles, and sleek silhouettes, all with the effortless sophistication perfected by Ralph Lauren. The designer first shared his pioneering style in 1967 with the release of a line of men’s striped ties. They became an immediate hit and Lauren grew his business into a global fashion and lifestyle brand that includes his sunglasses and prescription sunglasses collection.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/ralph-by-ralph-lauren-ra5293-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(999, 'Tom Ford FT0832 - N Fletcher', 'Tom Ford', 'Sunglasses', 480.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Tom-Ford-FT0832-N-Shiny-Black-1330L1-Grey-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns! Explore Tom Ford FT0832 - N Fletcher Sunglasses now and enjoy the latest promotions on Tom Ford frames.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/tom-ford-ft0832-n-fletcher-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(1000, 'Michael Kors MK2163 - San Marino', 'Michael Kors', 'Sunglasses', 155.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/michael-kors-sun-MK2163-391773.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Michael Kors MK2163 - San Marino Sunglasses now. In the MK2163 San Marino sunglasses, Michael Kors offers women a timeless square-frame design that’s as chic as it is functional. The oversized rims are crafted in hypoallergenic plastic for comfort and durability. A double rivet adds detail to the slim wire-core temples. Enjoy vintage styling with modern features when you step out in these San Marino sunglasses from Michael Kors. The sophisticated Michael Kors eyewear collection presents classic elegance to suit a variety of tastes. Frames by this celebrated designer exude a timeless appeal to complement modern wardrobes, but plenty of daring, trendsetting styles appear throughout the collection. From the modern, clean eyeglasses to the chic, wearable outerwear parading down the runways, Michael Kors continues to be a popular choice with those seeking accessible luxury.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/michael-kors-mk2163-san-marino-sunglasses', NULL, NULL);
