(1001, 'Oakley Youth Resistor', 'Oakley Youth', 'Sunglasses', 143.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Resistor-Olympic-Gold-901008-Prizm-24K-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Resistor-Polished-White-901007-Prizm-Sapphire-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Resistor-Sky-Blue-901005-Ruby-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Resistor-Polished-White-901004-Field-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Youth-Resistor-Ginger-901018-Prizm-Ruby-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Youth-Resistor-Youth-Fit-Yellow-901028-Prizm-Tungsten-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Resistor-Redline-901002-Prizm-Road-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Resistor-Retina-Burn-901006-Prizm-Jade-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Youth-Resistor-Matte-Celeste-901019-Prizm-Sapphire-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Youth-Resistor-Black-901020-Prizm-Grey-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Resistor-Re-Discover-Blue-Steel-901016-Sapphire-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Resistor-Patrick-Mahomes-II-Matte-Terrain-Tan-901017-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Resistor-Polished-Black-901001-Grey-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Youth-Resistor-Fern-Terrazzo-901032-Prizm-Black-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Youth-Resistor-Matte-White-901033-Prizm-Jade-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Youth-Resistor-Matte-Navy-901034-Prizm-Ruby-Sunglasses.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/Oakley-Youth-Resistor-Redline-901035-Prizm-Sapphire-Sunglasses.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Oakley Youth Resistor Sunglasses now. Resistor (Youth Fit) sunglasses from Oakley Youth boast an athletic, sporty look that appeals to the young and trendy. The wraparound style offers the best possible protection against glare from windscreens and water on puddles, while keeping eyes safe from errant balls or flying discs. Lightweight O Matter plastic keeps these shades durable for active children with wide-set eyes. Three-pointed lenses call attention to these youth-sized Resistor sunglasses by Oakley. The Oakley brand is universally recognized and is synonymous with innovative, quality craftsmanship. Oakley is a leading name in sports sunglasses because it offers athletes stylish shades that are made with cutting edge design and technology so that it not only looks good but can also withstand harsh environments and truly extreme conditions. Oakley has perfected sporty wrap sunglasses and shields and has modernized interpretations of other classic designs. The Oakley sunglass collection offers a wide variety of frames in an exciting collection of colors and performance-driven lens shading. FramesDirect.com is your online outlet for Oakley Sunglasses. FramesDirect.com is an authorized Oakley retailer, selling only 100% authentic Oakley lenses with its sunglasses and prescription sunglasses frames. Shop confidently for the quality eyewear you demand: each Oakley frame comes with original brand markings certified by Oakley itself.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/oakley-youth-resistor-youth-fit-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(1002, 'Michael Kors MK2177 - Cheyenne', 'Michael Kors', 'Sunglasses', 167.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/michael-kors-sun-MK2177-325113.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/michael-kors-sun-MK2177-300613.jpg, https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/michael-kors-sun-MK2177-31068G.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Michael Kors MK2177 - Cheyenne Sunglasses now. The Michael Kors MK2177 - Cheyenne sunglasses offer a retro-inspired square silhouette. These women’s frames are made from lightweight, lustrous plastic that\'s comfortable to wear. The slim temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for stability behind the ears. Enjoy classic styling with modern flair when you opt for these cool Cheyenne sunglasses from Michael Kors. The sophisticated Michael Kors eyewear collection presents classic elegance to suit a variety of tastes. Frames by this celebrated designer exude a timeless appeal to complement modern wardrobes, but plenty of daring, trendsetting styles appear throughout the collection. From the modern, clean eyeglasses to the chic, wearable outerwear parading down the runways, Michael Kors continues to be a popular choice with those seeking accessible luxury.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/michael-kors-mk2177-cheyenne-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(1003, 'Emporio Armani EA2134', 'Emporio Armani', 'Sunglasses', 194.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/emporio-armani-sun-EA2134-316113.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Emporio Armani EA2134 Sunglasses now. These men\'s EA2134 sunglasses from Emporio Armani offer a modern take on the classic horn-frame design. The oval frames are made in a lightweight metal that\'s strong enough to keep up on your busiest days. The slim temples curve inward gently and widen at the tips for stability behind the ears. With their distinctive design, these sunglasses stand out from the crowd wherever you go. The Emporio Armani eyewear collection leans on minimalist contemporary silhouettes and thick-rimmed frames in vibrant colors to create stunning modern eyewear for men and women. Youthful styles abound, with quirky accents and novel details that reflect your bold sense of fashion. The Armani tradition for smart luxury design shows in the artful lines and thoughtful details of this eyewear collection. Express your personal taste in sharp glasses from Emporio Armani.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/emporio-armani-ea2134-sunglasses', NULL, NULL),
(1004, 'Dolce & Gabbana DG6177', 'Dolce & Gabbana', '', 354.00, NULL, '[https://www.framesdirect.com/product_color_images/dolce-gabbana-sun-DG6177-501-87.jpg]', 'Free Shipping & Easy Returns, plus Price Match! Explore Dolce & Gabbana DG6177 Sunglasses now. Step out in style wearing the Dolce & Gabbana DG6177 sunglasses. These bold rectangular frames are made from hypoallergenic plastic that’s lightweight and durable, ideal for someone who likes to wear their shades often. The distinctive head-shaped temples curve inward gently for stability behind the ears, with an added touch of elegance. Fashioned in Italy, these unique sunglasses from Dolce & Gabbana will complete your everyday look. Luxury is all in the details, and Dolce & Gabbana eyewear for men and women has plenty to show off. Sleek eyeglasses and sunglasses frames accented with metallic embellishments, crystal ornamentation, and more, are as much jewelry as they are eyewear. D&G puts an haute couture spin on classic frames styles that stand out from the crowd.', 'https://www.framesdirect.com/dolce-gabbana-dg6177-sunglasses', '', NULL);
